(35, 'Stories from our Members - Thibault Marion', 1, 'stories-from-our-members---thibault-marion', '', 'Stories from our Members - Thibault Marion', 'Stories from our Members - Thibault Marion', 'Welcome to member profiles! In this series we want to share one members&rsquo; story on why they moved to NYC', '<p>Welcome to member profiles! In this series we want to share one members&rsquo; story on why they moved to NYC, why they stayed with Outpost Club and on what they like(d) about their time here. This week we&rsquo;re introducing you to Thibault.&nbsp;I hope you enjoy this article and to find out more about us or our members, go to &nbsp;www.outpost-club.com.</p>', '<p>Introduce yourself</p>\r\n<div>\r\n<h2><strong>Who are you?</strong></h2>\r\n<p>That\'s a big question, who am I? I\'m Thibault, I\'m from France but live in Shakespeare and Big Shaq \'s country: England. Skrrt. I am 29 years old, almost 30.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h2><strong>Where did you grow up? </strong></h2>\r\n<p>I grew up all over the place between France, New-Zealand and Germany!</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h2><strong>What are you doing here in NYC and why did you move here? </strong></h2>\r\n<p>I was in New-York to launch the US branch of a company I created with Matthew called Vyking.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h2><strong>What do you think about </strong><strong>coliving</strong><strong>&nbsp;and what are your experiences here?</strong></h2>\r\n<p>I had a great time at Outpost, it was a great way to meet people from all over the world like Russia, Turkey and Malaysia.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h2><strong>What\'s been your best experience in the time you have stayed </strong><strong>with</strong><strong> Outpost? </strong></h2>\r\n<p>The last week I spent at Outpost was great as I really took the time to get to know people from Outpost at the big Halloween party they organised. I recommend this unique experience, if you want to have an easy going settlement in the big Apple Outpost is the solution!</p>\r\n</div>', '22255144_10159554837275515_431709023051508608_o.jpg', 1, '2018-01-07 06:00:00', NULL, 0, 0, 0),
(36, 'Come with a suitcase, leave with friends', 1, 'come-with-a-suitcase-leave-with-friends', 'reviews-by-the-customers/2017/4/24/come-with-a-suitcase-leave-with-friends', 'Come with a suitcase, leave with friends', 'Come with a suitcase, leave with friends', 'If you\'re willing to be a part of the community, you\'ll never feel alone', '<p>The Flatbush House is not a house, it\'s a home. I\'ve never once felt out of place. Everybody\'s really nice and the house stays clean too. I showed up with only a suitcase and i\'m happy I didn\'t bring more. This house has everything you would ever need. They even had hot sauce when I arrived.</p>', '<p>The Flatbush House is not a house, it\'s a home. I\'ve never once felt out of place. Everybody\'s really nice and the house stays clean too. I showed up with only a suitcase and i\'m happy I didn\'t bring more. This house has everything you would ever need. They even had hot sauce when I arrived. I\'ll never forget our impromptu dinners and conversations and always having someone to do something with. If you\'re willing to be a part of the community, you\'ll never feel alone.</p>', '3.png', 1, '2017-03-23 05:00:00', NULL, 0, 0, 0),
(39, 'Press Release: Downtown Brooklyn House', 1, 'press-release-downtown-brooklyn-house', 'outpost-blogpress-release-downtown-brooklyn-house', 'Press Release: Downtown Brooklyn House', 'Press Release: Downtown Brooklyn House', 'The picturesque, historic neighborhood of Boerum Hill is now home to the eighth Outpost Club house! ', '<p>The picturesque, historic neighborhood of Boerum Hill is now home to the eighth Outpost Club house! The recently renovated and exceedingly charming Downtown Brooklyn House is located in an.</p>', '<p>The picturesque, historic neighborhood of Boerum Hill is now home to the eighth Outpost Club house! The recently renovated and exceedingly charming Downtown Brooklyn House is located in an easygoing neighborhood with great access to trendy spots for food and drink, independent shops, and is incredibly located to provide the quick access to the best neighborhoods of Brooklyn and Manhattan.</p>\r\n<p>Outpost Club will continue its practice of solving the big city housing problems for transient workers, digital nomads, students, start-ups, and newcomers in general. Located just six minutes from the F and G trains, and ten minutes from the A train, the Downtown Brooklyn House is a gorgeous four-story brownstone with complete interior renovations from updated wooden floors, appliances, and living spaces to provide a warm, contemporary feel. The home has 14 rooms and multiple common areas including living rooms, kitchens, and coworking spaces.</p>\r\n<p><img title=\"Press Release: Downtown Brooklyn House (Image-1), outpost-club.com\" src=\"../files/uploads/blog/press-release-downtown-brooklyn-house/press-release-downtown-brooklyn-house-4-2.png\" alt=\"Press Release: Downtown Brooklyn House (Image-1)\" /></p>\r\n<p>All, of course, is completely move-in ready - new members must only arrive at the door with their suitcase. Everything you could think to ask for in a new home is provided for you at Outpost. You can enjoy evening meals with fellow members in a fully stocked kitchen boasting stainless steel appliances, tables large enough to seat eight people, and routinely restocked kitchen essentials and dish soap. Set up for a weekend binge in the (co)living room where Netflix is available on the large 55&rdquo; TV, and get to work in the coworking space where you can print, scan, and fax. If you ever find yourself in need of a little peace and quiet, or feel the opposite desire and want to host a huge barbecue, this house has the perfect scenic rooftop and spacious backyard outfitted with tables and chairs for whatever quiet moment or fun get-together you desire. There&rsquo;s even a pay-per-use laundry machine within the home!</p>\r\n<p><img title=\"Press Release: Downtown Brooklyn House (Image-2), outpost-club.com\" src=\"../files/uploads/blog/press-release-downtown-brooklyn-house/press-release-downtown-brooklyn-house-3-1.png\" alt=\"Press Release: Downtown Brooklyn House (Image-2)\" /></p>\r\n<p>All rooms in the Downtown Brooklyn House are private, and each room comes with memory foam mattresses, pillows, extension cords, shelving, hooks, bed linens, and towels. Some of these rooms have en suite bathrooms, although these and the common full bathrooms throughout the house come with constantly restocked toilet paper, shampoo, body wash, and hairdryers.</p>\r\n<p><img title=\"Press Release: Downtown Brooklyn House (Image-3), outpost-club.com\" src=\"../files/uploads/blog/press-release-downtown-brooklyn-house/press-release-downtown-brooklyn-house-2-1.png\" alt=\"Press Release: Downtown Brooklyn House (Image-3)\" /></p>\r\n<p><strong>Membership with Outpost Club is a flexible, month-to-month commitment that does not require extensive documents, large deposits, or guarantors, but the longer the commitment the better the price. Private rooms at the Downtown Brooklyn House start at $2290.</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><img title=\"Press Release: Downtown Brooklyn House (Image-4), outpost-club.com\" src=\"../files/uploads/blog/press-release-downtown-brooklyn-house/press-release-downtown-brooklyn-house-1-1.png\" alt=\"Press Release: Downtown Brooklyn House (Image-4)\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p><em>Outpost Club was founded in 2016 by a team who knows what it is like to move to new places and start from scratch. Built on the foundational belief that renting a room should be as easy as buying a cup of coffee, Outpost founders developed a process to make it incredibly easy to move to New York - no scams, hidden fees, startup costs, or massive security deposits. It&rsquo;s Outpost Club&rsquo;s mission to provide more than a place to live and work - move in with Outpost and you&rsquo;ll gain an instant community with opportunities to socialize, network, and grow, all in beautiful and convenient houses at affordable prices.</em></p>\r\n<h3>More houses in <a href=\"../rooms-for-rent-in-brooklyn\" target=\"_blank\">Brooklyn&nbsp;</a>by Outpost Club.</h3>', 'press-downtown.jpg', 1, '2018-07-23 05:00:00', NULL, 0, 0, 0),
(40, '#MemberMonday: Lee Schofield', 1, 'membermonday-lee-schofield', 'outpost-blogmember-monday-lee-schofield', '#MemberMonday: Lee Schofield', '#MemberMonday: Lee Schofield', 'This week we\'re highlighting a truly special member from East Bushwick whose talents span several disciplines, Lee Schofield! \r\n', '<p>Outpost Club Coliving is for everyone, and we have&nbsp;virtually every type of artist, designer, coder, writer, foodie, scholar, scientist, and creative. This week we\'re highlighting a truly special member from East Bushwick whose talents span&nbsp;several&nbsp;of those disciplines, Lee Schofield!&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Outpost Club Coliving is for everyone, and we have&nbsp;virtually every type of artist, designer, coder, writer, foodie, scholar, scientist, and creative. This week we\'re highlighting a truly special member from East Bushwick whose talents span&nbsp;several&nbsp;of those disciplines, Lee Schofield!&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img title=\"#MemberMonday: Lee Schofield (Image-1), outpost-club.com\" src=\"../files/uploads/blog/membermonday-lee-schofield/membermonday-lee-schofield-1.png\" alt=\"#MemberMonday: Lee Schofield (Image-1)\" /></p>\r\n<h4>Tell us a little bit about yourself</h4>\r\n<p>I&rsquo;m from Sydney, Australia, and back in Sydney I was working as an Insights &amp; Analytics Manager for an Influencer Marketing company, but have a particular passion for innovation and human-centric research (user experience / customer experience).&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>I love <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/leescho_bw/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">photography</a> and have a collection of about 12 cameras back in Oz, love everything to do with food and drinks (particularly wine!), so in my past time you&rsquo;ll probably find me on a photo walk, hitting up some galleries or finding a new joint to eat at.</p>\r\n<h4>What brought you here?</h4>\r\n<p>I&rsquo;ve been at Outpost for about 6 weeks, and decided to stay here because of a combination of convenience and to be surrounded by other interesting people transitioning into the city. I think it attracts a particular type of person - usually quite creative and nomadic types.</p>\r\n<p>I didn&rsquo;t know anyone in New York when I first arrived. It&rsquo;s a city with so much opportunity, full of people pursuing their dreams, and I wanted to be amongst that. Outpost seemed like the perfect way to transition into it and meet like minded people.</p>\r\n<h4>What\'s one thing you\'re going to miss the most when you leave Outpost?</h4>\r\n<p>The people, of course. I&rsquo;ve met some amazing people who will be friends for a long time to come.</p>\r\n<h4>Do you have a favorite spot in the city? or one place you want to explore more?</h4>\r\n<p>Don&rsquo;t make me choose! I&rsquo;ve been spending a lot of time exploring Brooklyn and I&rsquo;ve only scratched the surface. I need to take more time to actually explore Manhattan!&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h4>Are there any ways that coliving has helped you accomplish more of what you want to do in the city? or helped you find new passions or interests?</h4>\r\n<p>Coliving has definitely helped me find people that have similar hobbies to me, so it&rsquo;s meant I&rsquo;ve had friends to bounce ideas off, and go out on photography walks and all that. It&rsquo;s helped reignite a few old hobbies and interests too, like video.</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><strong>Recently, Lee has been collaborating with others in the Outpost community to launch an innovative video series on LinkedIn! Check her introductory video below with fellow member&nbsp;Jay Flores!</strong></p>\r\n<p><iframe src=\"//player.vimeo.com/video/279350138?title=0&amp;amp;byline=0\" width=\"100%\" height=\"400px\"></iframe></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>And if you want to chat more with the rest of Outpost Club&nbsp;request to join our&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/outpostclub/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Facebook group</a>,&nbsp;and don\'t forget to keep up with our <a href=\"../blog\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">blog</a>!</strong></p>', 'membermonday-lee-schofield.jpg', 1, '2018-07-29 05:00:00', NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(42, 'Outpost - quick overview', 1, 'outpost---quick-overview', 'outpost-blog/blog-outpost-club/2016/10/14/outpost-quick-overview', 'Outpost - quick overview', 'Outpost - quick overview', 'Outpost Club provides coliving spaces at affordable and flexible rates in New York City. When you become a member you will live in a community of like-minded individuals in a location that opens', '<p>Outpost Club provides coliving spaces at affordable and flexible rates in New York City. When you become a member you will live in a community of like-minded individuals in a location that opens.</p>', '<p><!--StartFragment--><strong>Outpost Club provides </strong>coliving<strong> spaces at affordable and flexible rates in New York City. When you become a member you will live in a community of like-minded individuals in a location that opens access to the endless opportunities to be found in New York City.</strong></p>\r\n<p>To make things as easy and practical as possible, we offer you a flexible solution for living that is move in ready Membership with us give you access to the communities of all our NYC locations around New York City, allowing you to network with people like you, find new opportunities,&nbsp;and learn new things.</p>\r\n<p>We enjoy to creating a fun atmosphere between all the great people visiting New York City. The Outpost Club residences are beautifully designed spaces with incredibly quick Wi-Fi, and right around the corner from a 24/7 Metro stop which will take you to Manhattan in a short time.</p>\r\n<p>We currently have 3 townhouses in NYC (all 20 - 30 minutes from Manhattan) and have already had many new startups, projects, jobs, skills, and friendships come out of them.</p>\r\n<h3>Please take a brief look on the typical residents of Outpost Club - we will become a perfect place to live with us if you are:&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>looking to learn new skills related to business, technologies or the creativity</li>\r\n<li>looking for new opportunities in business, technologies or the creativity</li>\r\n<li>looking to make new friends or connections in NYC</li>\r\n<li>looking for short-term housing of 1-6 months</li>\r\n<li>an early-stage developer and entrepreneur looking for investments, co-founders, feedback</li>\r\n<li>an IT developer</li>\r\n<li>a designer or artist who like to have a network of other specialities</li>\r\n<li>a digital nomad</li>\r\n<li>a freelancer, or someone who can work from home</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Please browse this website and let us know!&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<p>BASIC INFO:</p>\r\n<p>Prices: $850 - $1400 monthly rental inclusive</p>\r\n<p>No Security Payments</p>\r\n<p>Weekly and Monthly Events</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"../join-us\" rel=\"nofollow\">Apply</a>&nbsp;- 3 Minutes Application</p>\r\n<p>Terms: Month-to-month, 15 day cancellation notice. Bedrooms and common areas come furnished and Price includes utilities, high-speed internet, furniture, cleaning service, house events.</p>\r\n<p><!--EndFragment--></p>', 'outpost---quick-overview.jpg', 1, '2016-10-13 05:00:00', NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(43, 'Outpost Club Coliving Carving Party', 1, 'outpost-club-coliving-carving-party', 'outpost-blog/blog-outpost-club/2016/10/22/o', 'Outpost Club Coliving Carving Party', 'Outpost Club Coliving Carving Party', 'Outpost Club Coliving Carving Party', '<p>We invite our guests, clients, friends and their beloved ones to come to the Outpost Pumpkin Carving Party on Sunday the 23rd at 3 pm in our Flatbush House at Nostrand ave! Bring the bright ideas.</p>', '<p>We invite our guests, clients, friends and their beloved ones to come to the Outpost Pumpkin Carving Party on Sunday the 23rd at 3 pm in our Flatbush House at Nostrand ave!&nbsp;Bring the bright ideas on how to carve the most terrifying pumpkin!</p>\r\n<p>More to that we will celebrate 1 year of Outpost Club!</p>\r\n<p><img title=\"Outpost Club Coliving Carving Party (Image-1), outpost-club.com\" src=\"../files/uploads/blog/carving-party/outpost%2Bclub%2Bpumpkin%2Bparty.jpgoutpost%2Bclub%2Bpumpkin%2Bparty.jpeg\" alt=\"Outpost Club Coliving Carving Party (Image-1)\" /></p>', 'pumpkin_party.jpeg', 0, '2016-10-21 05:00:00', NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(44, 'Flatbush House Barbeque Party', 1, 'flatbush-house-barbeque-party', 'outpost-blog/blog-outpost-club/2016/10/29/flatbush-house-barbeque-party', 'Flatbush House Barbeque Party', 'Flatbush House Barbeque Party', 'Flatbush House Barbeque Party', '<p>Every one of us is coming to the New York wants to feel the spirit of the city and thoroughly enjoy it. We don\'t want to be a just a tourist on vacation that go to see Times Square, Central Park,.</p>', '<p>Every one of us is coming to the New York wants to feel the spirit of the city and thoroughly enjoy it. We don\'t want to be a just a tourist on vacation that go to see Times Square, Central Park&nbsp;and the Brooklyn Bridge. We want to be able to answer the question, \"How does it feel to live in that great city?\" Unfortunately, hotels will not help you feel like a city dweller, or help you understand how locals experience New York. Luckily, we provide a great solution: We have an excellent house where you can move in with incredible tenants in the middle of the Brooklyn.</p>\r\n<p>Our house has a backyard where we had a BBQ party last Sunday. Outdoor&nbsp;parties are treasured traditions in New York, as&nbsp;people&nbsp;enjoy spending time with friends, cracking open a beer, and meeting&nbsp;new people. We started a fire and grilled delicious burgers and sausages, and enjoyed the warm weather in our backyard. We had a little bar set up where our skilled barman created custom drinks &mdash; an advantage of having a private yard.&nbsp;Many of us never wanted the party to end,&nbsp;as we had so much fun. Take a look at the pictures we took during the party, and make sure to stop by next time. Hopefully, we will see you at the next party here with us.</p>\r\n<p>Text by Andriy Taranukha</p>\r\n<p>Photos by Daria Kalita</p>\r\n<p><img title=\"Flatbush House Barbeque Party (Image-1), outpost-club.com\" src=\"../files/uploads/blog/BARBEQUE/img-52.jpg\" alt=\"Flatbush House Barbeque Party (Image-1)\" /></p>\r\n<p><img title=\"Flatbush House Barbeque Party (Image-2), outpost-club.com\" src=\"../files/uploads/blog/BARBEQUE/img-40.jpg\" alt=\"Flatbush House Barbeque Party (Image-2)\" /></p>\r\n<p><img title=\"Flatbush House Barbeque Party (Image-3), outpost-club.com\" src=\"../files/uploads/blog/BARBEQUE/img-30.jpg\" alt=\"Flatbush House Barbeque Party (Image-3)\" /></p>\r\n<p><img title=\"Flatbush House Barbeque Party (Image-4), outpost-club.com\" src=\"../files/uploads/blog/BARBEQUE/img-36.jpg\" alt=\"Flatbush House Barbeque Party (Image-4)\" /></p>\r\n<p><img title=\"Flatbush House Barbeque Party (Image-5), outpost-club.com\" src=\"../files/uploads/blog/BARBEQUE/img-24.jpg\" alt=\"Flatbush House Barbeque Party (Image-5)\" /></p>\r\n<p><img title=\"Flatbush House Barbeque Party (Image-6), outpost-club.com\" src=\"../files/uploads/blog/BARBEQUE/img-45.jpg\" alt=\"Flatbush House Barbeque Party (Image-6)\" /></p>\r\n<p><img title=\"Flatbush House Barbeque Party (Image-7), outpost-club.com\" src=\"../files/uploads/blog/BARBEQUE/img-55.jpg\" alt=\"Flatbush House Barbeque Party (Image-7)\" /></p>\r\n<p><img title=\"Flatbush House Barbeque Party (Image-8), outpost-club.com\" src=\"../files/uploads/blog/BARBEQUE/img-32.jpg\" alt=\"Flatbush House Barbeque Party (Image-8)\" /></p>', 'img-52.jpg', 1, '2016-10-28 05:00:00', NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
