(55, 'Our Corporate Housing Program', 1, 'our-corporate-housing-program', 'outpost-blog/blog-outpost-club/2017/12/7/our-corporate-housing-programedit', 'Our Corporate Housing Program', 'Our Corporate Housing Program', 'With the addition of Outpost Club’s newest house, we’ve reached a tipping point in our expansion. Having all housing types of accommodations covered, Outpost C', '<p>With the addition of Outpost Club&rsquo;s newest house, we&rsquo;ve reached a tipping point in our expansion. Having all housing types of accommodations covered, Outpost Club is now offering it&rsquo;s coliving.</p>', '<p>With the addition of Outpost Club&rsquo;s newest house,&nbsp;we&rsquo;ve reached a tipping point in our expansion. Having all housing types of accommodations covered, Outpost Club is now offering it&rsquo;s coliving services directly to companies and organizations. In this article, we want to give you some insights into our corporate housing program.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Who&rsquo;s it for?&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<p>Outpost Club&rsquo;s Corporate Housing Program is designed for all companies or organizations wanting to provide housing for their members. Now every organization can interact directly with Outpost Club to help their members find move-in-ready and affordable housing in New York City.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Why we launched our Corporate Housing Program?&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<p>&ldquo;We are looking to provide companies, non profits and schools with safe and move in ready locations across Brooklyn, close to transportation and social life, so that moving to New York becomes an easy prosess&rdquo; &mdash; Said Jacob Shapiro, our NYC Account Manager&nbsp;</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<div>\r\n<p><img title=\"Our Corporate Housing Program (Image-1), outpost-club.com\" src=\"../files/uploads/blog/Our_Corporate_Housing_Program/FullSizeRender_2.jpg\" alt=\"Our Corporate Housing Program (Image-1)\" /></p>\r\n<p><img title=\"Our Corporate Housing Program (Image-2), outpost-club.com\" src=\"../files/uploads/blog/Our_Corporate_Housing_Program/IMG_0733.jpg\" alt=\"Our Corporate Housing Program (Image-2)\" /></p>\r\n<p><img title=\"Our Corporate Housing Program (Image-3), outpost-club.com\" src=\"../files/uploads/blog/Our_Corporate_Housing_Program/266AFB82-C73B-4D62-8F65-32DDB762C9C6.jpg\" alt=\"Our Corporate Housing Program (Image-3)\" /></p>\r\n<p><img title=\"Our Corporate Housing Program (Image-4), outpost-club.com\" src=\"../files/uploads/blog/Our_Corporate_Housing_Program/IMG_9910.jpg\" alt=\"Our Corporate Housing Program (Image-4)\" /></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Interested?&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<p>Organizations looking for housing can now send their members to our <a href=\"../corporate-housing\">Corporate Housing page</a>, after contacting us to set up an agreement. For more information, feel free to reach out!&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Contact: Info@outpost-club.com</p>', 'FullSizeRender_2.jpg', 1, '2017-12-06 06:00:00', NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(56, 'Three Resources for Promotion in Social Networks in 2017', 1, 'three-resources-for-promotion-in-social-networks-in-2017', '', 'Three Resources for Promotion in Social Networks in 2017', 'Three Resources for Promotion in Social Networks in 2017', 'While the science of promotion in Social Networks is forming, here at Outpost we are always trying to find new ways of acquiring skills for promotion', '<p>While the science of promotion in Social Networks is forming, here at Outpost we are always trying to find new ways of acquiring skills for promotion. Here are some useful tips and resources for your consideration.</p>', '<p>While the science of promotion in Social Networks is forming, here at Outpost we are always trying to find new ways of acquiring skills for promotion. Here are some useful tips and resources for your consideration.</p>\r\n<p>1) First, there are a number of free or paid courses. One of the best in my point of view is Coursera <strong>UC Davis course on SEO and Social Media&nbsp;</strong>which in 4 weeks can teach you both basics and advanced techniques of Search Engine Optimization (SEO) with useful excel files you can use as well as promoting a business in social media from content to building of the useful connections with Opinion Leaders. Slow but quality organic growth.</p>\r\n<p>2) Skip the line includes different paid services to promote a content via Facebook. An interesting article by <strong>MIT Technology Review&nbsp;</strong>shows that paid advertisement at Facebook sometimes could be pretty questionable. There are as well a number of services mentioned in the article like MammothSocials.com or Boostlikes.com. As article <strong>Secret Strategies Revealed: Reaching 500k Facebook Likes&nbsp;</strong>suggests ways of exchanging Likes, buying Legitimate likes and working with Influencers.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>3) Influencers are the new preachers in the world of Marketing. Interesting discovery were special services like <strong>Klout, Tapinfluence, Peerindex</strong>. There you can target your resources onto really impactful Influencers, track the progress and grow the backlink profile.</p>\r\n<p>In any way, the best way to say Thank You to the business - is for the really happy customers to leave the review. We are very welcoming our existing, past and future guests to share their quick STARS review with a couple of words on the <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/outpostclubNY/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Outpost Club Facebook Page</a>, Google Maps review for Bedford House or Flatbush House&nbsp;or leave your comments in our <a href=\"../blog\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Blog</a>.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Share your thoughts as comments here about Social Media Promotion in today\'s\' world?</strong></p>', 'three-resources-for-promotion-in-social-networks.jpeg', 0, '2017-02-22 06:00:00', NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(396, 'Best Coffee Shops for Working From \'Home\' in NYC', 1, 'best-coffee-shops-for-working-from-home-in-nyc', '', 'Best Coffee Shops for Working From \'Home\' in NYC | Outpost Club blog', 'Best Coffee Shops for Working From \'Home\' in NYC', 'New York has bountiful cozy coffee shops and cafes serving up ambiance and the caffeine you need to get work done', '<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Whether you&rsquo;re a college student on the hunt for a latte, or have a full-time remote job and simply want to escape the confines of your apartment, New York has bountiful cozy coffee shops and cafes serving up ambiance and the caffeine you need to get work done. From Bushwick to SoHo, there are quaint spaces perfect for hammering out your to-do list.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Whether you&rsquo;re a college student on the hunt for a latte, or have a full-time remote job and simply want to escape the confines of your apartment, New York has bountiful cozy coffee shops and cafes serving up ambiance and the caffeine you need to get work done. From Bushwick to SoHo, there are quaint spaces perfect for hammering out your to-do list.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://www.devocion.com/pages/devocion-cafe-williamsburg-brooklyn-ny\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Devocion</a> - Williamsburg</strong></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This roomy Williamsburg spot offers house-roasted coffee, exposed brick and natural light that streams in from their overhead skylight.</span></p>\r\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://www.sweetleafcoffee.com/pages/greenpoint\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Sweetleaf</a> - Greenpoint</strong></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">For those that love a cozy living room, but still want to get out of their apartment, Sweetleaf serves up a homey atmosphere alongside delicious specialty coffees, like their Rocket Fuel, which has maple for a delicious hint of sweetness. During the day you can order a small bite as well, like smoked salmon or a savory vegan sandwich.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://www.yelp.com/biz/corto-brooklyn\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Corto</a> - Bed-Stuy</strong></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">With free Wi-Fi, a stunning backyard and delicious snacks like focaccia sandwiches, this coffee house is an ideal place to post up and get work over a light meal and latte.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://littleskips.nyc/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Little Skips</a> - Bushwick&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If you prefer a lively atmosphere and working alongside others (without being in the office, of course), this Bushwick hotspot is almost always bustling. Grab one of their signature sandwiches, a coffee, and snag a table while you can.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><strong><a href=\"http://www.ludlowcoffeesupply.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Ludlow Coffee Supply</a> - Lower East Side</strong></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">With plenty of cozy seating and a retro-meets-modern aesthetic, this trendy downtown locale is typically teeming with WFH Manhattanites. Grab a matcha latte, or once evening comes, you can even sip on a glass of red wine as you work.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://www.housingworks.org/locations/bookstore-cafe\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Housing Works Bookstore Cafe</a> - SoHo</strong></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">You can grab a coffee for a good cause at Housing Works, which is volunteer-run and donates proceeds to those affected by HIV/AIDs and homelessness.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://www.freeholdbrooklyn.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Freehold</a> - Williamsburg</strong></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">You might have made it to Freehold on a Saturday night for dancing and cocktails, but during the day this spacious Brooklyn spot is transformed into a coffee house. In addition to their traditional coffees and teas, Freehold also serves warm broth from Springbone Kitchen&mdash;the perfect pick-me-up for a wintery day spent working from your laptop.</span></p>\r\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://varietycoffeeroasters.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Variety Coffee</a> - Chelsea, Bushwick, Greenpoint</strong></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">With locations dotted over Manhattan and Brooklyn, head to Variety Coffee for a reliable cup of joe, free Wi-Fi and a cozy atmosphere ideal for sending emails and Slacks.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Finding the appropriate coffee shop for the work can be challenging. Dorms and coffee shops may be excessively loud when business calls or meetings call for full silence. We advise you to combine your work at home and outside the home as a consequence. We\'ve already talked about the options for working away from home. What about opportunities for working from home? <a href=\"../student-housing-nyc\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Student apartments</a> are ideal for working from home. The Outpost club offers a quiet and safe environment.</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Photo by <a href=\"https://unsplash.com/@thecreative_exchange?utm_source=unsplash&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_content=creditCopyText\">The Creative Exchange</a> on <a href=\"https://unsplash.com/s/photos/coffee-shop?utm_source=unsplash&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_content=creditCopyText\">Unsplash</a> </span></p>', 'the-creative-exchange-d1ngW7SNehM-unsplash.jpg', 1, '2021-11-16 06:00:00', '2022-11-01 07:20:45', NULL, 0, 0);
