(172, 'Review from Mohamed about The Clark House', 2, 'review-from-mohamed-about-the-clark-house', '', 'Mohamed / The Clark House', 'Review from Mohamed about The Clark House', 'What Mohamed thinks about The Clark House - customer review about Outpost Club', '', '<p>Organized around a community, this apartment is part of the OutPost Club. Thus, it is led by a house leader and there will be at least 4 other people usually in the apartment to chill with and talk to. Your roommates are really the luck of the draw! There will be several social events to attend. Laundry service is so close, it\'s basically an amenity. Be sure to check it out! :)</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a style=\"color: #c01e32;\" href=\"../the-clark-house\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferer\">Explore The Clark House</a></p>', 'mohamed.png', 1, '2018-12-04 06:00:00', '2022-08-05 14:14:52', 0, 0, 0),
(168, 'Where to Celebrate Repeal Day in New York', 1, 'where-to-celebrate-repeal-day-in-new-york', '', 'Where to Celebrate Repeal Day in New York', 'Where to Celebrate Repeal Day in New York', 'Dec. 5 is the anniversary of the end of Prohibition in the United States. Here\'s where to celebrate. ', '<p>Dec. 5 is the anniversary of the end of Prohibition in the United States. Here\'s where to celebrate.&nbsp;</p>', '<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The passage of the 18th Amendment in 1919 marked the official start of Prohibition in the United States, but that didn&rsquo;t keep New Yorkers from drinking. The city was the epicenter of the resistance to the Prohibition movement, and the market for alcohol spawned a huge amount of speakeasies and nightclubs that a lasting impact on New York City culture. </span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The 18th Amendment isn&rsquo;t what we&rsquo;re celebrating nearly 100 years later, though. The 21st Amendment repealed prohibition on Dec. 5, 1933, and at bars around the U.S. you can still find celebrations every year harkening back to the days when liquor didn&rsquo;t flow freely and downing drinks could have more drastic consequences than a headache the next morning. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Here are four Repeal Day events to check out next week: </span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Remy Repeal Day at The Back Room Speakeasy</strong></p>\r\n<p>Enjoy live swing with Svetlana &amp; The Delancey Five at a secret back-room speakeasy sponsored by Remy Martin. Register to attend ahead of time (tickets are free) to access the location of the Dec. 3 event and the entry password. Prohibition-themed cocktails will be available. Dress in your Prohibition-era best! Doors open at 7:30 p.m.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Repeal Day at The Boogie Woogie Room</strong></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">On Dec. 5 from 7p.m.-10 p.m., a secret entrance will lead you into the Boogie Woogie Room&rsquo;s Repeal Day party, with live music, burlesque, champagne fountains and bathtubs of cocktails (plus specialty cocktails by Redemption Rye). Your $19.33 ticket includes access to the party, one token redeemable for a $0.25 cocktail and a welcome drink.</span></p>\r\n<p><em><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The Boogie Woogie Room at Mondrian Park Ave., 444 Park Ave. South, Manhattan</span></em></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Repeal Day at Taproom No. 307</strong><strong><br /></strong></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">21st Amendment Brewery is doing at tap takeover at Taproom No. 307 between 7 p.m. and midnight. Specialty cocktails featuring Brooklyn-owned Widow Jane whiskey will also be available. &nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><em><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Taproom No. 307, 307 3rd Ave., Manhattan</span></em></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>3rd-Annual Repeal Day Party </strong></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Join the Repeal Society on Dec. 5 between 8 p.m.-midnight for their third-annual Repeal Day Party. This year&rsquo;s party will take place at the Shanty at the New York Distilling Co. and feature live music from Mike Davis and The New Wonders and burlesque by Margo Mayhem, Tansy and Dandy Dillinger. Drink specials are available all night. </span></p>\r\n<p><em><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">New York Distilling Co., 79 Richardson Street, Williamsburg</span></em></p>\r\n<p><br /><br /></p>', 'StockSnap_F6IZQA98OZ-min.jpg', 1, '2018-11-29 06:00:00', NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(169, 'Review from Silja about The Bushwick House', 2, 'review-from-silja-about-the-bushwick-house', '', 'Silja / The Bushwick House', 'Review from Silja about The Bushwick House', 'What Silja thinks about The Bushwick House - customer review about Outpost Club', '', '<p>Staying at the Bushwick House was an amazing experience. The people are so nice, the facilites were great and clean, and having two subway lines nearby was very convenient. I definitely recommend it, especially if you\'re travelling alone or don\'t know many people, because there\'s always someone around to chat and laugh with!</p>', 'silja.png', 1, '2018-11-30 06:00:00', NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(173, 'Review from Colleen about The Flatbush House', 2, 'review-from-colleen-about-the-flatbush-house', '', 'Colleen / The Flatbush House', 'Review from Colleen about The Flatbush House', 'What Colleen thinks about The Flatbush House - customer review about Outpost Club', '', '<p>Our 18-yr-old son, Lev, has been so grateful for the chance to live and study in New York staying at Valentin\'s place. The location is super-convenient to subway transit, with easy access to stores, laundry, restaurants, and within walking distance of parks. The group staying at the apartment has always been interesting, lively and sociable. It\'s been a great experience.</p>', 'colleen.png', 1, '2018-11-30 06:00:00', NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(174, 'Review from Victor about The Bed-Stuy House', 2, 'review-from-victor-about-the-bed-stuy-house', '', 'Victor / The Bed-Stuy House', 'Review from Victor about The Bed-Stuy House', 'What Victor thinks about The Bed-Stuy House - customer review about Outpost Club', '', '<p>The Outpost Club is the best thing that ever happened to me since I got to New York, I was feeling so lonely but here I found not just friends but family, and this an experience I&rsquo;ll never forget. Thanks!</p>', 'victor.png', 1, '2018-11-30 06:00:00', NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(175, 'Review from Michele about The Bushwick House', 2, 'review-from-michele-about-the-bushwick-house', '', 'Michele / The Bushwick House', 'Review from Michele about The Bushwick House', 'What Michele thinks about The Bushwick House - customer review about Outpost Club', '', '<p>Great place, great hosts!</p>', 'michele.png', 1, '2018-11-30 06:00:00', NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(176, 'Review from Brooke about The Lafayette House', 2, 'review-from-brooke-about-the-lafayette-house', '', 'Brooke / The Lafayette House', 'Review from Brooke about The Lafayette House', 'What Brooke thinks about The Lafayette House - customer review about Outpost Club', '', '<p>Staying with outpost is an experience I will never forget. The houses are everything you need but what is truly special is the sense of community fostered here. It is unlike other places I have stayed. I have had amazing experiences and made lifelong friends, I would go back again in a second.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a style=\"color: #c01e32;\" href=\"../the-lafayette-house\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferer\">Explore The Lafayette House</a></p>', 'brooke.png', 1, '2018-12-04 06:00:00', '2022-08-05 14:12:33', 0, 0, 0),
(177, 'Review from Eduardo about The Greenpoint House', 2, 'review-from-eduardo-about-the-greenpoint-house', '', 'Eduardo / The Greenpoint House', 'Review from Eduardo about The Greenpoint House', 'What Eduardo thinks about The Greenpoint House - customer review about Outpost Club', '', '<p>Looking for a place to stay for an extended, non-permanent time? Look no further! From the decor, to check in, to the amazing people who live here it was such an amazing experience. So honored to say I became best friends with the majority of the people in not just my own house, but others as well. An amazing experience!</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a style=\"color: #c01e32;\" href=\"../the-greenpoint-house\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferer\">Explore The Greenpoint House</a></p>', 'eduardo.png', 1, '2018-12-04 06:00:00', '2022-08-05 14:07:25', 0, 0, 0),
