(102, 253, 102, 'the-bed-stuy-house', 'the-bedstuy-house', 'The Bed-Stuy House', 'The Bed-Stuy House (NY 11221) | Outpost Club', 'We worked with interior designers to make The Bed-Stuy House comfortable in every room. ✓ Fully furnished ✓ Security ✓ Gas ✓ Electricity ✓ Water ✓ Wi-Fi ✓ Cleaning and maintenance', 'The Bed-Stuy House | Outpost Club', '<p>Bedford-Stuyvesant, Brooklyn</p>\r\n<p>Private rooms from $1670</p>', '<h1 class=\"h1\">The Bed-Stuy House</h1>\r\n<h4>A spacious home in the lively Bed-Stuy neighborhood</h4>', '<div>\r\n<p>The newly renovated Bed-Stuy House is located &mdash; you guessed it &mdash; in the heart of the Bedford-Stuyvesant neighborhood in Brooklyn. Bed-Stuy is rich in history, culture and community, and you&rsquo;ll have the opportunity to get to know people from every corner of the world, whether you&rsquo;re hanging out with your coliving housemates or visiting the corner bodega. Bed-Stuy is also home to a strong community of New Yorkers and a diverse range of restaurants and other local businesses, making it a blast to get to know and love.</p>\r\n<p><strong>The main draw</strong>: Every bedroom at the Bed-Stuy house has a private en-suite bathroom &mdash; so you&rsquo;ll literally never have to wait.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Perfect for you if:</strong> You want a spacious bedroom with plenty of room to relax in privacy when you need a break from the hustle and bustle of New York living.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Our suggestion:</strong> Walk just a couple blocks west and find yourself in Herbert Von King Park, a vibrant community green space that&rsquo;ll make you feel right at home.</p>\r\n</div>', 5, '', 'bed-stuy-main.jpg', 'bed-stuy-main.jpg', '', 290, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'The Bed-Stuy House', 0, 0, 'a:8:{i:8;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"title\";s:20:\"Throughout the house\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:699:\"<p>{throughout}</p>\r\n<table class=\"table v2\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<th>12+ Months</th>\r\n<th>5-11 Months</th>\r\n<th>1-4 Months</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Executive + Bath (Extra Large)</th>\r\n<td>$1890</td>\r\n<td>$1970</td>\r\n<td>$2570</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Executive + Bath</th>\r\n<td>$1720</td>\r\n<td>$1800</td>\r\n<td>$2400</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Executive + Bath (Small)</th>\r\n<td>$1670</td>\r\n<td>$1750</td>\r\n<td>$2350</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"5\">\r\n<p>*Prices above do not include $149/month/person utilities allowance fee</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div class=\"center\"><a class=\"button2 red\" href=\"online-questionnaire\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Apply for free</a></div>\";}i:1;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:12:\"The Bedrooms\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:4:\"body\";s:505:\"<p>All of the bedrooms in the Bed-Stuy House are private and feature en-suite bathrooms and full-sized beds, while most have desks and closets. Bedding is available for an additional fee. One of our favorite parts of the Bed-Stuy House? The bedrooms are gigantic compared to most New York City apartments, and some even include fireplaces for the ultimate cozy vibe.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Amenities:</strong> full-size memory-foam mattresses, shelving, hooks and closets/organizational tools.</li>\r\n</ul>\";s:6:\"images\";a:11:{i:0;s:22:\"bed-stuy-bedroom-1.jpg\";i:1;s:23:\"bed-stuy-bedroom-10.jpg\";i:2;s:23:\"bed-stuy-bedroom-11.jpg\";i:3;s:22:\"bed-stuy-bedroom-7.jpg\";i:4;s:22:\"bed-stuy-bedroom-6.jpg\";i:5;s:22:\"bed-stuy-bedroom-5.jpg\";i:6;s:22:\"bed-stuy-bedroom-4.jpg\";i:7;s:22:\"bed-stuy-bedroom-9.jpg\";i:8;s:22:\"bed-stuy-bedroom-3.jpg\";i:9;s:22:\"bed-stuy-bedroom-2.jpg\";i:10;s:22:\"bed-stuy-bedroom-8.jpg\";}}i:3;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:20:\"The (Co)Living Rooms\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:4:\"body\";s:362:\"<p>The common living rooms in each unit of the Bed-Stuy House&nbsp;are&nbsp;where members can go to relax, work and hang out! One unit includes a spacious private lounge equipped with everything from&nbsp;couches to games to a large flat-screen TV.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Security::</strong> 24/7 security in common areas</li>\r\n<li>Google Chromecast.</li>\r\n</ul>\";s:6:\"images\";a:3:{i:0;s:28:\"bed-stuy-coliving-room-1.jpg\";i:1;s:28:\"bed-stuy-coliving-room-3.jpg\";i:2;s:28:\"bed-stuy-coliving-room-2.jpg\";}}i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:24:\"The Kitchens/Dining Room\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:560:\"<p>In these units, the kitchen and dining room are the first rooms you enter, located on the bottom floor of each unit. These open spaces are used for cooking up dinner with friends and relaxing in the evening over a glass of wine.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Amenities</strong> include electric stoves, stainless-steel fridges, microwaves, large sinks, coffee makers, blenders, plenty of cabinets, cookware, tableware, cutting boards and anything else you would need in a kitchen.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Security</strong>: 24/7 security in all common areas.</li>\r\n</ul>\";s:6:\"images\";a:5:{i:0;s:22:\"bed-stuy-kitchen-3.jpg\";i:1;s:22:\"bed-stuy-kitchen-2.jpg\";i:2;s:22:\"bed-stuy-kitchen-4.jpg\";i:3;s:22:\"bed-stuy-kitchen-5.jpg\";i:4;s:22:\"bed-stuy-kitchen-1.jpg\";}}i:5;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:13:\"The bathrooms\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:412:\"<p>Every unit in the Bed-Stuy House is equipped with enough shared bathrooms that you can be sure you&rsquo;ll never have to wait.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Also included</strong>: toilet paper, hand soap and small garbage bags, which will never be empty!</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h6 class=\"h5\">Laundry room</h6>\r\n<p>The building also has a washer and dryer, so you can do all your laundry in the comfort of your own home.</p>\";s:6:\"images\";a:7:{i:0;s:23:\"bed-stuy-bathroom-8.jpg\";i:1;s:23:\"bed-stuy-bathroom-7.jpg\";i:2;s:23:\"bed-stuy-bathroom-5.jpg\";i:3;s:23:\"bed-stuy-bathroom-1.jpg\";i:4;s:23:\"bed-stuy-bathroom-2.jpg\";i:5;s:23:\"bed-stuy-bathroom-6.jpg\";i:6;s:23:\"bed-stuy-bathroom-3.jpg\";}}i:9;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"title\";s:20:\"PERKS AND BENEFITS: \";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:645:\"<div class=\"fx ch3 w perc_advantages\">\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Fast, reliable WiFi</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Regular professional cleaning</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Furnished interiors</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">In-unit laundry</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Keyless entry</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Spacious bedrooms</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Community events</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Dedicated community manager</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Updated appliances</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Dedicated maintenance team</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\";}i:10;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"title\";s:6:\"Prices\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:857:\"<table class=\"table v2\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<th>12+ Months</th>\r\n<th>5-11 Months</th>\r\n<th>1-4 Months</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Executive + Bath (Extra Large)</th>\r\n<td>$1890</td>\r\n<td>$1970</td>\r\n<td>$2570</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Executive + Bath</th>\r\n<td>$1720</td>\r\n<td>$1800</td>\r\n<td>$2400</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Executive + Bath (Small)</th>\r\n<td>$1670</td>\r\n<td>$1750</td>\r\n<td>$2350</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"5\">\r\n<p>*Prices above do not include $149/month/person utilities allowance fee</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div class=\"center\"><a class=\"button2 red\" href=\"online-questionnaire\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Apply for free</a></div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Availability: Year-round / Minimum stay of 1 month / Month-to-month payment options available / Minimum age 18</strong></p>\";}i:11;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:30:\"Welcome to Bed-Stuy, Brooklyn.\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:4:\"body\";s:1079:\"<div>\r\n<p>Walk off the train and into this historic Brooklyn neighborhood that feels like home with its quaint, brownstone-lined streets and vibrant culture. Immerse yourself in the community and you&rsquo;ll find unique locally owned shops, neighbors who are always up for a good conversation, and a rich history worth honoring. The neighborhood features the lively Herbert Von King park, trendy coffee shops like Brooklyn Blend and eclectic cuisine ranging from Caribbean to Japanese. You can explore surrounding neighborhoods like Clinton Hill and Williamsburg by foot, or hop on the subway and be in Manhattan in 30 minutes.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h6 class=\"h5\">Location</h6>\r\n<p>The closest subway station is the Delancey Street strop, served by the M and J train and is only a 10-minute walk away. You can reach the Lower East Side in 30 minutes and Midtown Manhattan in 45 minutes, or easily explore Downtown Brooklyn in 15 minutes.</p>\r\n<p>The neighborhood features Herbert Von King Park, trendy coffee shops and eclectic cuisine ranging from Cuban to Japanese.</p>\r\n</div>\";s:6:\"images\";a:4:{i:0;s:56:\"aee22cb703e77c3c63e13bf273a93b2f-rimg-w720-h478-gmir.jpg\";i:1;s:24:\"bed-stuy_corcoran_08.jpg\";i:2;s:32:\"bed-stuy-brooklyn-new-york-4.jpg\";i:3;s:58:\"Fulton-street-brooklyn-bedford-stuyvesant-nyc-new-york.jpg\";}}}', '', 'a:5:{i:0;s:3:\"181\";i:1;s:3:\"215\";i:2;s:3:\"214\";i:3;s:3:\"186\";i:4;s:3:\"184\";}', '', '<div class=\"txt\">\r\n<h1 class=\"center\">The Bed-Stuy House Move-In Guide</h1>\r\n<h2><em><strong>Welcome to Outpost Club! This is a guide to make your move in successful. We&rsquo;ve done this many times before so we know the drill! To start, here is your address: 780 Lafayette Avenue, Brooklyn, NY, 11221</strong></em></h2>\r\n<hr class=\"hr\" />\r\n<h3>House Leader</h3>\r\n<p>First, get to know your house leader. They will be your point of contact for questions and concerns.</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"fx w vc ch2\">\r\n<div><img id=\"cldfkgliklaggnopdgnepabenoiiopbi\" style=\"display: block; top: 787px; left: 1089px; z-index: 1999; position: absolute; cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; background-image: none; border: none; opacity: 1; max-width: 24px; max-height: 24px; transition: all 50ms ease 0s;\" src=\"chrome-extension://cldfkgliklaggnopdgnepabenoiiopbi/ptlite-icon_32.png\" alt=\"\" /><img style=\"width: 100%;\" src=\"../files/uploads/august_lock.gif\" alt=\"\" />\r\n<p>How to use an August Lock</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h3>Getting in the building</h3>\r\n<p>All interior doors are locked with an August Lock. An August Lock is an electronic lock that uses an application called <strong><a class=\"green\" href=\"http://august.com/\" target=\"_blank\">August</a></strong>&nbsp;that you can use to unlock it. Find it in the app store, create an account, and ask your house leader to give you access.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>Wifi</h3>\r\n<p>As always, you need wifi. The wifi name is Outpost (or some variation of that) and the password is befreenyc (all lower case).</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>ID</h3>\r\n<p>For our records, we need a picture of your Photo ID. The house leader will take a picture of it</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>Communication with Other Residents</h3>\r\n<p>We use facebook messenger to communicate, so the house leader will need to add you to the group. If you don&rsquo;t have a facebook, please continually check in with the house leader to see if there is important house news you need to know.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>See the House</h3>\r\n<p>The house leader will show you your room (if they haven&rsquo;t already). Note your bed number, which can be found on your bed frame. Take a look at the house with the house leader. If you would like to lock away your valuables, use the lockers in the basement. Outpost Club is not responsible for the safety of your valuables and we do not provide locks, just lockers.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>Kitchen</h3>\r\n<p>You&rsquo;ll need a section of the fridge, which is partition by area so that everyone has equal access. If you open the fridge, you&rsquo;ll see each section has a letter and a number corresponding with your bed. Use this area of the fridge for your items, and talk to others in the house if you need more space. This goes for the cabinets as well: find your section, which will be labeled by your bed number.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>Events</h3>\r\n<p>The Outpost Club will also be holding events at your place and at all the Outpost Club locations, so make sure to ask the house leader about any upcoming events. Additionally we have a facebook group for all Outpost Club members in New York. This group has announcement about events, opportunities in New York, general announcements, and more good stuff.&nbsp;<strong><a class=\"green\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/outpostclub/\" target=\"_blank\">You can request to join that group here</a></strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>Cleanliness</h3>\r\n<p>The common spaces of the house are used by a lot of people so please keep them clean! There are some easy ways to think about cleanliness at Outpost Club:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Leave rooms in the condition that you found them&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Clean up after yourself</li>\r\n<li>Do not leave your personal stuff out in common areas if you are not going to return immediately</li>\r\n<li>When it\'s your turn to contribute, contribute! Check the cleaning boards for your day of resposibilities, and if your name is not there&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Additionally, the notes around the house are there to reduce confusion and make the community run smoothly, so follow the notes!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;Extensions</p>\r\n<p>Additionally, we happy to have our members stay longer, however we can\'t extend you stay if we don\'t know about your extension! As soon as you are aware of the need to extend your stay, let us know by emailing bookings@outpost-club.com.&nbsp;<strong>If you have not committed to an extension, your bed can be reserved by anyone admitted to Outpost Club.</strong></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"center\"><a class=\"button2\" href=\"current-members\">Return to Current Members Page</a></div>\r\n<hr class=\"hr\" />', 2, '40.69082275', '-73.94161214', 498, '', '2022-08-22 15:07:30'),
