(163, 0, NULL, 'member-benefits', '', 'Member Benefits', 'Member Benefits', 'As an Outpost Club member, you have access to exclusive deals around the city and around the world. Explore the benefits of being an Outpost Club member below!', 'Member Benefits', '', '', '<div class=\"txt\">\r\n<div>\r\n<h1 class=\"h1 center\">Member Benefits</h1>\r\n<p class=\"center\">As an Outpost Club member, you have access to exclusive deals around the city and around the world. Explore the benefits of being an Outpost Club member below!</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"fx w ch300px vc\">\r\n<div class=\"img w300px\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/benefits1.png\" alt=\"BKLYN commons\" width=\"\" height=\"\" /></div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h3 class=\"h6\">BKLYN commons</h3>\r\n<p>Outpost Club is excited to provide out members with a great deal from our partners and friends over at BKLYN Commons. BKYLN Commons is a family-owned and operated coworking space.</p>\r\n<p>As an Outpost Club member, you have the ability to become a member at BKLYN Commons with incredible discounts.<strong> BKLYN Commons is offering Outpost members 50%&nbsp;off Open Desk Memberships, and 15% off office space and dedicated desk rental rates!&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<hr class=\"hr\" />\r\n<div class=\"fx w  ch300px vc \">\r\n<div class=\"img w300px\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/hellorented.png\" alt=\"hellorented\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h3 class=\"h6\">hellorented</h3>\r\n<p>Outpost Club\'s partners over at HelloRented have a great product that can save all our members a lot of money. HelloRented wants to answer one question: what if you didn\'t need to pay your security deposit? With HelloRented, you do need to! For a small monthly fee, HelloRented will fund your security deposit for you. This allows all our members to use their own money, instead of having it sit idle in some bank account. Ask our Outpost Club team about this offer</p>\r\n<div class=\"center\"><a class=\"button2 center\" href=\"mailto:bookings@outpost-club.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Ask us about hellorented</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<hr class=\"hr\" />\r\n<div class=\"fx w ch2 m0\">\r\n<div>\r\n<h3 class=\"h6\"><a class=\"green\" href=\"https://www.swissescape.co/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Swiss Escape</a></h3>\r\n<p>Swiss Escape is a coliving and coworking space in the Alps in Switzerland. It is conveniently located in the heart of the village, a few minutes walking distance from the ski lifts, shops, restaurants and sport facilities. All accommodation and working facilities are included in the price. They welcome guests for a minimum stay of one week, and up to three months. Explore their offerings at <a class=\"green\" href=\"https://www.swissescape.co/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://www.swissescape.co/&nbsp;</a></p>\r\n<p>They have one option for their discount:Discount:</p>\r\n<ul dir=\"ltr\">\r\n<li>10% off of all stays at Swiss Escape</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Use the code OUTPOSTCLUB25 at checkout to receive the discount!</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"img_slider benef\">\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/swiss/swiss1.jpg\" alt=\"swissescape\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/swiss/swiss2.jpg\" alt=\"swissescape\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/swiss/swiss3.jpg\" alt=\"swissescape\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/swiss/swiss4.jpg\" alt=\"swissescape\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/swiss/swiss5.jpg\" alt=\"swissescape\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/swiss/swiss6.jpg\" alt=\"swissescape\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/swiss/swiss7.jpg\" alt=\"swissescape\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/swiss/swiss8.jpg\" alt=\"swissescape\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/swiss/swiss9.jpg\" alt=\"swissescape\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/swiss/swiss10.jpg\" alt=\"swissescape\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<hr class=\"hr\" />\r\n<div class=\"fx w ch2 m0\">\r\n<div>\r\n<h3 class=\"h6\"><a class=\"green\" href=\"http://www.mokrinhouse.com/about-us/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Mokrin House</a></h3>\r\n<p>Mokrin House is a coworking and coliving space located in the north of Serbia. It is a modern and urban spot in the rural surrounding. Mokrin House is a perfect place for freelancers, entrepreneurs and digital nomads, who are looking to getaway from the big cities and enjoy living and working in the countryside, for 2 weeks, 2 months or 2 years.</p>\r\n<p>They will take full care of you, providing 3 yummy, homemade, healthy meals per day, a big desk for you to work on and comfortable bed for the best sleep you will have in a long time. In their &nbsp;free time and after work hours they love to drink good coffee, organize workshops, educational seminars, cooking classes, movie nights and many random activities. Explore their offerings at <a class=\"green\" href=\"http://www.mokrinhouse.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://www.mokrinhouse.com/</a></p>\r\n<p>As an Outpost Club member, you get the exclusive discount of:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>10% discount on the daily price</li>\r\n<li>18% discount on the weekly or longer stay</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Use the code OUTPOSTCLUB25 at checkout to receive the discount!</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div class=\"img_slider benef\">\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/morkin/morkin1.jpg\" alt=\"mokrinhouse\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/morkin/morkin2.jpg\" alt=\"mokrinhouse\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/morkin/morkin3.jpg\" alt=\"mokrinhouse\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/morkin/morkin4.jpg\" alt=\"mokrinhouse\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/morkin/morkin5.jpg\" alt=\"mokrinhouse\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/morkin/morkin6.JPG\" alt=\"mokrinhouse\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/morkin/morkin7.jpg\" alt=\"mokrinhouse\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/morkin/morkin8.jpg\" alt=\"mokrinhouse\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/morkin/morkin9.jpg\" alt=\"mokrinhouse\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/morkin/morkin10.jpg\" alt=\"mokrinhouse\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/morkin/morkin11.jpg\" alt=\"mokrinhouse\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/morkin/morkin12.jpg\" alt=\"mokrinhouse\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/morkin/morkin13.jpg\" alt=\"mokrinhouse\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<hr class=\"hr\" />\r\n<div class=\"fx w ch2 m0\">\r\n<div>\r\n<h3 class=\"h6\"><a class=\"green\" href=\"https://www.sun-desk.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">SunDesk</a></h3>\r\n<p>Outpost Club has partnered with SunDesk! SunDesk has been gracious enough to offer our members to become their guests at a discounted price. SunDesk is a coliving and coworking space in Morocco! Their beautifully designed spaces are the perfect getaway where you can also remain productive. Located in the town of Taghazout, there are a number of restaurants to try out wholesome Moroccan dishes. If you like cooking, you&rsquo;re also welcome to prepare your own meals in our office kitchen. When it&rsquo;s time to take a break, check out the surf, or just relax, their &nbsp;terrace offers a stunning view of Taghazout and the ocean.&nbsp;Explore their offering at <a class=\"green\" href=\"https://www.sun-desk.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://www.sun-desk.com/</a></p>\r\n<p>SunDesk is offering Outpost Club members a suit of discounts!</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>For weekly stays: pay 6 nights and get your 7th night free!, get 7 nights for a week booking</li>\r\n<li>For monthly stays: 10% discount on month bookings</li>\r\n<li>For any stay, you\'ll receive one free surf lesson!</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Use the code OUTPOSTCLUB25 at checkout to receive the discount!</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"img_slider benef\">\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/sundesk-1.JPG\" alt=\"sun-desk\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/sundesk-2.jpg\" alt=\"sun-desk\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/sundesk-3.JPG\" alt=\"sun-desk\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/sundesk-4.jpg\" alt=\"sun-desk\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/sundesk-5.jpg\" alt=\"sun-desk\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/sundesk-6.jpg\" alt=\"sun-desk\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<hr class=\"hr\" />\r\n<div class=\"fx w ch2 m0\">\r\n<div>\r\n<h3 class=\"h6\"><a class=\"green\" href=\"http://retreats.io/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Retreats</a></h3>\r\n<p>Outpost Club has partnered with Retreats.io to offer their coliving services to our members!</p>\r\n<p>Retreats is a living experience off the beaten track on a private estate in the middle of the French countryside. Setup for the international traveller with everything you would need in a quality home. Swimming pool, access to vehicles, hiking from the front door and a very French way of life. More detailed information at our website https://www.retreats.io</p>\r\n<p>Retreats is offering all Outpost Club members the following deal:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>15% off mainstay one month (min stay one week)</li>\r\n<li>Access to Retreats\'&nbsp;<a class=\"green\" href=\"http://retreats.io/faq-eworkexchange/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">e-work-exchange -&nbsp;one weeks work in exchange for a one month stay!</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Discover the benefits of living and working off the grid in a billionaire landscape!&nbsp;Use the code OUTPOSTCLUB25 at checkout to receive the discount!</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"img_slider benef\">\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/retreats-1.jpg\" alt=\"retreats\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/retreats-2.jpg\" alt=\"retreats\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/retreats-3.jpg\" alt=\"retreats\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/retreats-4.jpg\" alt=\"retreats\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/retreats-5.jpg\" alt=\"retreats\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/retreats-6.jpg\" alt=\"retreats\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/retreats-7.jpg\" alt=\"retreats\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/retreats-8.jpg\" alt=\"retreats\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/retreats-9.jpg\" alt=\"retreats\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<hr class=\"hr\" />\r\n<div class=\"fx w ch2 m0\">\r\n<div>\r\n<h3 class=\"h6\"><a class=\"green\" href=\"https://www.lunabluretreats.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Lunablu Retreats </a></h3>\r\n<p>Become part of our ever-growing tribe of friends, co-workers, entrepreneurs and business people who are, just like you, committed to sharing their skills, passion, knowledge and commitment to make the working world a better place! Lunablu\'s offers tailor-made group coworkations typically for 8-16 participants. They offer their &nbsp;services worldwide, but have hubs in The Netherlands and in Italy. More information www.lunabluretreats.com</p>\r\n<p>Lunablu Retreats is offering the following deal to Outpost Club members:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>5% discount on a coworking retreat with Lunablu in 2019</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Use the code OUTPOSTCLUB25 at checkout to receive the discount!</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"img_slider benef\">\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/lunablu-1.jpg\" alt=\"lunabluretreats\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/lunablu-2.jpg\" alt=\"lunabluretreats\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/lunablu-3.jpg\" alt=\"lunabluretreats\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/lunablu-4.jpg\" alt=\"lunabluretreats\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/lunablu-5.jpg\" alt=\"lunabluretreats\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/lunablu-6.jpg\" alt=\"lunabluretreats\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/lunablu-7.jpg\" alt=\"lunabluretreats\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/lunablu-8.jpg\" alt=\"lunabluretreats\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/lunablu-9.png\" alt=\"lunabluretreats\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<hr class=\"hr\" />\r\n<div class=\"fx w ch2 m0\">\r\n<div>\r\n<h3 class=\"h6\"><a class=\"green\" href=\"https://cocohub.io/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">CoCoHub Malta</a></h3>\r\n<p>In one of the most beautiful areas of Malta, CoCoHub created an inspiring working and living environment. Who needs motivational quotes if you are staying in one of the most welcoming and beautiful communities with the 24/7 ability to grind? Outpost Club has partnered with CoCoHub Malta to offer Outpost Club members the chance to stay on the Mediterranean for as short or as long as you\'d like! Explore CoCoHub Malta\'s offerings at&nbsp; <a class=\"green\" href=\"https://cocohub.io/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">cocohub.io</a></p>\r\n<p>They are offering our members a simple deal:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Stay 5 Weeks, pay 4 weeks. It\'s a 20% discount!</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Use the code OUTPOSTCLUB25 at checkout to receive the discount!</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"img_slider benef\">\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/cocohub-1.jpg\" alt=\"CoCoHub\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/cocohub-2.jpg\" alt=\"CoCoHub\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/cocohub-3.jpg\" alt=\"CoCoHub\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/cocohub-4.jpg\" alt=\"CoCoHub\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/cocohub-5.jpg\" alt=\"CoCoHub\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/cocohub-6.jpg\" alt=\"CoCoHub\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/cocohub-7.jpg\" alt=\"CoCoHub\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/cocohub-8.jpg\" alt=\"CoCoHub\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<hr class=\"hr\" />\r\n<div class=\"fx w ch2 m0\">\r\n<div>\r\n<h3 class=\"h6\"><a class=\"green\" href=\"http://restation.co/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Restation</a></h3>\r\n<p>Restation is excited to have members of Outpost Club in the heart of Las Palmas, the capital of Gran Canaria island, one of the best places in Europe for remote work and surfing. Restation coliving, located steps away from amazing urban beach, makes everyone feel at home from day one. Everything is included in flat fee: accommodation in single rooms, coworking space access, use of shared areas including sunny rooftop, internet and utilities, as well as regular events and support on-site. Check out <a class=\"green\" href=\"http://www.restation.co\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">www.restation.co</a> for more details on services.</p>\r\n<p>Restation is offering Outpost Club members the following discount:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>10% off all stays at Restation!</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Use the code OUTPOSTCLUB25 at checkout to receive the discount!</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"img_slider benef\">\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/restation-1.jpg\" alt=\"restation\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/restation-2.jpg\" alt=\"restation\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/restation-3.jpg\" alt=\"restation\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/restation-4.jpg\" alt=\"restation\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/restation-5.jpg\" alt=\"restation\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/restation-6.jpg\" alt=\"restation\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/restation-7.jpg\" alt=\"restation\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/restation-8.jpg\" alt=\"restation\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<hr class=\"hr\" />\r\n<div class=\"fx w ch2 m0\">\r\n<div>\r\n<h3 class=\"h6\">sun and co.</h3>\r\n<p>Sun and Co. is the first coliving and coworking community on the whole Mediterranean Coast. A place for freelancers, entrepreneurs, location independent workers, digital nomads and anyone looking for a great work and leisure balance. A real co-living experience, all under one roof in a 19th-century house located in the centre of J&aacute;vea, a historic seaside town in Spain. Check out <a class=\"green\" href=\"https://sun-and-co.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://sun-and-co.com/&nbsp;</a>for more details on services.</p>\r\n<p>Sun and Co is offering Outpost Club members the following discount:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>5% off of all stays at Sun and Co.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Use the code OUTPOSTCLUB25 at checkout to receive the discount!</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"img_slider benef\">\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/sun-and-1.jpeg\" alt=\"sun and co\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/sun-and-2.jpg\" alt=\"sun and co\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/sun-and-3.jpg\" alt=\"sun and co\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/sun-and-4.jpg\" alt=\"sun and co\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/sun-and-5.jpg\" alt=\"sun and co\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/sun-and-6.jpg\" alt=\"sun and co\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/sun-and-7.jpg\" alt=\"sun and co\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/sun-and-8.jpg\" alt=\"sun and co\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/sun-and-9.jpg\" alt=\"sun and co\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/sun-and-10.jpg\" alt=\"sun and co\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<hr class=\"hr\" />\r\n<div class=\"fx w ch2 m0\">\r\n<div>\r\n<h3 class=\"h6\">Coconat</h3>\r\n<p>Coconat is a space for anyone to be inspired, concentrate, work, and play in the countryside! Join our temporary community in the beautiful German countryside, just one hour outside of Berlin. At Coconat you can expect to find a great mix of people from the local community, international residents working with Coconat and on their own, berliners and international location independents from creative industries, universities, or working on personal projects. Check out <a class=\"green\" href=\"http://coconat-space.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">coconat-space.com</a> for more details on services offered</p>\r\n<p>Coconat is excited to provide Outpost Club members with the following discount!</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>10% off of all stays at Coconat!</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Use the code OUTPOSTCLUB25 at checkout to receive the discount!</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"img_slider benef\">\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/coconat-1.JPG\" alt=\"Coconat\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/coconat-2.JPG\" alt=\"Coconat\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/coconat-3.jpg\" alt=\"Coconat\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/coconat-4.jpg\" alt=\"Coconat\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/coconat-5.jpg\" alt=\"Coconat\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/coconat-6.jpg\" alt=\"Coconat\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/coconat-7.jpg\" alt=\"Coconat\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/coconat-8.jpg\" alt=\"Coconat\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/coconat-9.jpg\" alt=\"Coconat\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"../files/uploads/benefits/coconat-10.jpg\" alt=\"Coconat\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 7, '', '', '', '', 163, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'Member Benefits', 0, 0, 'a:0:{}', '', '', '', '', 0, '0.00000000', '0.00000000', 0, '', NULL),
(164, 0, NULL, 'referral-program-terms-and-conditions', '', 'Outpost Club Referral Program Rules', 'Outpost Club Referral Program Rules', 'The Program Rules are in addition to any agreements between you and Outpost Club', 'Outpost Club Referral Program Rules', '', '', '<div class=\"txt\">\r\n<h1 class=\"center\">Outpost Club Referral Program Rules&nbsp;</h1>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><em>Last Updated:&nbsp;June 28th, 2021</em></p>\r\n<h3>Program Overview</h3>\r\n<p>These Outpost Club Referral Program Rules (&ldquo;Program Rules&rdquo;) govern your participation in the Outpost Club Referral Program. The Program Rules are in addition to any agreements between you and Outpost Club. The Outpost Club Terms are incorporated by reference and shall apply to your participation in the Outpost Club Referral Program, including, if necessary, to resolve any disputes between you and Outpost Club related to or arising out of the Referral Program.</p>\r\n<p>The Outpost Club Referral Program (&ldquo;Referral Program&rdquo;) is offered by Outpost Club, Inc. and its affiliates (together referred to as &ldquo;Outpost Club&rdquo;) and provides Members who are interested in referring their family and friends (&ldquo;Referrers&rdquo;) the opportunity to refer eligible individuals to join the Outpost Club community as new Members. The Referral triggers when the Referred Member signs an agreement and pays first Invoice. These Program Rules apply to both referrers and referred Users, so please read carefully to understand your respective rights and obligations.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>Referrer Eligibility</h3>\r\n<p>To be eligible to participate in the Referral Program as a referrer, you must (a) be a legal resident of your country; (b) be the age of majority in your territory of residence; and (c) maintain a Outpost Club account in good standing. Referrers must be or have been an Outpost Club member (tenant) and Outpost Club can require proof of a lease or check our own systems to determine this. Referrers may be Members. A single person may use the Outpost Club Platform in several ways (for example, as a Member and Potential Member). However, if you violate the Referral Program Rules or any applicable Terms of Service, Outpost Club may suspend or terminate your ability to participate in the Referral Program under any or all of your accounts. For example, if you are a Member and you engage in prohibited referral activity under your Outpost Club account, Outpost Club may terminate your ability to participate in the Referral Program under all of your Outpost Club accounts.</p>\r\n<h3>Eligibility of the person who is referred&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<p>There are 2 main criteria that the person who is referred must meet in order for all benefiting parties to receive the rewards:</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li><strong>The person who is referred must sign and pay for a stay at Outpost Club with a commitment that is no less than 6 months (181 days)&nbsp;</strong></li>\r\n<li>The&nbsp;person who is referred must have used the referal code or name of the Referrer during the application process, to indicated - before signing - that they had been referred by the Referrer.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h3>Outpost Club Codes</h3>\r\n<p>Under the Referral Program, Outpost Club may provide you with a unique alphanumeric code (&ldquo;Outpost Club Code&rdquo;) to distribute to eligible individuals to become new Members. Outpost Club may also provide you the ability to create additional Outpost Club Codes. Outpost Club owns all rights in and to any Outpost Club Code whether provided to you or created by you. You acknowledge and agree that: (a) Outpost Club may limit the number of Outpost Club Codes you may create or are made available to you, (b) you have no ownership rights in any form over the Outpost Club Codes, and (c) Outpost Club may reclaim, deactivate, invalidate or terminate your Outpost Club Code at any time at its discretion.</p>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3>How to Refer New Members</h3>\r\n<h3>a. Referred MEMBERS.</h3>\r\n<p>You may refer eligible individuals to become new Members on the Outpost Club Platform. In order to be eligible for a Referral Reward (defined below) for a new Member, the person must (i) have never previously created an Outpost Club account or lived with Outpost Club; (ii) be at least the age of majority in your territory of residence, and (iii) satisfy the applicable Reward Criteria, as discussed below. If these conditions are met, the person shall be considered your &ldquo;Referred Member.&rdquo;</p>\r\n<h3>B. Invitations through the Outpost Club Platform.</h3>\r\n<p>You may invite your family and friends to become new Members directly through the Outpost Club Platform by entering or providing Outpost Club with your invitee&rsquo;s contact information (all information collected by Outpost Club under the Referral Program shall be governed by Outpost Club\'s Privacy Policy). Inviting an individual through the Outpost Club Platform may generate an automatic invitation text (SMS) or email (the &ldquo;Invitation&rdquo;) to the person which may be sent through your phone number or a number controlled by Outpost Club. The Invitation may contain a promotional offer of Outpost Club credit or the special offer to a new Member. You represent that you have the necessary consent from your invitee to send them the Invitation (either directly or through the Outpost Club Platform). If your invitee follows the links in your Invitation and creates a Outpost Club account using the information provided, your Outpost Club Code will be automatically applied on the new Member\'s account, as applicable.</p>\r\n<h3>C. Other Invitations.</h3>\r\n<p>You may also invite eligible individuals to become new Members by distributing your Outpost Club Code directly and instructing them to manually input your Outpost Club Code into the Outpost Club Application form.&nbsp;A Member will not be able to apply your Outpost Club Code if (i) they&rsquo;ve already applied another Member&rsquo;s Outpost Club Code or a different promotion code, (ii) they&rsquo;ve already received Outpost Club credit from Outpost Club or another source on their Member account prior to entry of your Outpost Club Code, or (iii) they already concluded an agreement with Outpost Club prior to entering your Outpost Club Code in their Account. A Member will not be able to apply your Outpost Club Code if they start their application without entering your Code. If a Member does not enter your Outpost Club Code you will not receive attribution for the referral and they will not be considered your Referred Member. Outpost Club reserves the right to supply new Members with Outpost Club credit or sign-on bonuses at its discretion.</p>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3>Referral Rewards</h3>\r\n<h3>a. General.</h3>\r\n<p>You are eligible to earn a referral incentive (&ldquo;Referral Reward&rdquo;) for each Referred Member that you refer to the Outpost Club Platform (subject to certain maximum limits and the other terms in these Referral Program Rules). As discussed above, in order to qualify as your Referred Member, the new Member must satisfy the applicable Reward Criteria, sign the Membership Agreement and pay the first Invoice. The Reward Criteria are set by Outpost Club in its sole discretion and are subject to change at any time. Outpost Club, at its sole discretion, may make available certain promotions with different Reward Criteria or Referral Rewards to other Members or prospective Members. These promotions, unless offered to you, shall have no bearing whatsoever on your Agreement or relationship with Outpost Club.</p>\r\n<p>The Referral Rewards are triggered after a Referred Member signs an agreement and pays first Invoice.</p>\r\n<p>If the new Member that you refer satisfies the Reward Criteria, the type of Reward you are eligible to receive may depend on (i) which Outpost Club Member account you used to refer the new member, (ii) the Outpost Club region associated with your Outpost Club account, (iii) the Outpost Club region associated with the Referred Member when they apply your Outpost Club Code, or (iv) other factors as determined and communicated by Outpost Club.</p>\r\n<h3>b. Earning Rewards for Referred MEMBERS.</h3>\r\n<p>New Members you refer in some promotional cases may receive Outpost Club credit upon creating their new Outpost Club account by signing an agreement and paying the first Invoice (&ldquo;Referral Credit&rdquo;). Referral Credit is only valid for use on the Outpost Club Platform and is not transferable or redeemable for cash. Referral Credit may contain certain restrictions such as expiration dates or geographical use limitations which will be communicated to the new Member. New Members should check with their Outpost Club representative to determine whether they qualify to have Referral Credit and any restrictions on its use. In order to satisfy the Referral Criteria, the referred Member must use their first Outpost Club month credit before the Referral Credit expires, but in no event later than thirty (30) days from the creation of their Outpost Club account. All terms and conditions for the distribution and use of Referral Credit are determined by Outpost Club in its sole discretion.</p>\r\n<h3>c. Maximum Rewards for Referred MEMBERS.</h3>\r\n<p>The maximum amount of Referral Rewards that Outpost Club will pay for Referred Members is $2,000 per month (either in cash, Outpost Club credit, or a combination of the two). For example, if the Referral Reward is $250 per Referred Member and you generate 10 Referred Members in a single month, the maximum you can earn is $2,000 (in cash or Outpost Club credit) for such month.</p>\r\n<h3>D. Resolving Disputes over Referrals.</h3>\r\n<p>Only one person can earn a Referral Reward for a single Referred Member. In the event that multiple persons claim credit for a particular referral, Outpost Club has full discretion to determine which person earned such referral according to Outpost Club\'s systems.</p>\r\n<h3>E. Reservation of rights.</h3>\r\n<p>Outpost Club reserves the right to withhold or deduct Referral Rewards or Referral Credit obtained through the Referral Program in the event that Outpost Club determines or believes that the receipt of the Referral Reward or Referral Credit was in error, fraudulent, illegal, or in violation of these Referral Program Rules or any other applicable agreement between you and Outpost Club.</p>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3>Restrictions</h3>\r\n<p>In connection with your participation in the Referral Program, you expressly agree to the restrictions listed below. When distributing, promoting or communicating your Referral Code(s) you agree that:</p>\r\n<p>If you violate any of these restrictions Outpost Club may, in its discretion, remove your eligibility to participate in the Referral Program, and/or deny you any Referral Rewards earned in violation or suspected violation of these restrictions.</p>\r\n<ol data-rte-list=\"default\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>No spamming.</strong> You agree that you will not &ldquo;spam&rdquo; anyone with invitations to join the Outpost Club community, and that you at all times will remain compliant with CAN-SPAM, the TCPA, and other applicable laws. The following specific activities are prohibited:</p>\r\n<ol data-rte-list=\"default\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Mass emailing, texting or messaging people you do not personally know;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Use of automated systems or bots through any channel to distribute, post or respond to your Referral Code;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Use of scripts, programed or automatic dialers to send invites or to communicate Referral Codes; and</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Posting referral codes on event or venue pages without express permission from the owner.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>No Misrepresentations.</strong> You agree that you will not attempt to mislead anyone in connection with the Referral Program, either by affirmative representation, implication, or omission. In particular, you agree that you will not:</p>\r\n<ol data-rte-list=\"default\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Impersonate any person or entity</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Create fake accounts, blogs, webpages, profiles, websites, links or messages</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Misrepresent your relationship with Outpost Club or any other third party (Don&rsquo;t create content or communications that could have the effect of leading a consumer to believe that it is an official communication from Outpost Club.)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Suggest that an affiliation or partnership exists with a third party where none exists.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Don&rsquo;t make misrepresentations with respect to the characteristics or qualification requirements for any referral rewards. You acknowledge that Outpost Club may change the characteristics or qualification requirements for referral rewards in its discretion, and therefore you shall not represent any fixed characteristics (e.g., amount of Outpost Club credit, expiration date).</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Prohibited content.</strong> You agree that you will not use the Outpost Club brand in connection with:</p>\r\n<ol data-rte-list=\"default\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Disparaging or defamatory content concerning Outpost Club or third parties;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Content which promotes racism, bigotry, hatred, discrimination or physical harm of any kind against any group or individual;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Offensive, abusive, intimidating or harassing content</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Content that is sexually explicit, obscene and/or contains nudity</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Any political and/or religious statement;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Content containing images or reference to drugs, alcohol, tobacco, weapons or firearms</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Content that violates someone else&rsquo;s privacy</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Other restrictions.</strong> You also agree that you will not:</p>\r\n<ol data-rte-list=\"default\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Specify the monetary amount of the referral code unless authorised by Outpost Club in writing;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Create websites, domains, URLs, social media handles or email addresses containing the word &ldquo;Outpost Club&rdquo;;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Use the names or marks of Outpost Club competitors</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Use images of celebrities or other public or private figures without their written consent</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Use someone else&rsquo;s brand name or intellectual property without their written consent</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Engage in phishing or attempting to obtain financial or other personal information</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Solicit passwords or personally identifiable information</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Sell your Referral Code. You agree that you will only distribute your Outpost Club Code free of charge only for promotional purposes. You may not sell, trade, or barter your Outpost Club Code under any circumstances. You may not pay or provide anything of value to an invited user beyond any referral credit or collateral supplied by Outpost Club.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Violate or infringe the rights of a third party. You will not create any Outpost Club Code that infringes on the intellectual property rights of any third party. You will adhere to the License terms in any use of the Outpost Club Marks.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Advertise. You agree that you will not pay to advertise your Outpost Club Code or the Referral Program, including via Google, Facebook, Twitter, Bing and Craigslist.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Create printed materials other than those authorized by Outpost Club</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Post printed materials on public or private property without the express written consent.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Engage in fraudulent activity. You agree that you and your referrals will not defraud or abuse (or attempt to defraud or abuse) Outpost Club, the terms of the Outpost Club Referral Program, or any invited users.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3>Other Terms</h3>\r\n<p>The following terms shall also apply to your participation in the Referral Program.</p>\r\n<ol data-rte-list=\"default\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Referred Members who earn a Referral Reward for satisfying the Reward Criteria are not eligible for other sign-on bonuses or sign-on guarantees.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Members cannot earn Referral Rewards for referring themselves.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>In exchange for allowing you to promote your Outpost Club Code online (subject to the restrictions above), you agree to include a link on any such promotion page back to Outpost Club promotion page (or such other page as Outpost Club designates).</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>All Outpost Club promotions run for a limited time only and are subject to change at Outpost Club\'s discretion.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</div>', 7, '', '', '', '', 164, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'Outpost Club Referral Program Rules', 0, 0, 'a:0:{}', '', '', '', '', 0, '0.00000000', '0.00000000', 0, '', NULL),
