(200, 131, 0, 'are-the-shared-bedrooms-co-ed-what-about-the-rest-of-the-house', '', 'Are the bedrooms co-ed? What about the rest of the house', 'Are the shared bedrooms co-ed? What about the rest of the house?', '', 'Are the shared bedrooms co-ed? What about the rest of the house?', '', '', '<p>All shared bedrooms (rooms with two beds in one bedroom) are gender-separated unless otherwise requested by a group. All other spaces of shared apartments (kitchens, living rooms, shared bathrooms, etc.) are&nbsp;shared by all. If you have rented a private bedroom, your bedroom is for you and you alone, however the shared spaces of the apartment outside your bedroom are shared by all. If you plan to rent an entire apartment, none of this answer applies to you: you get to share your apartment with whomever your agree to share it with.</p>', 6, '', '', '', '', 196, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'Are the shared bedrooms co-ed? What about the rest of the house?', 0, 0, 'a:0:{}', '', '', '', '', 0, '0.00000000', '0.00000000', 0, '', '2022-08-16 14:18:14'),
(201, 114, NULL, 'do-you-provide-a-month-to-month-option', '', 'Do you provide a month-to-month option?', 'Do you provide a month-to-month option?', '', 'Do you provide a month-to-month option?', '', '', '<p>We do not provide the standard month-to-month option, but we do provide the ability to&nbsp;make continuous one-month commitments. What this means is that you can rent for a month, then decide during the month that you would like to extend of another month.&nbsp;As soon as you know you would like to extend another month, let us know! The longer you wait, the higher the chance someone else might reserve your room.</p>', 6, '', '', '', '', 121, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'Do you provide a month-to-month option?', 0, 0, 'a:0:{}', '', '', '', '', 0, '0.00000000', '0.00000000', 0, '', NULL),
