e\";s:1:\"2\";s:5:\"title\";s:33:\"Have them download the August app\";s:11:\"description\";s:223:\"iOS: <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/ua/app/august-home/id648730592?mt=8\" target=\"_blank\">AppStore</a><br>\r\nAndroid: <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.august.luna\" target=\"_blank\"> Google Play</a>\";}i:3;a:3:{s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:5:\"title\";s:27:\"Have them create an account\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:3:{s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:5:\"title\";s:36:\"Test out the app on the August locks\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";}i:5;a:3:{s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:5:\"title\";s:29:\"Give them the front door code\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";}}}i:3;a:3:{s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:5:\"title\";s:36:\"Tell them the wifi name and password\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:4:{s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:5:\"title\";s:48:\"Take a picture of their ID and put it into Slack\";s:11:\"description\";s:97:\" <a href=\"https://outpostclub.slack.com/messages/C6WFJNGR2\" target=\"_blank\">Slack #id Channel</a>\";s:3:\"sub\";a:1:{i:1;a:3:{s:4:\"type\";s:2:\"11\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:5;a:4:{s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:5:\"title\";s:15:\"Show them house\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";s:3:\"sub\";a:6:{i:5;a:3:{s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:5:\"title\";s:118:\"Show the members how to use the appliances, and where they can find the kitchen supplied (plates, forks, coffee, etc.)\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:3:{s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:5:\"title\";s:46:\"Show them their cabinet space and fridge space\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:3:{s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:5:\"title\";s:53:\"Tell them about the cleaning board and ADD THEM TO IT\";s:11:\"description\";s:71:\"Make sure they choose a day they can actually do their responsibilities\";}i:3;a:3:{s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:5:\"title\";s:61:\"Tell them that we hold events, and to join the Facebook group\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:3:{s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:5:\"title\";s:56:\"Add their name to the blackboard downstairs at the house\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";}i:6;a:3:{s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:5:\"title\";s:28:\"Tell them how the mail works\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";}}}i:8;a:3:{s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"6\";s:5:\"title\";s:4:\"Note\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";}}', '', '', '', '', 0, '0.00000000', '0.00000000', 0, '', NULL),
