(242, 222, NULL, 'how-to-show-the-house-to-prospective-clients-checklist', '', 'How to Show The House to Prospective Clients Checklist', 'How to Show The House to Prospective Clients Checklist', '', 'How to Show The House to Prospective Clients Checklist', '', '', '', 12, '', '', '', 'fa-list-ul', 227, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'How to Show The House to Prospective Clients Checklist', 0, 0, 'a:6:{i:1;a:3:{s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"description\";s:275:\"Sometimes potential members think that the online videos of the houses that we send them are not enough to make their decision, and want to see the inside of the house. It will be your responsibility to show them the house, which is an opportunity for you to make some money!\";}i:2;a:4:{s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:5:\"title\";s:32:\"During the week of their showing\";s:11:\"description\";s:246:\"You receive a message on the Slack  <a href=\"https://outpostclub.slack.com/\" target=\"_blank\">#house-showing</a> saying that you need to show the house to a prospective client. You’ll receive their name, phone number, and days they are available\";s:3:\"sub\";a:3:{i:3;a:3:{s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:5:\"title\";s:35:\"Call the prospective client and say\";s:11:\"description\";s:589:\"<i>\"Hi! This is [YOUR NAME] with Outpost Club. I\'m getting in contact to schedule a tour of our [HOUSE NAME]. What time works for you?”</i>\r\n<br>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>If they don’t answer the phone, send them a text saying:</strong><br>\r\n<i>“Hi! This is [YOUR NAME] with Outpost Club. I\'m getting in contact to schedule a tour of our [HOUSE NAME]. What time works for you?”</i></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Make sure to choose a time that works for you too!</strong><br>\r\nYou can always reschedule the time if they mention a time that doesn’t work for you.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\";}i:4;a:3:{s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:5:\"title\";s:37:\"Agree to a time for the house showing\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";}i:5;a:3:{s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:5:\"title\";s:77:\"Prepare accordingly to be at the house on that day. Write it in your schedule\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";}}}i:3;a:4:{s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:5:\"title\";s:27:\"On the day of their showing\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";s:3:\"sub\";a:6:{i:1;a:3:{s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:5:\"title\";s:55:\"Call the prospective client the morning of the showing.\";s:11:\"description\";s:155:\"Say, <i>“Hey there, I’ll be showing you the Outpost Club Coliving Space today, can you confirm that you’ll be arriving at the agree upon time?”</i>\";}i:2;a:3:{s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:5:\"title\";s:59:\"If they don’t answer the phone, send them a text saying: \";s:11:\"description\";s:211:\"<i>“Hey there, I’ll be showing you the Outpost Club Coliving Space today, can you confirm that you’ll be arriving at the agree upon time? A simple ‘Yes I’ll be there’ response would be great!” </i>\";}i:3;a:3:{s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:5:\"title\";s:73:\"Arrive at the house 30 minutes to an hour in advance of the house showing\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:4:{s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:5:\"title\";s:32:\"Make sure the house is in order.\";s:11:\"description\";s:46:\"The house does not need to look perfect, but: \";s:3:\"sub\";a:5:{i:1;a:3:{s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:5:\"title\";s:91:\"Countertops/tables should be cleared: place any dirty dishes/cups in the sink or dishwasher\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:3:{s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:5:\"title\";s:48:\"Trash left out should be placed in the trash bin\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:3:{s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:5:\"title\";s:26:\"Put shoes in the shoe rack\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:3:{s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:5:\"title\";s:106:\"Make sure members’ personal items that are left in the common rooms are placed in the lost-and-found box\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";}i:5;a:3:{s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:5:\"title\";s:53:\"Anything else that looks messy or unorganized, fix it\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";}}}i:5;a:3:{s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:5:\"title\";s:30:\"Find an open room to show them\";s:11:\"description\";s:129:\"his room should be the type of room they are looking to reserve. If not available, find the cleanest version of this type of room\";}i:6;a:3:{s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:5:\"title\";s:63:\"Let all the current members who are home know about the showing\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";}}}i:5;a:4:{s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:5:\"title\";s:16:\"When they arrive\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";s:3:\"sub\";a:7:{i:1;a:3:{s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:5:\"title\";s:45:\"Meet them at the door and introduce yourself:\";s:11:\"description\";s:73:\"<i>“Hi! I’m [YOUR NAME] the [YOUR ROLE] here at Outpost Club”</i>\r\n\";}i:2;a:3:{s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:5:\"title\";s:61:\"Sit down with them and give them time to take off their shoes\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:3:{s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:5:\"title\";s:26:\"While sitting, tell them: \";s:11:\"description\";s:303:\"<i>“You are seeing the [HOUSE NAME], it has [TOTAL NUMBER OF BEDS], and the community is vibrant, you’ll be living with some great people. Included in membership is move in ready furniture and equipment, utilities, cleaning services, and community events! Let’s go take a look at the house.”</i>\";}i:4;a:4:{s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:5:\"title\";s:14:\"Show the house\";s:11:\"description\";s:34:\"Basically just the important parts\";s:3:\"sub\";a:4:{i:1;a:4:{s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:5:\"title\";s:12:\"Living room:\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";s:3:\"sub\";a:3:{i:1;a:3:{s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:5:\"title\";s:19:\"Printer, paper, ink\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:3:{s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:5:\"title\";s:2:\"TV\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:3:{s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:5:\"title\";s:7:\"Lockers\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";}}}i:2;a:4:{s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:5:\"title\";s:8:\"Kitchen:\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";s:3:\"sub\";a:4:{i:1;a:3:{s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:5:\"title\";s:57:\"Restockables: coffee, tea, sugar, salt, pepper, olive oil\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:3:{s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:5:\"title\";s:78:\"Restockables: paper towels, dish soap, dishwasher detergent, garbage bags, etc\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:3:{s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:5:\"title\";s:50:\"Kitchen essentials: pots, pans, plates, silverware\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:3:{s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:5:\"title\";s:45:\"Appliances: let them know they can use it all\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";}}}i:3;a:4:{s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:5:\"title\";s:10:\"Bathrooms:\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";s:3:\"sub\";a:1:{i:1;a:3:{s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:5:\"title\";s:43:\"Toilet paper, shampoo, body wash, hand soap\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";}}}i:4;a:4:{s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:5:\"title\";s:9:\"Bedrooms:\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";s:3:\"sub\";a:1:{i:1;a:3:{s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:5:\"title\";s:40:\"Linens - bed is prepared when you arrive\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:5;a:3:{s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:5:\"title\";s:34:\"Ask them if the have any questions\";s:11:\"description\";s:186:\"If you don’t know the answers to their questions, let them know they can ask their questions to <a href=\"mailto:bookings@outpost-club.com\" target=\"_blank\">bookings@outpost-club.com</a>\";}i:6;a:3:{s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:5:\"title\";s:19:\"Ask them directly  \";s:11:\"description\";s:56:\"<i>“When are you looking to make a decision by?”</i>\";}i:7;a:3:{s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:5:\"title\";s:95:\"Say “Thank you for coming!” and walk them to the front door (make sure they actually leave)\";s:11:\"description\";s:29:\"Make sure they actually leave\";}}}i:6;a:4:{s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:5:\"title\";s:29:\"Immediately after the showing\";s:11:\"description\";s:51:\"Report back to Outpost Club on how the showing went\";s:3:\"sub\";a:4:{i:1;a:3:{s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:5:\"title\";s:25:\"Was the person interested\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:3:{s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:5:\"title\";s:86:\"When are they looking to make a decision by? What day should our sales team follow up?\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:3:{s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:5:\"title\";s:33:\"Did the showing go well or poorly\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:3:{s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:5:\"title\";s:35:\"Did the person ask weird questions \";s:11:\"description\";s:97:\"Sometimes other companies will send people to our houses to “spy” and see what it’s like”\";}}}i:7;a:3:{s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"7\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"description\";s:109:\"If you complete these task and the person books a stay with us for two months or more, you will receive $100!\";}}', '', '', '', '', 0, '0.00000000', '0.00000000', 0, '', NULL),
