(411, 253, 332, 'the-gates-house', '', 'The Gates House', 'The Gates House (NY 11221) | Outpost Club', 'We worked with interior designers to make The Gates House comfortable in every room. ✓ Fully furnished ✓ Security ✓ Gas ✓ Electricity ✓ Water ✓ Wi-Fi ✓ Cleaning and maintenance', 'The Gates House | Outpost Club', '<p>Bushwick, Brooklyn</p>\r\n<p>Private rooms from $1450</p>', '<h1 class=\"h1 center\">The Gates House</h1>\r\n<h4>A SPACIOUS HOME IN A LIVELY NEIGHBORHOOD</h4>', '<div>\r\n<h6 class=\"h5\">The scoop&nbsp;</h6>\r\n<p>The Gates House is located in Bushwick, known for its artistic murals and hip atmosphere. You&rsquo;ll find plenty of cafes, restaurants and shopping within walking distance &mdash; making it the perfect Brooklyn neighborhood to explore. This home has three units and spacious common area accessible through the basement.</p>\r\n<p>The house has been recently renovated space throughout with updated appliances, modern furnishings, exposed brick and hardwood floors. The spaces are arranged around bright and inviting common areas, which are spacious in comparison to your average New York City apartment.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h6 class=\"h5\">Location</h6>\r\n<p>The nearest subway station is a 3-minute walk from the Gates House, giving you easy access to both Williamsburg and Manhattan. Hop on the J at the Gates Avenue station and you can be on the Lower East Side in a mere 25 minutes. This conveniently located home allows you to enjoy the slower pace of Brooklyn while having easy access to all of New York City.</p>\r\n<p>The neighborhood features a nearby grocery store, popular thrift stores and eclectic cuisine ranging from Pan-Latin eats to vegan dishes at Chez Alex.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h6 class=\"h5\">The space</h6>\r\n<p>The house is a renovated building with updated appliances, hardwood floors, large windows and unique details like exposed brick and wood. The Gates House has three apartments altogether, each with three private bedrooms, two bathrooms and a shared common area. All of the common areas are large in comparison to your average New York City apartment.</p>\r\n<p><strong>This space is move-in ready; all you have to do is show up.</strong></p>\r\n</div>', 5, '', 'gates-house-bedroom-10.jpg', 'gates-house-bedroom-10.jpg', '', 273, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'The Gates House', 0, 0, 'a:8:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"title\";s:20:\"Throughout the house\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:587:\"<p>{throughout}</p>\r\n<table class=\"table v2\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<th>12+ Months</th>\r\n<th>5-11 Months</th>\r\n<th>1-4 Months</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Private (Standard)</th>\r\n<td>$1450</td>\r\n<td>$1540</td>\r\n<td>$2140</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>2-Person Shared</th>\r\n<td>$790</td>\r\n<td>$840</td>\r\n<td>$890</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"5\">\r\n<p>*Prices above do not include $149/month/person utilities allowance fee</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div class=\"center\"><a class=\"button2 red\" href=\"online-questionnaire\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Apply for free</a></div>\";}i:1;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:12:\"The Bedrooms\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:4:\"body\";s:302:\"<p>All of the bedrooms in the Gates House are private and feature full-sized beds.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Amenities</strong>: full-size memory-foam mattresses, shelving, hooks and closets/organizational tools.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Services</strong>: Bedding is available for an additional fee.</li>\r\n</ul>\";s:6:\"images\";a:8:{i:0;s:26:\"gates-house-bedroom-10.jpg\";i:1;s:25:\"gates-house-bedroom-5.jpg\";i:2;s:25:\"gates-house-bedroom-3.jpg\";i:3;s:25:\"gates-house-bedroom-4.jpg\";i:4;s:25:\"gates-house-bedroom-8.jpg\";i:5;s:25:\"gates-house-bedroom-7.jpg\";i:6;s:26:\"gates-house-bedroom-9.jpeg\";i:7;s:25:\"gates-house-bedroom-6.jpg\";}}i:2;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:24:\"The kitchens/dining room\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:4:\"body\";s:644:\"<p>In these apartments, the kitchen and dining room are the first rooms you enter. These spaces are used for cooking up dinner and relaxing in the evening over a glass of wine.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Amenities</strong> include electric stoves, stainless-steel fridges, microwaves, large sinks, coffee makers, blenders, plenty of cabinets, cookware, tableware, cutting boards and anything else you would need in a kitchen.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Also included:</strong> paper towels, dish soap, hand soap and garbage/recycling bags, all of which are routinely restocked.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Security:</strong> 24/7 security in common areas.</li>\r\n</ul>\";s:6:\"images\";a:1:{i:0;s:24:\"gates-house-kitchen.jpeg\";}}i:3;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:19:\"The (Co)Living Room\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:419:\"<p>The common area is shared by all Outpost members at the Gates House and features sprawling couches, an air hockey table, flatscreen TVs and a table for working or eating. Whether you&rsquo;re looking to work or play, the common area has everything you need to feel right at home.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Security:</strong> 24/7 security in common areas.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Tech:</strong> Google Chromecast.</li>\r\n</ul>\";s:6:\"images\";a:3:{i:0;s:26:\"gates-house-coliving-3.jpg\";i:1;s:26:\"gates-house-coliving-2.jpg\";i:2;s:26:\"gates-house-coliving-1.jpg\";}}i:4;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:13:\"The bathrooms\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:317:\"<p>The Gates House features sleek and renovated bathrooms with modern appliances to suit all your needs. There&rsquo;s two bathrooms per apartment, so you&rsquo;ll never need to wait!</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Also included</strong>: toilet paper, hand soap and small garbage bags, which will never be empty!</li>\r\n</ul>\";s:6:\"images\";a:1:{i:0;s:24:\"gates-house-bathroom.jpg\";}}i:5;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"title\";s:19:\"PERKS AND BENEFITS:\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:645:\"<div class=\"fx ch3 w perc_advantages\">\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Fast, reliable WiFi</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Regular professional cleaning</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Furnished interiors</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">In-unit laundry</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Keyless entry</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Spacious bedrooms</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Community events</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Dedicated community manager</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Updated appliances</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Dedicated maintenance team</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\";}i:6;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"title\";s:6:\"Prices\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:745:\"<table class=\"table v2\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<th>12+ Months</th>\r\n<th>5-11 Months</th>\r\n<th>1-4 Months</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Private (Standard)</th>\r\n<td>$1450</td>\r\n<td>$1540</td>\r\n<td>$2140</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>2-Person Shared</th>\r\n<td>$790</td>\r\n<td>$840</td>\r\n<td>$890</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"5\">\r\n<p>*Prices above do not include $149/month/person utilities allowance fee</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div class=\"center\"><a class=\"button2 red\" href=\"online-questionnaire\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Apply for free</a></div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Availability: Year-round / Minimum stay of 1 month / Month-to-month payment options available / Minimum age 18</strong></p>\";}i:7;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:30:\"Welcome to Bushwick, Brooklyn.\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:4:\"body\";s:642:\"<div>\r\n<p>Bushwick is deservedly known for its public art &mdash; the famous street murals &mdash; and its legendary nightlife scene. It&rsquo;s also home to people from all different walks of life, and you won&rsquo;t be surprised to experience what feels like a beautiful celebration of culture just walking down a street like Knickerbocker Avenue, listening to the languages being spoken while deciding which food cart to stop at. The neighborhood features the cherished Maria Hernandez Park, trendy cafes like Variety, a plethora of nightlife options, and an active community that encourages you to get to know your neighbors.</p>\r\n</div>\";s:6:\"images\";a:7:{i:0;s:77:\"45f35bd23f049a76a8ec91d6dda27135--bushwick-brooklyn-williamsburg-brooklyn.jpg\";i:1;s:7:\"90.jpeg\";i:2;s:17:\"bikes-771x466.png\";i:3;s:49:\"Bushwick-Collective-Mural-Brooklyn-New-York-8.jpg\";i:4;s:27:\"GettyImages_817252928.0.jpg\";i:5;s:27:\"shutterstock_1047264637.jpg\";i:6;s:102:\"stock-photo-peace-new-york-rainy-street-art-brooklyn-bushwick-f8a5ec13-63d8-451e-af4b-b75183ecd9de.jpg\";}}}', '', '', '', '', 2, '40.69200256', '-73.92480177', 505, '', '2022-09-08 01:05:53'),
