(422, 253, 336, 'the-crown-heights-house', '', 'The Crown Heights House', 'The Crown Heights House (NY 11213) | Outpost Club', 'We worked with interior designers to make The Crown Heights House comfortable in every room. ✓ Fully furnished ✓ Security ✓ Gas ✓ Electricity ✓ Water ✓ Wi-Fi ✓ Cleaning and maintenance', 'The Crown Heights House | Outpost Club', '<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Crown Heights</span>, Brooklyn</p>\r\n<p>Private rooms from $1290</p>', '<h1 class=\"h1 center\">The Crown Heights House</h1>\r\n<h4>A SPACIOUS HOME IN A LIVELY NEIGHBORHOOD</h4>', '<div>\r\n<h6 class=\"h5\">The Scoop</h6>\r\n<p>You&rsquo;ll find the Crown Heights House in the heart of &mdash; you guessed it &mdash; Crown Heights, Brooklyn, in an area dotted with plentiful green space, historic Victorian mansions and streets lined with classic Brooklyn brownstones.</p>\r\n<p>The Crown Heights House is an easy walk from a star variety of the neighborhood&rsquo;s multitude of cafes and Carribean eateries, and just a few blocks from multiple subway lines, so you can always get to your destination in a hurry.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h6 class=\"h5\">Location</h6>\r\n<p>The closest subway stations are the Utica Ave. stop, served by the A/C trains and the Crown Heights-Utica Ave. stop, served by the 2/3 and 4 trains. Both are less than 10 minutes away walking. You can get to Manhattan in less than half an hour from either station with no transfers.</p>\r\n<p>This house is walking distance from multiple green spaces, including being just one block from St. John&rsquo;s Park, with a rec center, athletic courts and playing fields. It&rsquo;s a 10-minute walk from Lincoln Terrace / Arthur S. Somers Park, a large community park packed with basketball, tennis and handball courts, football fields and playgrounds.</p>\r\n</div>', 5, '', 'the-crown-heights-house.jpg', 'the-crown-heights-house.jpg', '', 293, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'The Crown Heights House', 0, 0, 'a:9:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"title\";s:20:\"Throughout the house\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:586:\"<p>{throughout}</p>\r\n<table class=\"table v2\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<th>12+ Months</th>\r\n<th>5-11 Months</th>\r\n<th>1-4 Months</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Private Large</th>\r\n<td>$1440</td>\r\n<td>$1520</td>\r\n<td>$2120</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Private Standard</th>\r\n<td>$1340</td>\r\n<td>$1420</td>\r\n<td>$2020</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"5\">\r\n<p>*Prices above do not include $149/month/person utilities allowance fee</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div class=\"center\"><a class=\"button2 red\" href=\"online-questionnaire\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Apply for free</a></div>\";}i:1;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:12:\"The Bedrooms\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:4:\"body\";s:372:\"<p>All of the bedrooms in the Crown Heights House are private and feature full-sized beds, while most include desks and some have shared balcony access.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Amenities:</strong> full-size memory-foam mattresses, shelving, hooks and closets/organizational tools.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Services:</strong> Bedding is available for an additional fee.</li>\r\n</ul>\";s:6:\"images\";a:4:{i:0;s:36:\"the-crown-heights-house-bedroom3.jpg\";i:1;s:36:\"the-crown-heights-house-bedroom4.jpg\";i:2;s:36:\"the-crown-heights-house-bedroom2.jpg\";i:3;s:36:\"the-crown-heights-house-bedroom1.jpg\";}}i:2;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:19:\"The (Co)Living Room\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:265:\"<p>The living rooms are at the heart of each unit within the Crown Heights House. The furnished units have comfy couches and TVs, and are equipped with everything you need to relax.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Security</strong>: 24/7 security in common areas</li>\r\n</ul>\";s:6:\"images\";a:5:{i:0;s:37:\"the-crown-heights-house-coliving1.jpg\";i:1;s:37:\"the-crown-heights-house-coliving3.jpg\";i:2;s:37:\"the-crown-heights-house-coliving2.jpg\";i:3;s:37:\"the-crown-heights-house-coliving6.jpg\";i:4;s:37:\"the-crown-heights-house-coliving5.jpg\";}}i:3;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:24:\"The Kitchens/Dining Room\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:728:\"<p>The kitchen and dining room in the Crown Heights House are spacious and open, with large street-facing windows and updated stainless steel appliances, including a dishwasher. These spaces are used for cooking dinner and relaxing in the evening over a glass of wine.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Amenities</strong> include electric stoves, stainless-steel fridges, microwaves, large sinks, coffee makers, blenders, plenty of cabinets, cookware, tableware, cutting boards and anything else you would need in a kitchen.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Supplies</strong>: Dishwasher detergent, soap, sponges, recycling and trash bags, all-purpose cleaner, paper towels.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Security</strong>: 24/7 security in common areas.</li>\r\n</ul>\";s:6:\"images\";a:2:{i:0;s:37:\"the-crown-heights-house-kitchen-2.jpg\";i:1;s:35:\"the-crown-heights-house-kitchen.jpg\";}}i:4;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:13:\"The bathrooms\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:492:\"<p>Every unit in the Crown Heights House has enough shared bathrooms so you can be sure you&rsquo;ll never have to wait.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Supplies</strong>: toilet paper, hand soap and small garbage bags, which will never be empty!</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><strong><strong>LAUNDRY</strong></strong></p>\r\n<p>The Crown Heights House also has free on-site laundry, a rarity in New York, so you won&rsquo;t have to worry about finding quarters or lugging your clothing to the laundromat!</p>\";s:6:\"images\";a:2:{i:0;s:37:\"the-crown-heights-house-bathroom1.jpg\";i:1;s:37:\"the-crown-heights-house-bathroom2.jpg\";}}i:5;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:13:\"Outdoor Space\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:4:\"body\";s:313:\"<p>The Crown Heights House offers rooftop access with views of Crown Heights&rsquo; tree-lined streets and large amount of green spaces. There is also a spacious backyard with plentiful seating and a fire pit for outdoor gatherings in the spring, summer and fall. Some bedrooms have shared balconies, as well.</p>\";s:6:\"images\";a:4:{i:0;s:36:\"the-crown-heights-house-outdoor3.jpg\";i:1;s:36:\"the-crown-heights-house-outdoor4.jpg\";i:2;s:36:\"the-crown-heights-house-outdoor1.jpg\";i:3;s:36:\"the-crown-heights-house-outdoor2.jpg\";}}i:6;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"title\";s:20:\"PERKS AND BENEFITS: \";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:642:\"<div class=\"fx ch3 w perc_advantages\">\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Fast, reliable WiFi</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Regular professional cleaning</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Furnished interiors</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">On-site laundry</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Keyless entry</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Rooftop access</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Community events</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Dedicated community manager</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Updated appliances</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Dedicated maintenance team</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\";}i:7;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"title\";s:6:\"Prices\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:744:\"<table class=\"table v2\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<th>12+ Months</th>\r\n<th>5-11 Months</th>\r\n<th>1-4 Months</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Private Large</th>\r\n<td>$1440</td>\r\n<td>$1520</td>\r\n<td>$2120</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Private Standard</th>\r\n<td>$1340</td>\r\n<td>$1420</td>\r\n<td>$2020</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"5\">\r\n<p>*Prices above do not include $149/month/person utilities allowance fee</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div class=\"center\"><a class=\"button2 red\" href=\"online-questionnaire\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Apply for free</a></div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Availability: Year-round / Minimum stay of 1 month / Month-to-month payment options available / Minimum age 18</strong></p>\";}i:8;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:35:\"Welcome to Crown Heights, Brooklyn.\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:4:\"body\";s:711:\"<div>\r\n<p>Walk off the train and into this historic Brooklyn neighborhood that feels like home with its quaint, brownstone-lined streets and vibrant culture. Immerse yourself in the community and you&rsquo;ll find unique locally owned shops, neighbors who are always up for a good conversation, and a rich history worth honoring. The neighborhood features the lively Herbert Von King park, trendy coffee shops like Brooklyn Blend and eclectic cuisine ranging from Caribbean to Japanese. You can explore surrounding neighborhoods like Clinton Hill and Williamsburg by foot, or hop on the subway and be in Manhattan in 30 minutes. With so much to explore, you&rsquo;ll never be bored in Crown Heights.</p>\r\n</div>\";s:6:\"images\";a:6:{i:0;s:15:\"16334_image.jpg\";i:1;s:27:\"5912826960_a9fbc6587b_b.jpg\";i:2;s:26:\"brownstones-park-slope.jpg\";i:3;s:48:\"Crown_Heights,_Brooklyn,_NY,_USA_-_panoramio.jpg\";i:4;s:23:\"crown-heights-north.jpg\";i:5;s:74:\"Curiosities-Top-Picks-10-Place-to-Eat-Crown-Heights-by-Shalom-Serraf-1.png\";}}}', '', '', '', '', 2, '40.67302395', '-73.93023425', 502, '', '2022-07-11 06:27:39'),
