(267, 0, NULL, 'nob-hill', '', 'Nob Hill', 'Nob Hill Apartments For Rent | Coliving Spaces', '', 'Nob Hill', '<h1 class=\"big_p\">A month-to-month coliving house for international entrepreneurs, developers, designers, digital nomads and students. We offer you a great startup community atmosphere so you can live, work and network with like-minded people.</h1>', '', '<p>Our house consists of two levels, with 14 bedrooms, six bathrooms, a kitchen and a co-working area. The house has recently been remodeled&nbsp;and features new bathrooms and a fully equipped kitchen.</p>\r\n<p>All members of Outpost Club enjoy access to the living rooms, co-working areas with fast WiFi (100Mbps+) and a backyard that plays host to frequent BBQs and parties.</p>\r\n<p>For your convenience, there a washer and dryer are provided&nbsp;for complimentary use. Our house has a new digital lock system and there are cameras in common spacesfor added security.</p>', 9, '', '', '', '', 347, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Nob Hill', 0, 0, 'a:0:{}', '', '', '', '', 0, '0.00000000', '0.00000000', 0, '', NULL),
