(278, 254, NULL, 'the-lakeview-house', 'lakeview2', 'Lakeview House', 'Oceanview (SF) Room Rentals, Shared Apartments | Outpost Club', '', 'The Lakeview House', '<p>Lakeview, San Francisco</p>\r\n<p>Shared rooms from $1100 | Private rooms from $2100</p>', '<h1 class=\"h1\">Lakeview House</h1>\r\n<h4>This magnificent home in great condition is available for you to rent</h4>', '<div>\r\n<h6 class=\"h5\">The Scoop</h6>\r\n<p>The Lakeview House is the latest addition to Outpost in San Francisco. We chose the Oceanview neighborhood because it&rsquo;s perfect for professionals and students alike, located just south of the City College of San Francisco and east of San Francisco State University. The house is surrounded by green spaces like Lake Merced Park and within easy access to BART and multiple Mini lines.</p>\r\n<p>Our Lakeview house features three floors of exclusively designed space with plenty of natural light. Enjoy expansive views of the city from the kitchen&rsquo;s panoramic windows and lounge on the terrace or in the backyard in your spare time. We&rsquo;ve included everything you&rsquo;ll need to feel right at home, so all you need to bring is your suitcase.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h6 class=\"h5\">Location</h6>\r\n<p>This coliving house is located near the City College of San Francisco and San Francisco State University.</p>\r\n<p>The closest Muni stations are at Broad St./Plymouth Ave., on the M-Ocean View line, and Lee St. and Ocean Ave., on the K-Ingleside and T-Third lines. Multiple bus lines serve the neighborhood. The closest BART station is Balboa Park.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h6 class=\"h5\">The space</h6>\r\n<p>This house features three floors of newly renovated space, with hardwood floors and updated appliances. The kitchen and common areas are massive compared to the average San Francisco apartment, and furnished with everything you&rsquo;ll need for work and play.</p>\r\n<p><strong>This space is move-in ready; all you have to do is show up with your suitcase.</strong></p>\r\n</div>', 5, '', 'lakeview-29.jpg', 'lakeview-52.jpg', '', 534, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'The Lakeview House', 0, 0, 'a:8:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"title\";s:20:\"Throughout the house\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:1583:\"<p>{throughout}</p>\r\n<table class=\"table v2\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<th class=\"title\">\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><span class=\"gold\">Gold</span> Membership</p>\r\n<p class=\"price\">$690 One-Time Fee</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</th>\r\n<th colspan=\"2\">\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><span class=\"silver\">Silver</span> Membership</p>\r\n<p><span class=\"bronze\">Bronze</span> Membership</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p class=\"price\">$79 One-Time Fee</p>\r\n<p class=\"price\">No Fee*</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"2\"><em>*Bronze members must move in on <strong>the first day</strong> of the month</em></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<th>1-12 Months</th>\r\n<th>4+ Months</th>\r\n<th>1-3 Months</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Private (Executive)</th>\r\n<td>$2100</td>\r\n<td>$2300</td>\r\n<td>$2400</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>2-people shared</th>\r\n<td>$1100</td>\r\n<td>$1250</td>\r\n<td>$1350</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"5\">See the benefits of Bronze, Silver, and Gold Membership <a class=\"red\" href=\"../memberships\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">here</a>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><em>**The prices shown indicate <strong>the prices valid for move-in between Feb 1, 2020, and Sept<em><strong><em><strong>&nbsp;30</strong></em></strong></em>, 2020</strong>. The exact price is indicated in your membership agreement and may vary depending on the length of commitment, your membership level and the size of your group, if applicable.</em></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div class=\"center\"><a class=\"button2\" href=\"join-us\">I`m interested</a></div>\";}i:1;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:12:\"The Bedrooms\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:4:\"body\";s:483:\"<p>Your room will be move-in ready, just like the rest of the house; there&rsquo;s no need to even bring a pillow. There are single and shared rooms, depending on availability and your price range.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Amenities: memory-foam mattresses, memory-foam pillows, extension cords to your bedside, shelving, hooks, bed linens, towels and closets/organizational tools.</li>\r\n<li>Gold and members silver: Bed linens and towels will be available for you when you arrive.</li>\r\n</ul>\";s:6:\"images\";a:7:{i:0;s:22:\"lakeview-bedroom-3.jpg\";i:1;s:22:\"lakeview-bedroom-4.jpg\";i:2;s:22:\"lakeview-bedroom-1.jpg\";i:3;s:22:\"lakeview-bedroom-2.jpg\";i:4;s:22:\"lakeview-bedroom-5.jpg\";i:5;s:22:\"lakeview-bedroom-6.jpg\";i:6;s:22:\"lakeview-bedroom-7.jpg\";}}i:2;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:24:\"The kitchens/dining room\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:748:\"<p>The kitchen has plenty of counter space for cooking on your own or with a group, as well as updated appliances, a spacious fridge and two dining sets. The spaces are used for potluck dinners, solo meals and chats in the evening over a glass of wine.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Amenities include a gas stove, stainless-steel fridge, microwave, large sinks, a coffee maker, a Ninja blender, an electric kettle, plenty of cabinets, cookware, tableware, cutting boards and anything else you would need in a kitchen.</li>\r\n<li>Also included: salt, pepper, sugar, coffee grounds, tea, olive oil, paper towels, dish soap, hand soap and garbage/recycling bags, all of which are routinely restocked.</li>\r\n<li>Security: 24/7 security in all common areas.</li>\r\n</ul>\";s:6:\"images\";a:6:{i:0;s:22:\"lakeview-kitchen-1.jpg\";i:1;s:22:\"lakeview-kitchen-4.jpg\";i:2;s:22:\"lakeview-kitchen-5.jpg\";i:3;s:22:\"lakeview-kitchen-6.jpg\";i:4;s:22:\"lakeview-kitchen-8.jpg\";i:5;s:22:\"lakeview-kitchen-9.jpg\";}}i:3;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:20:\"The co-working space\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:4:\"body\";s:459:\"<p>The large kitchen serves as the principal common area for the Oceanview House. This open-plan room features a large dining table with ample room for co-working. There is also desk space within the bedrooms themselves. The centerpiece of the common room is undoubtedly the stunning views of San Francisco gained from the panoramic windows. This space also includes a printer (paper and ink included) to make sure you\'ll always be ready to be productive.</p>\";s:6:\"images\";a:4:{i:0;s:24:\"lakeview-coworking-3.jpg\";i:1;s:24:\"lakeview-coworking-1.jpg\";i:2;s:24:\"lakeview-coworking-4.jpg\";i:3;s:24:\"lakeview-covorking-5.jpg\";}}i:4;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:13:\"The bathrooms\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:633:\"<p>We provide many bathroom essentials, as well. There are five bathrooms in the Lakeview House, one private and four that are free to use regardless of which room you&rsquo;re in.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Also included: toilet paper, shampoo, body wash, hand soap and small garbage bags, which will never run out! We also provide hair dryers, so there\'s no need to bring your own.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>LAUNDRY ROOM</p>\r\n<p>The Lakeview House also has a washer and dryer where members can do their laundry for free in the comfort of their own home.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Security: 24/7 security in all common areas, as well as lockers.</li>\r\n</ul>\";s:6:\"images\";a:4:{i:0;s:23:\"lakeview-bathroom-3.jpg\";i:1;s:23:\"lakeview-bathroom-2.jpg\";i:2;s:23:\"lakeview-bathroom-5.jpg\";i:3;s:23:\"lakeview-bathroom-6.jpg\";}}i:5;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:8:\"Backyard\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:4:\"body\";s:289:\"<p>The Lakeview House has a spacious backyard with a grill and seating so you can enjoy the outdoors year-around. The space plays host to plenty of barbecues, parties and casual get-togethers. A balcony off two of the house&rsquo;s bedrooms provides sweeping views of the neighborhood.</p>\";s:6:\"images\";a:3:{i:0;s:23:\"lakeview-backyard-2.jpg\";i:1;s:23:\"lakeview-backyard-3.jpg\";i:2;s:23:\"lakeview-backyard-4.jpg\";}}i:6;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"title\";s:19:\"Additional benefits\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:352:\"<p>Your membership gives you the opportunity to move between all our houses month to month, allowing you to see what it&rsquo;s like to live in different neighborhoods.</p>\r\n<p><strong>We screen all candidates before approving applications so that there are no worries about moving into a new place with new people &mdash; only excitement!</strong></p>\";}i:7;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"title\";s:6:\"Prices\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:2046:\"<p>We have flexible month-to-month commitment options. We do not require extensive documents from you, guarantors or large deposits. A longer commitment on your side helps us to provide you with better prices.</p>\r\n<table class=\"table v2\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<th class=\"title\">\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><span class=\"gold\">Gold</span> Membership</p>\r\n<p class=\"price\">$690 One-Time Fee</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</th>\r\n<th colspan=\"2\">\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><span class=\"silver\">Silver</span> Membership</p>\r\n<p><span class=\"bronze\">Bronze</span> Membership</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p class=\"price\">$79 One-Time Fee</p>\r\n<p class=\"price\">No Fee*</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"2\"><em>*Bronze members must move in on <strong>the first day</strong> of the month</em></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<th>1-12 Months</th>\r\n<th>4+ Months</th>\r\n<th>1-3 Months</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Private (Executive)</th>\r\n<td>$2100</td>\r\n<td>$2300</td>\r\n<td>$2400</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>2-people shared</th>\r\n<td>$1100</td>\r\n<td>$1250</td>\r\n<td>$1350</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"5\">See the benefits of Bronze, Silver, and Gold Membership <a class=\"red\" href=\"../memberships\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">here</a>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><em>**The prices shown indicate <strong>the prices valid for move-in between <em><strong>Feb 1, 2020, and Sept<em><strong><em><strong>&nbsp;30</strong></em></strong></em>, 2020</strong></em></strong>. The exact price is indicated in your membership agreement and may vary depending on the length of commitment, your membership level and the size of your group, if applicable.</em></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div class=\"center\"><a class=\"button2\" href=\"join-us\">Get your exclusive offer now</a></div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Availability: Year-round / Minimum stay of 1 month / Month-to-month payment options available / Minimum age 18 / 30-day cancellation notice with Gold Membership</strong></p>\";}}', '', '', 'a:3:{i:0;s:3:\"283\";i:1;s:3:\"238\";i:2;s:3:\"311\";}', '', 0, '0.00000000', '0.00000000', 0, '', NULL),
(280, 253, 282, 'the-upper-manhattan-house', '', 'The Upper Manhattan House', 'The Upper Manhattan House | Outpost Club', 'We worked with interior designers to make The Upper Manhattan House comfortable in every room. ✓ Fully furnished ✓ Security ✓ Gas ✓ Electricity ✓ Water ✓ Wi-Fi ✓ Cleaning and maintenance', 'The Upper Manhattan House | Outpost Club', '<p>Upper Manhattan, New York</p>\r\n<p>Private rooms from $1350</p>', '', '<div>\r\n<h6 class=\"h5\">The Scoop</h6>\r\n<p>Our Upper Manhattan House is situated in the vibrant, historic Harlem neighborhood. Surrounded by institutions of higher education, parks, restaurants and cafes, it&rsquo;s an area full of things to see and do, while still being within easy reach of downtown Manhattan. Situated beside St. Nicolas Park and within easy reach of Central Park, you&rsquo;ll find some of the city&rsquo;s best jazz music on your doorstep, as well as multiple subway lines and buses taking you downtown.</p>\r\n<p>The Upper Manhattan House is spread over two adjoining apartment buildings, with two floors of individual Outpost apartments in each building. Members enjoy spacious common areas within their apartment, including a living room and kitchen, and one room&nbsp;includes access to a large balcony.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h6 class=\"h5\">The Neighborhood</h6>\r\n<p>This space features hardwood floors, all major appliances and exposed brick. The kitchen and common areas are roomy compared to the average New York City apartment, with open kitchens and living rooms, all furnished with everything you&rsquo;ll need for work and play.</p>\r\n<p>This space is move-in ready; all you have to do is show up with your suitcase.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>', 5, '', 'upper-manhattan-background-front.jpg', 'upper-manhattan-bedroom-3.1200x1200-2.jpg', '', 330, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'The Upper Manhattan House', 0, 0, 'a:8:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"title\";s:20:\"Throughout the house\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:603:\"<p>{throughout}</p>\r\n<table class=\"table v2\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<th>12+ Months</th>\r\n<th>5-11 Months</th>\r\n<th>1-4 Months</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Private (Standard with balcony)</th>\r\n<td>$1600</td>\r\n<td>$1680</td>\r\n<td>$2280</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Private (Standard)</th>\r\n<td>$1550</td>\r\n<td>$1630</td>\r\n<td>$2230</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"5\">\r\n<p>*Prices above do not include $149/month/person utilities allowance fee</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div class=\"center\"><a class=\"button2 red\" href=\"join-us-manhattan\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Apply for free</a></div>\";}i:1;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:12:\"The Bedrooms\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:4:\"body\";s:455:\"<p>Each bedroom features large windows overlooking the neighborhood and some rooms have an adjoining balcony. This house consists of private rooms only, so you can relax away from the business of city life. Bedding is available for an additional fee.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Amenities</strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>:</strong> memory-foam full-sized mattresses, pillows, shelving, hooks and closets/organizational tools.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\";s:6:\"images\";a:5:{i:0;s:29:\"upper-manhattan-bedroom-3.jpg\";i:1;s:29:\"upper-manhattan-bedroom-5.jpg\";i:2;s:29:\"upper-manhattan-bedroom-6.jpg\";i:3;s:29:\"upper-manhattan-bedroom-7.jpg\";i:4;s:29:\"upper-manhattan-bedroom11.jpg\";}}i:2;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:24:\"The kitchens/dining room\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:724:\"<p>The large kitchens in each apartment feature all necessary appliances, with plenty of counter space for cooking on your own or with a group. Each kitchen includes a dining table that can be used for eating, socializing or co-working, as well as an adjacent living area for relaxing after work. The kitchen is the gathering place for potluck dinners, solo meals and chats in the evening over a glass of wine.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Amenities include</strong> a gas stove, stainless-steel fridge, microwave, large sinks, a coffee maker, plenty of cabinets, cookware, tableware, cutting boards and anything else you would need in a kitchen.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Security:</strong> 24/7 security in all common areas.</li>\r\n</ul>\";s:6:\"images\";a:3:{i:0;s:29:\"upper-manhattan-kitchen-2.jpg\";i:1;s:29:\"upper-manhattan-kitchen-5.jpg\";i:2;s:29:\"upper-manhattan-kitchen-6.jpg\";}}i:3;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"title\";s:20:\"The co-working space\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:202:\"<p>The individual kitchens in every apartment serve as the principal co-working areas for the Upper Manhattan House. These open-plan rooms feature large dining tables with ample room for co-working.</p>\";}i:4;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:13:\"The bathrooms\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:187:\"<p>We provide many bathroom essentials, as well.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Also included:</strong> toilet paper, hand soap and small garbage bags, which will never run out!&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\";s:6:\"images\";a:2:{i:0;s:30:\"upper-manhattan-bathroom-5.jpg\";i:1;s:30:\"upper-manhattan-bathroom-4.jpg\";}}i:5;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:11:\"The Terrace\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:4:\"body\";s:160:\"<p>The Upper Manhattan House features access to a private balcony for one of the bedrooms, so you can enjoy relaxing outdoor space during the warmer months.</p>\";s:6:\"images\";a:1:{i:0;s:27:\"upper-manhattan-terrace.jpg\";}}i:6;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"title\";s:19:\"Additional benefits\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:178:\"<p><strong>We screen all candidates before approving applications so that there are no worries about moving into a new place with new people &mdash; only excitement!</strong></p>\";}i:7;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"title\";s:6:\"Prices\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:761:\"<table class=\"table v2\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<th>12+ Months</th>\r\n<th>5-11 Months</th>\r\n<th>1-4 Months</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Private (Standard with balcony)</th>\r\n<td>$1600</td>\r\n<td>$1680</td>\r\n<td>$2280</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Private (Standard)</th>\r\n<td>$1550</td>\r\n<td>$1630</td>\r\n<td>$2230</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"5\">\r\n<p>*Prices above do not include $149/month/person utilities allowance fee</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div class=\"center\"><a class=\"button2 red\" href=\"join-us-manhattan\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Apply for free</a></div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Availability: Year-round / Minimum stay of 1 month / Month-to-month payment options available / Minimum age 18</strong></p>\";}}', '', '', '', '<div class=\"txt\">\r\n<h1 class=\"\">The Upper Manhattan House Move-In Guide</h1>\r\n<h2><em><strong>2282 7th Avenue, Manhattan</strong></em></h2>\r\n<hr class=\"hr\" />\r\n<h3><strong>The Community</strong></h3>\r\n<p>Welcome to Outpost! We&rsquo;re glad you&rsquo;re here. Coliving isn&rsquo;t just about having roommates or sharing a kitchen &mdash; it&rsquo;s about recognizing that we can do more, accomplish more and be more when we work together.</p>\r\n<p>We communicate with each other via our house&rsquo;s Messenger group, which your House Leader will add you upon arrival. We also offer an Outpost Slack channel where you can find other members with similar interests and meet new people in your area. We send out relevant updates and information via email, so keep an eye out!</p>\r\n<p>Your <strong>Member Portal</strong> is where you can RSVP for community events, submit maintenance and cleaning requests and access important documents. <a class=\"green\" href=\"../user/login\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Find it here</a>.</p>\r\n<p>Your <strong>House Leader</strong> will be your main point of contact with Outpost. Here&rsquo;s what they can help you with:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Info about community activities</li>\r\n<li>Restocking supplies</li>\r\n<li>Questions about Outpost</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>We have a lot of activities to help you get involved with our community and get to know the city. Pay attention to your Member Portal and your house&rsquo;s Messenger group to keep up with what&rsquo;s going on, or just ask your House Leader!</p>\r\n<h3><strong>The Logistics</strong></h3>\r\n<h3>Moving In</h3>\r\n<p>The House Leader will provide you a key that opens the building &mdash; once inside you&rsquo;ll use the August app and the codes below to access your unit.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Apt 1</strong>: 0281</li>\r\n<li><strong>Apt 2</strong>: 8351</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Here&rsquo;s how to use the app:</p>\r\n<div class=\"fx w vc ch2\">\r\n<div><img style=\"width: 70%; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../files/uploads/august_lock.gif\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>When you move in, your House Leader will give you a tour of the house and talk to you a bit about the Outpost community. They&rsquo;ll also:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Take a photo of your ID (for our records and according to state law)</li>\r\n<li>Add you to your Messenger group</li>\r\n<li>Assign you cupboard and refrigerator space, according to your room number.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>The WiFi name is Outpost (or something similar) and the password is <strong>befreenyc</strong>.</p>\r\n<h3>Living at Outpost</h3>\r\n<p>You&rsquo;ll find helpful information linked above in our Guide to Responsible Coliving, but there are a few more things you should know:</p>\r\n<p><strong>Recycling is required</strong>, and New York City has strict guidelines. Watch the video below to see what you should recycle:</p>\r\n<iframe style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/EUyVELb5PzY\" width=\"70%\" height=\"400\"></iframe><br /><br />\r\n<p><strong>Cleanliness is also required.</strong> That&rsquo;s especially true of common areas, including shared rooms. Here are some easy ways to think about cleanliness at Outpost:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Leave rooms in the condition in which you found them</li>\r\n<li>Clean up after yourself</li>\r\n<li>Don&rsquo;t leave your belongings in the common area unless you&rsquo;re returning immediately</li>\r\n<li>Pay attention to the signs around the house: They&rsquo;re there to help our community run smoothly!</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Outpost is not responsible for lost or damaged mail or packages.</strong> Your House Leader will check the mail regularly. Make sure to put your full address, including your outside door code, in the delivery field when you order something. You may find your package left inside the main door, concealed outside, with a roommate who picked it up for you or returned to a distribution center for a later delivery. It&rsquo;s your responsibility to track your packages and make sure you&rsquo;re home to receive them when necessary.</p>\r\n</div>', 1, '40.81492000', '-73.94439000', 492, '', NULL),
(284, 253, NULL, 'the-apollo-manhattan-house', '', 'The Apollo Manhattan House', 'The Apollo Manhattan House | Outpost Club', '', 'The Apollo Manhattan House', '<p>Upper Manhattan, New York</p>\r\n<p>Private rooms from $1590</p>', '', '<div>\r\n<h6 class=\"h5\">The Scoop</h6>\r\n<p>The Apollo Manhattan House is located in the historic Harlem neighborhood, just a 14-minute walk from Central Park. The house is in the heart of the Harlem restaurant and bar scene, with abundant entertainment venues on your doorstep. The 2/3 subway station is just a 2-minute walk away at 125th Street, allowing you to get around the city quickly and easily.</p>\r\n<p>The Apollo Manhattan House consists of a single unit on the second floor of a beautiful Manhattan brownstone walkup, with only four units in the entire building. The house is one of our smallest in terms of members, with only three bedrooms, all of which are private. This gives the house a personal, community vibe, which is perfect for those who are new to the city. The unit has ample space compared with your average New York City apartment, all of which is recently renovated throughout.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h6 class=\"h5\">Location</h6>\r\n<p>This coliving space is located in the vibrant Harlem neighborhood, surrounded by restaurants, bars and live music venues. The house is just seconds away from Lower Lenox, known as Restaurant Row for the abundance of food and drink options available, and is in easy reach of the famous Apollo Theater and Central Park.</p>\r\n<p>The Apollo Manhattan House is only a 2-minute walk to the 2/3 trains at 125th Street Station and an 14-minute walk to the A/C and B/D trains at 125th &amp; St Nicholas Ave., plus multiple bus lines serve the neighborhood. The house is just 19 minutes to Times Square, 27 minutes to Rockefeller Center and 31 minutes to Wall Street. The City College of New York is just a 22-minute walk and Columbia University is just 23 minutes&rsquo; walking distance. Just one block from the house is the vibrant Marcus Garvey Park, plus Morningside Park and Central Park are both less than 15 minutes&rsquo; walking distance.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h6 class=\"h5\">The space</h6>\r\n<p>This recently renovated space features hardwood floors, all major appliances and plenty of natural light throughout. The kitchen and common areas are spacious compared to the average New York City apartment, with everything from a separate galley kitchen and large living area to spacious bedrooms, all furnished with everything you&rsquo;ll need for work and play.</p>\r\n<p><strong>This space is move-in ready; all you have to do is show up with your suitcase.</strong></p>\r\n</div>', 5, '', 'apollo-livingroom-2.jpg', 'apollo-bedroom-1.jpg', '', 428, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'The Apollo Manhattan House', 0, 0, 'a:7:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"title\";s:20:\"Throughout the house\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:1455:\"<p>{throughout}</p>\r\n<table class=\"table v2\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<th class=\"title\">\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><span class=\"gold\">Gold</span> Membership</p>\r\n<p class=\"price\">$690 One-Time Fee</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</th>\r\n<th colspan=\"2\">\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><span class=\"silver\">Silver</span> Membership</p>\r\n<p><span class=\"bronze\">Bronze</span> Membership</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p class=\"price\">$29 One-Time Fee</p>\r\n<p class=\"price\">No Fee*</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"2\"><em>*Bronze members must move in on <strong>the first day</strong> of the month</em></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<th>1-12 Months</th>\r\n<th>4+ Months</th>\r\n<th>1-3 Months</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Private</th>\r\n<td>$1590</td>\r\n<td>$1690</td>\r\n<td>$1790</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"5\">See the benefits of Bronze, Silver and Gold Membership <a class=\"red\" href=\"../memberships\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">here</a>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><em>**The prices shown indicate <strong>the prices valid for move-in between Dec. 15, 2019, and <em><strong>April 30</strong></em>, 2020</strong>. The exact price is indicated in your membership agreement and may vary depending on the length of commitment, your membership level and the size of your group, if applicable.</em></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div class=\"center\"><a class=\"button2\" href=\"join-us\">I`m interested</a></div>\";}i:1;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:12:\"The Bedrooms\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:4:\"body\";s:599:\"<p>Your room will be move-in ready, just like the rest of the house; there&rsquo;s no need to even bring a pillow. There are three bedrooms to choose from in the Apollo Manhattan House, all leading off the communal living room. Each bedroom features large windows overlooking the neighborhood as well as plenty of storage space.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Amenities: memory-foam mattresses, memory-foam pillows, extension cords to your bedside, shelving, hooks, bed linens, towels and closets/organizational tools.</li>\r\n<li>Services: Bed linens and towels will be available for you when you arrive.</li>\r\n</ul>\";s:6:\"images\";a:5:{i:0;s:20:\"apollo-bedroom-1.jpg\";i:1;s:20:\"apollo-bedroom-2.jpg\";i:2;s:20:\"apollo-bedroom-4.jpg\";i:3;s:20:\"apollo-bedroom-3.jpg\";i:4;s:20:\"apollo-bedroom-5.jpg\";}}i:2;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:24:\"The kitchens/dining room\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:731:\"<p>The Apollo Manhattan House features a separate galley kitchen with all major appliances, as well as counter space for cooking on your own or with a group. There is a dining table in the adjacent living room that can be used for eating, socializing or co-working, and both spaces are regularly cleaned by our in-house cleaning service. The kitchen is the gathering place for potluck dinners, solo meals and chats in the evening over a glass of wine.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Amenities include a gas stove, stainless-steel fridge, microwave, large sinks, a coffee maker, plenty of cabinets, cookware, tableware, cutting boards and anything else you would need in a kitchen.</li>\r\n<li>Security: 24/7 security in all common areas.</li>\r\n</ul>\";s:6:\"images\";a:2:{i:0;s:20:\"apollo-kitchen-1.jpg\";i:1;s:20:\"apollo-kitchen-2.jpg\";}}i:3;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:20:\"The co-working space\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:4:\"body\";s:170:\"<p>The living room serves as the principal co-working area for the Apollo Manhattan House. This open-plan room includes a dining table with ample room for co-working.</p>\";s:6:\"images\";a:2:{i:0;s:23:\"apollo-livingroom-2.jpg\";i:1;s:23:\"apollo-livingroom-1.jpg\";}}i:4;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"title\";s:13:\"The bathrooms\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:260:\"<p style=\"text-align: left;\">We provide many bathroom essentials, as well. There is one bathroom in the Apollo Manhattan House for only three bedrooms, so you&rsquo;ll never have to wait. The bathroom is regularly serviced by our in-house cleaning service.</p>\";}i:5;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"title\";s:19:\"Additional benefits\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:387:\"<p>Your Gold Membership gives you the opportunity to move between all our houses from month to month, allowing you to see what it&rsquo;s like to live in different neighborhoods and even in other cities.</p>\r\n<p><strong>We screen all candidates before approving applications so that there are no worries about moving into a new place with new people &mdash; only excitement!</strong></p>\";}i:6;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"title\";s:6:\"Prices\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:1892:\"<p>We have flexible month-to-month commitment options. We do not require extensive documents from you, guarantors or large deposits. A longer commitment on your side helps us to provide you with better prices.</p>\r\n<table class=\"table v2\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<th class=\"title\">\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><span class=\"gold\">Gold</span> Membership</p>\r\n<p class=\"price\">$690 One-Time Fee</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</th>\r\n<th colspan=\"2\">\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><span class=\"silver\">Silver</span> Membership</p>\r\n<p><span class=\"bronze\">Bronze</span> Membership</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p class=\"price\">$29 One-Time Fee</p>\r\n<p class=\"price\">No Fee*</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"2\"><em>*Bronze members must move in on <strong>the first day</strong> of the month</em></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<th>1-12 Months</th>\r\n<th>4+ Months</th>\r\n<th>1-3 Months</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Private</th>\r\n<td>$1590</td>\r\n<td>$1690</td>\r\n<td>$1790</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"5\">See the benefits of Bronze, Silver and Gold Membership <a class=\"red\" href=\"../memberships\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">here</a>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><em>**The prices shown indicate <strong>the prices valid for move-in between Dec. 15, 2019, and <em><strong>April 30</strong></em>, 2020</strong>. The exact price is indicated in your membership agreement and may vary depending on the length of commitment, your membership level and the size of your group, if applicable.</em></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div class=\"center\"><a class=\"button2\" href=\"join-us\">Get your exclusive offer now</a></div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Availability: Year-round / Minimum stay of 1 month / Month-to-month payment options available / Minimum age 18 / 30-day cancellation notice with Gold Membership</strong></p>\";}}', '', '', '', '', 0, '0.00000000', '0.00000000', 0, '', NULL),
(281, 253, NULL, 'upper-east-side-house', '', 'The Upper East Side House', 'Upper East Side (NYC) Room Rentals, Shared Apartments | Outpost Club', '', 'The Upper East Side House', '<p>Upper Manhattan, New York</p>\r\n<p>Shared rooms&nbsp;from $890 | Private rooms from $1390</p>', '', '<div>\r\n<h6 class=\"h5\">The Scoop</h6>\r\n<p>Our Upper East Side House is at the heart of the popular Upper East Side neighborhood. The house is in a vibrant yet leafy area, just a 5-minute walk from Carl Schurz Park and the East River and within walking distance of Central Park and cultural institutions like the Metropolitan Museum of Art.</p>\r\n<p>The Upper East Side House consists of five apartments spread across four floors in a classic five-floor New York City walkup. With multiple subway stations and bus stops within easy reach, it&rsquo;s a great base from which to commute downtown or to explore the city. Members enjoy spacious common areas within their apartment, including a living room and kitchen, plus the fifth-floor apartments enjoy access to a rooftop with views of the city.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h6 class=\"h5\">The Neighborhood</h6>\r\n<p>This coliving house is located in the beautiful Upper East Side neighborhood, filled with historic buildings, tranquil parks and renowned galleries, and within a short commute to all major business hubs and universities. The nearest subway station is 86th St. &amp; 2nd Ave., just an 8-minute walk, which is served by the Q, R, M and N trains, followed by the 4/5/6 trains at 86th St. &amp; Lexington, just a 10-minute walk away, plus multiple bus lines serve the neighborhood.</p>\r\n<p>You can be at Rockefeller Plaza or Times Square in less than 30 minutes, or the Financial District in 40 minutes. Plus, the neighborhood itself is filled with attractions to entertain your weekends or evenings. The Upper East Side House is a 5-minute walk from Carl Schurz Park, a 20-minute walk from Central Park and a 20-minute walk from the Metropolitan Museum of Art and the Neue Gallery, as well as being surrounded by numerous cafes and restaurants.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h6 class=\"h5\">The space</h6>\r\n<p>This space features hardwood floors, major appliances and exposed brick. The kitchen and common areas are roomy compared to the average New York City apartment, with open kitchens and living rooms, all furnished with everything you&rsquo;ll need for work and play.</p>\r\n<p><strong>This space is move-in ready; all you have to do is show up with your suitcase.</strong></p>\r\n</div>', 5, '', 'upper-east-side-bedroom.jpg', 'upper-east-side-bedroom.jpg', '', 398, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'The Upper East Side House', 0, 0, 'a:8:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"title\";s:20:\"Throughout the house\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:1600:\"<p>{throughout}</p>\r\n<table class=\"table v2\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<th class=\"title\">\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><span class=\"gold\">Gold</span> Membership</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</th>\r\n<th colspan=\"2\">\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><span class=\"silver\">Silver</span> Membership</p>\r\n<p><span class=\"bronze\">Bronze</span> Membership</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"2\"><em>*Bronze members must move in on <strong>the first day</strong> of the month</em></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<th>1-12 Months</th>\r\n<th>4+ Months</th>\r\n<th>1-3 Months</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Private (Standard Large)</th>\r\n<td>$1690</td>\r\n<td>$1790</td>\r\n<td>$1850</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Private (Standard)</th>\r\n<td>$1550</td>\r\n<td>$1690</td>\r\n<td>$1750</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Private (Economy)</th>\r\n<td>$1390</td>\r\n<td>$1490</td>\r\n<td>$1550</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>2-people shared</th>\r\n<td>$890</td>\r\n<td>$1050</td>\r\n<td>$1090</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"5\">See the benefits of Bronze, Silver and Gold Membership <a class=\"red\" href=\"../memberships\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">here</a>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><em>**The prices shown indicate <strong>the prices valid for move-in between June 1, 2020, and August 31, 2020</strong>. The exact price is indicated in your membership agreement and may vary depending on the length of commitment, your membership level and the size of your group, if applicable.</em></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div class=\"center\"><a class=\"button2 red\" href=\"join-us\" target=\"_blank\">Apply</a></div>\";}i:1;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:12:\"The Bedrooms\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:4:\"body\";s:557:\"<p>Your room will be move-in ready, just like the rest of the house; there&rsquo;s no need to even bring a pillow. There are five apartments in the Upper East Side House, three of which have four bedrooms, while the remainder have five or six bedrooms. This house consists of private rooms only, so you can relax away from the busyness of city life.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Amenities:</strong> memory-foam mattresses (twin-sized for shared rooms, full-sized for single rooms), pillows, shelving, hooks and closets/organizational tools.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\";s:6:\"images\";a:4:{i:0;s:27:\"upper-east-side-bedroom.jpg\";i:1;s:29:\"upper-east-side-bedroom12.jpg\";i:2;s:31:\"upper-east-side-bedroom-3-1.jpg\";i:3;s:29:\"upper-east-side-bedroom11.jpg\";}}i:2;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:24:\"The kitchens/dining room\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:4:\"body\";s:686:\"<p>The kitchens in each apartment feature many necessary appliances, with counter space for cooking on your own or with a group. Each kitchen includes a dining table that can be used for eating, socializing or co-working, as well as an adjacent living area for relaxing after work. The kitchen is the gathering place for potluck dinners, solo meals and chats in the evening over a glass of wine.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Many apartments&nbsp;include a gas stove, stainless-steel fridge, microwave, large sinks, a coffee maker, plenty of cabinets, cookware, tableware, cutting boards and anything else you would need in a kitchen.</li>\r\n<li>Security: 24/7 security in all common areas.</li>\r\n</ul>\";s:6:\"images\";a:3:{i:0;s:31:\"upper-east-side-livingroom2.jpg\";i:1;s:27:\"upper-east-side-kitchen.jpg\";i:2;s:31:\"upper-east-side-livingroom1.jpg\";}}i:3;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"title\";s:20:\"The co-working space\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:244:\"<p>The individual kitchens in every apartment serve as the principal co-working area for the Upper East Side House. These open-plan rooms feature dining tables with ample room for co-working and many of the bedrooms also include desk space.</p>\";}i:4;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:13:\"The bathrooms\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:480:\"<p>We provide many bathroom essentials, as well.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>toilet paper, shampoo, body wash, hand soap, and small garbage bags, which will never run out!&nbsp;</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p class=\"h5\">Laundry room</p>\r\n<p>The Upper East Side House also has a washer and dryer in every apartment where members can do their laundry for free in the comfort of their own home.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Security: 24/7 security in all common areas, as well as lockers.</li>\r\n</ul>\";s:6:\"images\";a:1:{i:0;s:28:\"upper-east-side-bathroom.jpg\";}}i:5;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:8:\"The roof\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:162:\"<p>The Upper East Side House features rooftop access for apartments located on the fifth floor, so you can enjoy ample outdoor space during the warmer months.</p>\";s:6:\"images\";a:2:{i:0;s:26:\"upper-east-side-roof-2.jpg\";i:1;s:26:\"upper-east-side-roof-1.jpg\";}}i:6;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"title\";s:19:\"Additional benefits\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:382:\"<p>Your Gold Membership gives you the opportunity to move between all our houses month to month, allowing you to see what it&rsquo;s like to live in different neighborhoods and even in other cities.</p>\r\n<p><strong>We screen all candidates before approving applications so that there are no worries about moving into a new place with new people &mdash; only excitement!</strong></p>\";}i:7;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"title\";s:6:\"Prices\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:2023:\"<p>We have flexible month-to-month commitment options. We do not require extensive documents from you, guarantors or large deposits. A longer commitment on your side helps us to provide you with better prices.</p>\r\n<table class=\"table v2\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<th class=\"title\">\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><span class=\"gold\">Gold</span> Membership</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</th>\r\n<th colspan=\"2\">\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><span class=\"silver\">Silver</span> Membership</p>\r\n<p><span class=\"bronze\">Bronze</span> Membership</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"2\"><em>*Bronze members must move in on <strong>the first day</strong> of the month</em></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<th>1-12 Months</th>\r\n<th>4+ Months</th>\r\n<th>1-3 Months</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Private (Standard Large)</th>\r\n<td>$1690</td>\r\n<td>$1790</td>\r\n<td>$1850</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Private (Standard)</th>\r\n<td>$1550</td>\r\n<td>$1690</td>\r\n<td>$1750</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Private (Economy)</th>\r\n<td>$1390</td>\r\n<td>$1490</td>\r\n<td>$1550</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>2-people shared</th>\r\n<td>$890</td>\r\n<td>$1050</td>\r\n<td>$1090</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"5\">See the benefits of Bronze, Silver and Gold Membership <a class=\"red\" href=\"../memberships\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">here</a>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><em>**The prices shown indicate <strong>the prices valid for move-in between June 1, 2020, and August 31, 2020</strong>. The exact price is indicated in your membership agreement and may vary depending on the length of commitment, your membership level and the size of your group, if applicable.</em></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div class=\"center\"><a class=\"button2 red\" href=\"join-us\" target=\"_blank\">Apply</a></div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Availability: Year-round / Minimum stay of 1 month / Month-to-month payment options available / Minimum age 18 / 30-day cancellation notice with Gold Membership</strong></p>\";}}', '', '', 'a:3:{i:0;s:3:\"185\";i:1;s:3:\"298\";i:2;s:3:\"280\";}', '', 0, '0.00000000', '0.00000000', 0, '', NULL);
