(289, 288, NULL, 'the-jersey-city-house', '', 'The Jersey City House', 'Journal Square (Jersey City) Room Rentals | Outpost Club', '', 'The Jersey City House', '<p>Journal Square, Jersey City</p>\r\n<p>Private rooms from $990</p>', '', '<div>\r\n<h6 class=\"h5\">The Scoop</h6>\r\n<p>Our Jersey City House is located on the second floor of a walk-up in the historic Journal Square area of Jersey City, New Jersey and is a short walk from public transportation and multiple historic sites of interest.</p>\r\n<p>The Jersey City House is one of our smallest houses in terms of members, with four private bedrooms. Members can enjoy a separate kitchen and common area and spacious bedrooms while home, and reach Manhattan in less than half an hour for work or nights out.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h6 class=\"h5\">Location</h6>\r\n<p>This coliving house is located in the revitalized Journal Square neighborhood, just a few blocks from our Journal Square House, and is only a short commute into New York City on public transportation and is an easy commute to downtown Jersey City and Hoboken.</p>\r\n<p>The house is a 10-minute walk from the Journal Square Transportation Center Path Plaza, where you can catch the Journal Square-33rd Street train into Midtown Manhattan, or the Newark-World Trade Center train into Lower Manhattan. Multiple bus lines also serve the neighborhood.</p>\r\n<p><strong>You can be in the Financial District in 25 minutes and to Times Square, Rockefeller Plaza or Downtown Brooklyn in 50 minutes.</strong></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h6 class=\"h5\">The space</h6>\r\n<p>The Jersey City House features hardwood floors, gas appliances and updated paint and tile work. The kitchen and common areas are cozy and welcoming. The best part? It&rsquo;s all furnished with everything you&rsquo;ll need for work and play, whether you&rsquo;re meal prepping or hosting a movie night.</p>\r\n<p><strong>This space is move-in ready; all you have to do is show up with your suitcase.</strong></p>\r\n</div>', 5, '', 'Journal-Square-Jersey-City-98-2-background.jpg', 'Journal-Square-Jersey-City-98-2-main.jpg', '', 481, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'The Jersey City House', 0, 0, 'a:7:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"title\";s:20:\"Throughout the house\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:1414:\"<p>{throughout}</p>\r\n<table class=\"table v2\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<th class=\"title\">\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><span class=\"gold\">Gold</span> Membership</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</th>\r\n<th colspan=\"2\">\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><span class=\"silver\">Silver</span> Membership</p>\r\n<p><span class=\"bronze\">Bronze</span> Membership</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"2\"><em>*Bronze members must move in on <strong>the first day</strong> of the month</em></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<th>1-12 Months</th>\r\n<th>4+ Months</th>\r\n<th>1-3 Months</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Private (Standart Large)</th>\r\n<td>$1200</td>\r\n<td>$1290</td>\r\n<td>$1350</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Private (Standart)</th>\r\n<td>$990</td>\r\n<td>$1090</td>\r\n<td>$1140</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"5\">See the benefits of Bronze, Silver, and Gold Membership <a class=\"red\" href=\"../memberships\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">here</a>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><em>**The prices shown indicate <strong>the prices valid for move-in between June 1, 2020, and August 31, 2020</strong>. The exact price is indicated in your membership agreement and may vary depending on the length of commitment, your membership level and the size of your group, if applicable.</em></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div class=\"center\"><a class=\"button2\" href=\"join-us\">I`m interested</a></div>\";}i:1;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:12:\"The Bedrooms\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:538:\"<p>Your room will be move-in ready, just like the rest of the house; there&rsquo;s no need to even bring a pillow. There are four private bedrooms in the Jersey City House.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Amenities</strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: memory-foam full-sized mattresses, memory-foam pillows, shelving, hooks and closets/organizational tools.</span></li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Services:</strong> <strong>If you are a Silver or Gold member, bed linens and towels will be available for you when you arrive.</strong></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\";s:6:\"images\";a:8:{i:0;s:40:\"Journal-Square-Jersey-City-bedroom-7.jpg\";i:1;s:40:\"Journal-Square-Jersey-City-bedroom-6.jpg\";i:2;s:40:\"Journal-Square-Jersey-City-bedroom-5.jpg\";i:3;s:40:\"Journal-Square-Jersey-City-bedroom-4.jpg\";i:4;s:45:\"Journal-Square-Jersey-City-98-2-bedroom-9.jpg\";i:5;s:40:\"Journal-Square-Jersey-City-bedroom-3.jpg\";i:6;s:40:\"Journal-Square-Jersey-City-bedroom-1.jpg\";i:7;s:40:\"Journal-Square-Jersey-City-bedroom-8.jpg\";}}i:2;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:24:\"The kitchens/dining room\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:601:\"<p>The kitchen in this house features gas appliances, with plenty of counter space for cooking on your own or with a group, and includes a dining table that can be used for eating, socializing or co-working. The kitchen is the gathering place for potluck dinners, solo meals and chats in the evening over a glass of wine.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Amenities include a gas stove, stainless-steel fridge, microwave, large sinks, a coffee maker, plenty of cabinets, cookware, tableware, cutting boards and anything else you would need in a kitchen.</li>\r\n<li>Security: 24/7 security in all common areas.</li>\r\n</ul>\";s:6:\"images\";a:3:{i:0;s:40:\"Journal-Square-Jersey-City-Kitchen-3.jpg\";i:1;s:40:\"Journal-Square-Jersey-City-Kitchen-4.jpg\";i:2;s:40:\"Journal-Square-Jersey-City-Kitchen-1.jpg\";}}i:3;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"title\";s:20:\"The co-working space\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:198:\"