(300, 253, NULL, 'the-mt-morris-park-house', '', 'The Mt. Morris Park House', 'Harlem (NYC) Room Rentals, Shared Apartments | Outpost Club', '', 'The Mt. Morris Park House', '<p>Manhattan, New York</p>\r\n<p>Private rooms from $1690</p>', '<h1 class=\"h1\">The Mt. Morris Park House</h1>\r\n<h4>This magnificent home in perfect condition is available for you to rent</h4>', '<div>\r\n<h6 class=\"h5\">The Scoop</h6>\r\n<p>The Mt. Morris Park House is in the heart of Harlem, surrounded by restaurants and cafes while still being within easy commuting distance of downtown Manhattan. The house is just one block from the 125th St. Station and is in close proximity to several higher education institutions and multiple parks.</p>\r\n<p>The Mt. Morris Park House is one of our smallest in terms of members, with only three bedrooms and five members, which gives it an intimate, communal feel. The house itself is a single unit situated on the third floor of a historic Manhattan walkup and newly renovated throughout.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h6 class=\"h5\">Location</h6>\r\n<p>This coliving space is located in the center of Harlem, in a lively neighborhood filled with restaurants, bars, cafes and live music venues. The house is just off Restaurant Row on Lower Lenox, with numerous food, drink and entertainment options at your doorstep, as well as the Apollo Theater within easy reach. The house is a 1-minute walk to the 2/3 trains at 125th St. Station and an 11-minute walk to the A/C and B/D trains at 125th &amp; St Nicholas Av., and multiple bus lines serve the neighborhood.</p>\r\n<p>The Mt. Morris Park House is just 22 minutes from Times Square and 30 minutes from Wall Street by subway. You can reach Columbia University in just 23 minutes walking and the City College of New York with a 22-minute walk. Just one block away is popular Marcus Garvey Park, plus Morningside Park and Central Park are both less than 15 minutes&rsquo; walking distance from the Mt. Morris Park House.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h6 class=\"h5\">The space</h6>\r\n<p>This newly renovated space features hardwood floors, updated appliances and exposed brick throughout. The kitchen and common areas are large compared to the average New York City apartment, with everything from a large living area and kitchen to spacious bedrooms, all furnished with everything you&rsquo;ll need for work and play.</p>\r\n<p><strong>This space is move-in ready; all you have to do is show up with your suitcase.</strong></p>\r\n</div>', 5, '', 'the-mt-morris-park-bedroom1.jpg', 'the-mt-morris-park-bedroom1.jpg', '', 429, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'The Mt. Morris Park House', 0, 0, 'a:7:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"title\";s:20:\"Throughout the house\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:1456:\"<p>{throughout}</p>\r\n<table class=\"table v2\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<th class=\"title\">\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><span class=\"gold\">Gold</span> Membership</p>\r\n<p class=\"price\">$690 One-Time Fee</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</th>\r\n<th colspan=\"2\">\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><span class=\"silver\">Silver</span> Membership</p>\r\n<p><span class=\"bronze\">Bronze</span> Membership</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p class=\"price\">$29 One-Time Fee</p>\r\n<p class=\"price\">No Fee*</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"2\"><em>*Bronze members must move in on <strong>the first day</strong> of the month</em></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<th>1-12 Months</th>\r\n<th>4+ Months</th>\r\n<th>1-3 Months</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Private</th>\r\n<td>$1690</td>\r\n<td>$1790</td>\r\n<td>$1890</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"5\">See the benefits of Bronze, Silver, and Gold Membership <a class=\"red\" href=\"../memberships\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">here</a>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><em>**The prices shown indicate <strong>the prices valid for move-in between Dec. 15, 20