(311, 254, NULL, 'nob-hill-house', 'nob-hill', 'Nob Hill House', 'Nob Hill (SF) Room Rentals, Shared Apartments | Outpost Club', '', 'Nob Hill House', '<p>Nob Hill, San Francisco</p>\r\n<p>Shared rooms from $990 | Private rooms from $1450</p>', '<h1 class=\"h1\">Nob Hill House</h1>\r\n<h4>This magnificent home in perfect condition is available for you to rent</h4>', '<div>\r\n<h6 class=\"h5\">The Scoop</h6>\r\n<p>Our Nob Hill House is at the heart of the popular, historic Nob Hill neighborhood. We chose Nob Hill because it&rsquo;s at the center of the action, a short commute from downtown and with plenty of entertainment options nearby. Transit links abound, with several bus stops, BART and a cable car station in close proximity and downtown within easy walking distance.</p>\r\n<p>Our Nob Hill House is a lively community of 14 private and shared rooms, with spacious common areas including a kitchen and living room. Members enjoy an expansive backyard as well as plenty of space for co-working and socializing.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h6 class=\"h5\">Location</h6>\r\n<p>This coliving house is located in the beautiful Nob Hill neighborhood, filled with historic buildings, leafy parks and entertainment options, within a short commute to downtown.</p>\r\n<p>The Nob Hill House is a 19-minute walk to Union Square and a 16-minute walk to Civic Center. The closest BART station is Civic Center, while both the California St. &amp; Larkin St. stop on the cable car and a local bus stop are all just a 2-minute walk away, which means you can be in the Financial District in under 15 minutes. The house is also a walking distance from the Market St. and 5th St. Muni stop.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h6 class=\"h5\">The space</h6>\r\n<p>This newly renovated space features hardwood floors and updated appliances. The kitchen and common areas are massive compared to the average San Francisco apartment, with everything from a large living area to a spacious backyard included, all furnished with everything you&rsquo;ll need for work and play.</p>\r\n<p><strong>This space is move-in ready; all you have to do is show up with your suitcase.</strong></p>\r\n</div>', 5, '', 'nob-hill-house-main.jpg', 'nob-hill-house-background.jpg', '', 529, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Nob Hill House', 0, 0, 'a:8:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"title\";s:20:\"Throughout the house\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:1581:\"<p>{throughout}</p>\r\n<table class=\"table v2\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<th class=\"title\">\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><span class=\"gold\">Gold</span> Membership</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</th>\r\n<th colspan=\"2\">\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><span class=\"silver\">Silver</span> Membership</p>\r\n<p><span class=\"bronze\">Bronze</span> Membership</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"2\"><em>*Bronze members must move in on <strong>the first day</strong> of the month</em></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<th>1-12 Months</th>\r\n<th>4+ Months</th>\r\n<th>1-3 Months</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Private (Standart)</th>\r\n<td>$2050</td>\r\n<td>$2200</td>\r\n<td>$2300</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Private (Economy)</th>\r\n<td>$1650</td>\r\n<td>$1800</td>\r\n<td>$1900</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>2-people shared</th>\r\n<td>$1100</td>\r\n<td>$1250</td>\r\n<td>$1350</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>2-people shared</th>\r\n<td>$990</td>\r\n<td>$1150</td>\r\n<td>$1190</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"5\">See the benefits of Bronze, Silver, and Gold Membership <a class=\"red\" href=\"../memberships\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">here</a>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><em>**The prices shown indicate <strong>the prices valid for move-in between June 1, 2020, and August 31, 2020</strong>. The exact price is indicated in your membership agreement and may vary depending on the length of commitment, your membership level and the size of your group, if applicable.</em></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div class=\"center\"><a class=\"button2\" href=\"join-us\">I`m interested</a></div>\";}i:1;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:12:\"The Bedrooms\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:4:\"body\";s:648:\"<p>Your room will be move-in ready, just like the rest of the house; there&rsquo;s no need to even bring a pillow. There are 14 bedrooms in the Nob Hill House with a choice of private or shared rooms, depending on availability and your price range.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Amenities</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: memory-foam full-sized mattresses, memory-foam pillows, shelving, hooks and closets/organizational tools.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Gold and Silver members: </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Bed linens and towels will be available for you when you arrive.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\";s:6:\"images\";a:10:{i:0;s:29:\"nob-hill-house-background.jpg\";i:1;s:28:\"nob-hill-house-bedroom-6.jpg\";i:2;s:28:\"nob-hill-house-bedroom-5.jpg\";i:3;s:28:\"nob-hill-house-bedroom-7.jpg\";i:4;s:28:\"nob-hill-house-bedroom-3.jpg\";i:5;s:28:\"nob-hill-house-bedroom-2.jpg\";i:6;s:28:\"nob-hill-house-bedroom-1.jpg\";i:7;s:28:\"nob-hill-house-bedroom-4.jpg\";i:8;s:23:\"nob-hill-bedroom-11.jpg\";i:9;s:23:\"nob-hill-bedroom-10.jpg\";}}i:2;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:24:\"The kitchens/dining room\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:807:\"<p>The large kitchen features updated appliances, with plenty of counter space for cooking on your own or with a group, and of course a spacious fridge. There is also a large dining table which can be used for eating, socializing or co-working. The kitchen is the center of potluck dinners, solo meals and chats in the evening over a glass of wine.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Amenities include a gas stove, stainless-steel fridge, microwave, large sinks, a coffee maker, plenty of cabinets, cookware, tableware, cutting boards and anything else you would need in a kitchen.</li>\r\n<li>Also included: salt, pepper, sugar, coffee grounds, tea, olive oil, paper towels, dish soap, hand soap and garbage/recycling bags, all of which are routinely restocked.</li>\r\n<li>Security: 24/7 security in all common areas.</li>\r\n</ul>\";s:6:\"images\";a:4:{i:0;s:28:\"nob-hill-house-kitchen-3.jpg\";i:1;s:28:\"nob-hill-house-kitchen-2.jpg\";i:2;s:28:\"nob-hill-house-kitchen-1.jpg\";i:3;s:20:\"nob-hill-house-4.jpg\";}}i:3;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:20:\"The co-working space\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:4:\"body\";s:391:\"<p>The large kitchen serves as the principal common area for the Nob Hill House. This open-plan room features a large dining table with ample room for co-working and you can also use the desk space throughout the house and within the bedrooms for your remote working needs. This space also includes a printer (paper and ink included) to make sure you\'ll always be ready to be productive.</p>\";s:6:\"images\";a:3:{i:0;s:30:\"nob-hill-house-coworking-1.jpg\";i:1;s:30:\"nob-hill-house-coworking-2.jpg\";i:2;s:30:\"nob-hill-house-coworking-3.jpg\";}}i:4;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:13:\"The bathrooms\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:613:\"<p>We provide many bathroom essentials, as well. There are four full bathrooms and two half bathrooms in the Nob Hill House, so you&rsquo;ll never have to wait.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Also included: toilet paper, shampoo, body wash, hand soap and small garbage bags, which will never run out! We also provide hair dryers, so there\'s no need to bring your own.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>LAUNDRY ROOM</p>\r\n<p>The Nob Hill House also has a washer and dryer where members can do their laundry for free in the comfort of their own home.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Security: 24/7 security in all common areas, as well as lockers.</li>\r\n</ul>\";s:6:\"images\";a:4:{i:0;s:29:\"nob-hill-house-bathroom-3.jpg\";i:1;s:29:\"nob-hill-house-bathroom-2.jpg\";i:2;s:26:\"nob-hill-house-luyndry.jpg\";i:3;s:29:\"nob-hill-house-bathroom-1.jpg\";}}i:5;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"title\";s:8:\"Backyard\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:251:\"<p>The Nob Hill House features a spacious backyard where members can socialize, including an ample seating area and a grill for the warmer months. This is the perfect place to read a book or get to know your roommates on beautiful California days.</p>\";}i:6;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"title\";s:19:\"Additional benefits\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:382:\"<p>Your Gold Membership gives you the opportunity to move between all our houses month to month, allowing you to see what it&rsquo;s like to live in different neighborhoods and even in other cities.</p>\r\n<p><strong>We screen all candidates before approving applications so that there are no worries about moving into a new place with new people &mdash; only excitement!</strong></p>\";}i:7;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"title\";s:6:\"Prices\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:2018:\"<p>We have flexible month-to-month commitment options. We do not require extensive documents from you, guarantors or large deposits. A longer commitment on your side helps us to provide you with better prices.</p>\r\n<table class=\"table v2\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<th class=\"title\">\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><span class=\"gold\">Gold</span> Membership</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</th>\r\n<th colspan=\"2\">\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><span class=\"silver\">Silver</span> Membership</p>\r\n<p><span class=\"bronze\">Bronze</span> Membership</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"2\"><em>*Bronze members must move in on <strong>the first day</strong> of the month</em></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<th>1-12 Months</th>\r\n<th>4+ Months</th>\r\n<th>1-3 Months</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Private (Standart)</th>\r\n<td>$2050<