(330, 253, 301, 'stuyvesant-heights-house', '', 'The Stuyvesant Heights House', 'Stuyvesant Heights House (NY 11221) | The Outpost Club', 'Affordable & 100% furnished rooms for rent in a coliving house in Stuyvesant Heights, Brooklyn. Submit a free application today and receive an exclusive offer with all inclusive pricing. ', 'Stuyvesant Heights House | The Outpost Club', '<p>Stuyvesant Heights, Brooklyn</p>\r\n<p>Private rooms from $1260</p>', '<h1 class=\"h1 center\">The Stuyvesant Heights House</h1>\r\n<h4>A SPACIOUS HOME IN A LIVELY NEIGHBORHOOD</h4>', '<div>\r\n<h6 class=\"h5\">The Scoop</h6>\r\n<p>The Stuyvesant Heights House is located in the historic Stuyvesant Heights neighborhood in Brooklyn. This Renaissance Revival-style home epitomizes historic Brooklyn architecture, with high ceilings, large windows and exposed brick throughout.</p>\r\n<p>The Stuyvesant Heights House consists of eight units spread across the four floors of living space within this classic Brooklyn row house. Multiple subway stations and bus stops are within walking distance, making it a great base from which to commute into Manhattan or explore the rest of Brooklyn.</p>\r\n<p>This house is a six-unit property with&nbsp;hardwood floors, updated appliances and exposed brick throughout. The kitchen and common areas are open, with high ceilings and exposed beams, and the bedrooms have large windows to let plenty of light in. The apartments are all furnished with everything you&rsquo;ll need for work and play.</p>\r\n<p><strong>The space is move-in ready; all you have to do is show up with your suitcase.</strong></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h6 class=\"h5\">Location</h6>\r\n<p>This coliving house is located in the historic Stuyvesant Heights neighborhood, filled with historic Brooklyn brownstones along tree-lined streets, and within walking distance of plenty of restaurants, bars and coffee shops. The closest subway station is Utica Ave., served by the A and C trains and just a 11-minute walk away, followed by the Kosciuszko Street Station, served by the J train and just a 12-minute walk away. Multiple bus lines also serve the neighborhood.</p>\r\n<p>You can reach the exciting Lower East Side neighborhood in less than half an hour, as well as Lower Manhattan in 30 minutes and Midtown Manhattan in 40 minutes.</p>\r\n</div>', 5, '', 'Copy of 662-madison-street-3r-4.jpg', 'Copy of 662-madison-stret-4l-3.jpg', '', 280, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'The Stuyvesant Heights House', 0, 0, 'a:8:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"title\";s:20:\"Throughout the house\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:590:\"<p>{throughout}</p>\r\n<table class=\"table v2\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<th>12+ Months</th>\r\n<th>5-11 Months</th>\r\n<th>1-4 Months</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Private (Large)</th>\r\n<td>$1340</td>\r\n<td>$1420</td>\r\n<td>$2020</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Private (Standard)</th>\r\n<td>$1260</td>\r\n<td>$1340</td>\r\n<td>$1940</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"5\">\r\n<p>*Prices above do not include $149/month/person utilities allowance fee</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div class=\"center\"><a class=\"button2 red\" href=\"online-questionnaire\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Apply for free</a></div>\";}i:1;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:12:\"The Bedrooms\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:4:\"body\";s:413:\"<p>There are eight individual units in the Stuyvesant Heights House, each with four or five bedrooms. This house consists of private rooms only, so you can relax away from the busyness of city life. Bedding is available for an additional fee.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Amenities</strong>: memory-foam mattresses, pillows, extension cords to your bedside, shelving, hooks and closets/organizational tools.</li>\r\n</ul>\";s:6:\"images\";a:6:{i:0;s:35:\"Copy of 662-madison-street-2l-4.jpg\";i:1;s:35:\"Copy of 662-madison-street-2r-1.jpg\";i:2;s:35:\"Copy of 662-madison-street-3l-2.jpg\";i:3;s:35:\"Copy of 662-madison-street-3l-4.jpg\";i:4;s:35:\"Copy of 662-madison-street-3r-3.jpg\";i:5;s:35:\"Copy of 662-madison-street-3l-5.jpg\";}}i:2;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:24:\"The kitchens/dining room\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:707:\"<p>The kitchen in each apartment features updated appliances, with plenty of counter space for cooking on your own or with a group. Each kitchen includes a dining table that can be used for eating, socializing or co-working, as well as an adjacent living area for relaxing after work. The kitchen is the gathering place for dinners, solo meals and chats in the evening over a glass of wine.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Amenities</strong> include a gas stove, stainless-steel fridge, dishwasher, microwave, large sinks, a coffee maker, plenty of cabinets, cookware, tableware, cutting boards and plenty of other kitchen supplies.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Security</strong>: 24/7 security in all common areas.</li>\r\n</ul>\";s:6:\"images\";a:1:{i:0;s:36:\"stuyvesant-heights-house-kitchen.jpg\";}}i:3;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"title\";s:22:\" The (co)working space\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:201:\"<p>The individual kitchens in every apartment serve as the principal co-working area for the Stuyvesant Heights House. These open-plan rooms feature large dining tables with ample room for working.</p>\";}i:4;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:13:\"The bathrooms\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:484:\"<p>We provide many bathroom essentials, as well. Every apartment in the Stuyvesant Heights House has two bathrooms, so you&rsquo;ll never have to wait.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Services: </strong>toilet paper, hand soap and small garbage bags, which will never run out!<strong>&nbsp;</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p class=\"h5\">Laundry room</p>\r\n<p>The Stuyvesant Heights House also has a washer and dryer in the basement, so you can do your laundry in the comfort of your own home.</p>\";s:6:\"images\";a:3:{i:0;s:41:\"stuyvesant-heights-house-bathroom-4_1.jpg\";i:1;s:41:\"stuyvesant-heights-house-bathroom-8_1.jpg\";i:2;s:42:\"stuyvesant-heights-house-bathroom-11_1.jpg\";}}i:5;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"title\";s:19:\"PERKS AND BENEFITS:\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:641:\"<div class=\"fx ch3 w perc_advantages\">\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Fast, reliable WiFi</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Regular professional cleaning</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Furnished interiors</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">In-unit laundry</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Keyless entry</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Large windows</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Community events</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Dedicated community manager</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Updated appliances</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Dedicated maintenance team</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\";}i:6;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"title\";s:6:\"Prices\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:748:\"<table class=\"table v2\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<th>12+ Months</th>\r\n<th>5-11 Months</th>\r\n<th>1-4 Months</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Private (Large)</th>\r\n<td>$1340</td>\r\n<td>$1420</td>\r\n<td>$2020</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Private (Standard)</th>\r\n<td>$1260</td>\r\n<td>$1340</td>\r\n<td>$1940</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"5\">\r\n<p>*Prices above do not include $149/month/person utilities allowance fee</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div class=\"center\"><a class=\"button2 red\" href=\"online-questionnaire\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Apply for free</a></div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Availability: Year-round / Minimum stay of 1 month / Month-to-month payment options available / Minimum age 18</strong></p>\";}i:7;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:30:\"Welcome to Bed-Stuy, Brooklyn.\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:4:\"body\";s:640:\"<div>\r\n<p>Walk off the train and into this historic Brooklyn neighborhood that feels like home with its quaint, brownstone-lined streets and vibrant culture. Immerse yourself in the community and you&rsquo;ll find unique locally owned shops, neighbors who are always up for a good conversation, and a rich history worth honoring. The neighborhood features the lively Herbert Von King park, trendy coffee shops like Brooklyn Blend and eclectic cuisine ranging from Caribbean to Japanese. You can explore surrounding neighborhoods like Clinton Hill and Williamsburg by foot, or hop on the subway and be in Manhattan in 30 minutes.</p>\r\n</div>\";s:6:\"images\";a:4:{i:0;s:58:\"aee22cb703e77c3c63e13bf273a93b2f-rimg-w720-h478-gmir_4.jpg\";i:1;s:27:\"bed-stuy_corcoran_08_12.jpg\";i:2;s:34:\"bed-stuy-brooklyn-new-york-4_4.jpg\";i:3;s:60:\"Fulton-street-brooklyn-bedford-stuyvesant-nyc-new-york_4.jpg\";}}}', '', '', '', '', 2, '40.68670000', '-73.93169000', 500, '', '2022-09-22 17:15:24'),
