(479, 253, 364, 'the-gramercy-park-studios', '', 'The Gramercy Park Studios', 'The Gramercy Park Studios (NY 10010) | Outpost Club', 'We worked with interior designers to make The Gramercy Park Studios comfortable in every room. ✓ Fully furnished ✓ Security ✓ Gas ✓ Electricity ✓ Water ✓ Wi-Fi ✓ Cleaning and maintenance', 'The Gramercy Park Studios | Outpost Club', '<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Gramercy Park,</span> Manhattan</p>\r\n<p>Private rooms from $3300</p>', '<h1 class=\"h1 center\">The Gramercy Park Studios</h1>\r\n<h4>PRIVATE ROOMS IN HISTORIC NOMAD</h4>', '<div>\r\n<h6 class=\"h5\">Scoop</h6>\r\n<p>The newly renovated Gramercy House is located in Manhattan&rsquo;s NoMad neighborhood, just across Madison Square Park from the Flatiron building.</p>\r\n<p>The main draw: The Gramercy House has just been reopened after a full renovation. Plus, you&rsquo;ll be steps from Madison Square Park.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Perfect for you if: You want Manhattan energy but want nearby green space to escape to.</strong></p>\r\n<p>Our suggestion: Grab your favorite book, stop by a coffee cart and find an open bench in Madison Square Park, just a 2-minute walk from the Gramercy House. Starting your Sunday morning relaxing in the park is the perfect way to start the week fresh.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h6 class=\"h5\">Location</h6>\r\n<p>The Gramercy House is surrounded by transit options. The closest subway stop is the 28 St 4/6 station, just one avenue over, about a 3-minute walk. The 28 St N/Q/R/W stop is just a 4-minute walk away, and the 23 St F, M and PATH stop is a 9-minute walk away. You can also walk 13 minutes to the 23 St 1/2 stop. Multiple Manhattan and Bronx bus routes also stop just a block away. The closest CitiBike station is just an avenue away, a 3-minute walk.</p>\r\n</div>', 5, '', 'the-gramercy-park-studios-bedroom-3.jpg', 'the-gramercy-park-studios-bedroom-3.jpg', '', 291, 1, 1, 0, 1, 'The Gramercy Park Studios', 0, 0, 'a:3:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:25:\"The Gramercy Park Studios\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:6:\"images\";a:10:{i:0;s:39:\"the-gramercy-park-studios-bedroom-3.jpg\";i:1;s:39:\"the-gramercy-park-studios-bedroom-7.jpg\";i:2;s:39:\"the-gramercy-park-studios-bedroom-6.jpg\";i:3;s:39:\"the-gramercy-park-studios-bedroom-5.jpg\";i:4;s:39:\"the-gramercy-park-studios-bedroom-4.jpg\";i:5;s:40:\"the-gramercy-park-studios-bathroom-3.jpg\";i:6;s:39:\"the-gramercy-park-studios-bedroom-1.jpg\";i:7;s:39:\"the-gramercy-park-studios-bedroom-2.jpg\";i:8;s:40:\"the-gramercy-park-studios-bathroom-4.jpg\";i:9;s:40:\"the-gramercy-park-studios-bathroom-2.jpg\";}s:4:\"body\";s:1228:\"<div>\r\n<p>Every room at the Gramercy House is newly renovated and fully furnished. Each room includes a full-size bed, desk and flat-screen TV, as well as a microwave and mini-fridge for your convenience. Air conditioning is via window units, meaning you&rsquo;ll always have control over the temperature in your room.</p>\r\n<p>The building itself is an 11-story elevator building in the NoMad (&ldquo;North of Madison Square Park\'\') neighborhood. Step inside and you&rsquo;ll find a newly re-designed hotel lobby with room to lounge.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<table class=\"table v2\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<th>12+ Months</th>\r\n<th>5-11 Months</th>\r\n<th>1-4 Months</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Extra Large Studio</th>\r\n<td>$4100</td>\r\n<td>$4200</td>\r\n<td>$4500</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Standard Large Studio</th>\r\n<td>$3600</td>\r\n<td>$3750</td>\r\n<td>$3950</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Standard Double Studio</th>\r\n<td>$3400</td>\r\n<td>$3600</td>\r\n<td>$3750</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Standard Studio</th>\r\n<td>$3300</td>\r\n<td>$3500</td>\r\n<td>$3750</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"5\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div class=\"center\"><a class=\"button2 red\" href=\"cassa-application\" rel=\"nofollow\">Check Availability</a></div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\";}i:1;O:8:\"stdClass\":