(391, 253, 315, 'the-bedford-house', '', 'The Bedford House', 'The Bedford House (NY 11221) | Outpost Club', 'We worked with interior designers to make The Bedford House comfortable in every room. ✓ Fully furnished ✓ Security ✓ Gas ✓ Electricity ✓ Water ✓ Wi-Fi ✓ Cleaning and maintenance', 'The Bedford House | Outpost Club', '<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Bedford-Stuyvesant</span>, Brooklyn</p>\r\n<p>Private rooms from $1450</p>', '<h1 class=\"h1 center\">The Bedford House</h1>\r\n<h4>BUILDING COMMUNITY IN HISTORIC BED-STUY</h4>', '<div>\r\n<p>As you enjoy the newly built Bedford House in the heart of Bed-Stuy, you&rsquo;ll meet people from every corner of the world, building a community from the comfort of your home while being within easy reach of all New York City has to offer. This historic, lively neighborhood features the popular Herbert Von King park, locally owned cafes and shops like Black Swan and the Mixtape Shop, and diverse cuisine ranging from Caribbean to Japanese.</p>\r\n<p><strong class=\"text_red\">The main draw</strong>: The spacious, furnished backyard, a luxury in New York and the perfect way to spend long summer evenings with your housemates.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Perfect for you if:</strong> You want to contribute to a community where neighbors support local businesses and get to know each other over spontaneous stoop hangs.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Our suggestion:</strong> Get to know Herbert Von King Park, a bustling green space right at the end of the block. Step outside the Bedford House and within just a couple of minutes, you&rsquo;ll be able to settle in to read a book, people watch or just relax for a minute away from the craziness of the city.</p>\r\n</div>', 5, '', 'the-bedford-house-bedroom-10.jpg', 'the-bedford-house-bedroom-10.jpg', '', 289, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'The Bedford House', 0, 0, 'a:9:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"title\";s:20:\"Throughout the house\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:605:\"<p>{throughout}</p>\r\n<table class=\"table v2\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<th>12+ Months</th>\r\n<th>5-11 Months</th>\r\n<th>1-4 Months</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Private (Large room with desk)</th>\r\n<td>$1510</td>\r\n<td>$1590</td>\r\n<td>$2190</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Private (Standard)</th>\r\n<td>$1450</td>\r\n<td>$1530</td>\r\n<td>$2130</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"5\">\r\n<p>*Prices above do not include $149/month/person utilities allowance fee</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div class=\"center\"><a class=\"button2 red\" href=\"online-questionnaire\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Apply for free</a></div>\";}i:1;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:12:\"The Bedrooms\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:4:\"body\";s:417:\"<p>All of the bedrooms in the Bedford House are private and feature full-sized beds, desks and closets, with bedding available for an additional fee. The basement shared lounge is equipped with comfortable couches and a 55-inch TV, perfect for a movie night with your housemates! Also in the basement, you&rsquo;ll find a coin-operated washer and dryer, so you can do your laundry in the comfort of your own home.</p>\";s:6:\"images\";a:6:{i:0;s:32:\"the-bedford-house-bedroom-11.jpg\";i:1;s:31:\"the-bedford-house-bedroom-5.jpg\";i:2;s:32:\"the-bedford-house-bedroom-10.jpg\";i:3;s:31:\"the-bedford-house-bedroom-7.jpg\";i:4;s:31:\"the-bedford-house-bedroom-6.jpg\";i:5;s:31:\"the-bedford-house-bedroom-8.jpg\";}}i:2;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:19:\"The (Co)Living Room\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:4:\"body\";s:338:\"<p>The common living room is located in the basement of the Bedford House. This is where members can go to relax and hang out and is equipped with comfortable couches and a 55-inch TV, perfect for any Outpost movie night!</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Google Chromecast</li>\r\n<li><strong>Security</strong>: 24/7 security in all common areas.</li>\r\n</ul>\";s:6:\"images\";a:4:{i:0;s:32:\"the-bedford-house-coliving-4.jpg\";i:1;s:32:\"the-bedford-house-coliving-1.jpg\";i:2;s:32:\"the-bedford-house-coliving-3.jpg\";i:3;s:32:\"the-bedford-house-coliving-2.jpg\";}}i:3;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:24:\"The Kitchens/Dining Room\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:560:\"<p>In these units, the kitchen and dining room are the first rooms you enter, located on the bottom floor of each unit. These open spaces are used for cooking up dinner with friends and relaxing in the evening over a glass of wine.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Amenities</strong> include electric stoves, stainless-steel fridges, microwaves, large sinks, coffee makers, blenders, plenty of cabinets, cookware, tableware, cutting boards and anything else you would need in a kitchen.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Security</strong>: 24/7 security in all common areas.</li>\r\n</ul>\";s:6:\"images\";a:5:{i:0;s:31:\"the-bedford-house-kitchen-2.jpg\";i:1;s:31:\"the-bedford-house-kitchen-3.jpg\";i:2;s:31:\"the-bedford-house-kitchen-4.jpg\";i:3;s:31:\"the-bedford-house-kitchen-1.jpg\";i:4;s:31:\"the-bedford-house-kitchen-5.jpg\";}}i:4;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:13:\"The bathrooms\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:511:\"<p>Every unit in the Bedford House is equipped with enough shared bathrooms that you can be sure you&rsquo;ll never have to wait.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Also included</strong>: toilet paper, hand soap and small garbage bags, which will never be empty! We also provide hairdryers, so there&rsquo;s no need to bring your own.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"h5\">Laundry room</p>\r\n<p>The Bedford House has a coin-operated washer and dryer in the basement, so you can do all your laundry in the comfort of your own home.</p>\";s:6:\"images\";a:3:{i:0;s:32:\"the-bedford-house-bathroom-2.jpg\";i:1;s:32:\"the-bedford-house-bathroom-5.jpg\";i:2;s:32:\"the-bedford-house-bathroom-1.jpg\";}}i:5;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:8:\"Backyard\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:4:\"body\";s:219:\"<p>One of the highlights of the Bedford House is the common backyard. This sun-drenched area has plenty of seating and furniture so housemates can work, read or relax outside in the warmer months and catch some sun.</p>\";s:6:\"images\";a:1:{i:0;s:30:\"the-bedford-house-backyard.jpg\";}}i:6;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"title\";s:20:\"PERKS AND BENEFITS: \";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:652:\"<div class=\"fx ch3 w perc_advantages\">\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Fast, reliable WiFi</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Regular professional cleaning</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Furnished interiors</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Furnished backyard</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Keyless entry</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Coin-operated laundry</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Community events</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Dedicated community manager</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Updated appliances</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Dedicated maintenance team</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\";}i:7;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"title\";s:6:\"Prices\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:763:\"<table class=\"table v2\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<th>12+ Months</th>\r\n<th>5-11 Months</th>\r\n<th>1-4 Months</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Private (Large room with desk)</th>\r\n<td>$1510</td>\r\n<td>$1590</td>\r\n<td>$2190</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Private (Standard)</th>\r\n<td>$1450</td>\r\n<td>$1530</td>\r\n<td>$2130</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"5\">\r\n<p>*Prices above do not include $149/month/person utilities allowance fee</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div class=\"center\"><a class=\"button2 red\" href=\"online-questionnaire\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Apply for free</a></div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Availability: Year-round / Minimum stay of 1 month / Month-to-month payment options available / Minimum age 18</strong></p>\";}i:8;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:19:\"Welcome to Bed-Stuy\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:4:\"body\";s:1004:\"<div>\r\n<p>Walk off the train and into this historic Brooklyn neighborhood that feels like home with its quaint, brownstone-lined streets and vibrant culture. Immerse yourself in the community and you&rsquo;ll find unique locally owned shops, neighbors who are always up for a good conversation, and a rich history worth honoring. The neighborhood features the lively Herbert Von King park, trendy coffee shops like Brooklyn Blend and eclectic cuisine ranging from Caribbean to Japanese. You can explore surrounding neighborhoods like Clinton Hill and Williamsburg by foot, or hop on the subway and be in Manhattan in 30 minutes.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h6 class=\"h5\">Location</h6>\r\n<p>The closest subway station to the Bedford House is Bedford-Nostrand, served by the G train and just a 8-minute walk away. Multiple bus lines also serve the neighborhood. You can reach the Lower East Side in 30 minutes and Midtown Manhattan in 45 minutes, or easily explore Downtown Brooklyn in just 15 minutes.</p>\r\n</div>\";s:6:\"images\";a:4:{i:0;s:58:\"aee22cb703e77c3c63e13bf273a93b2f-rimg-w720-h478-gmir_1.jpg\";i:1;s:26:\"bed-stuy_corcoran_08_9.jpg\";i:2;s:34:\"bed-stuy-brooklyn-new-york-4_1.jpg\";i:3;s:60:\"Fulton-street-brooklyn-bedford-stuyvesant-nyc-new-york_1.jpg\";}}}', '', '', 'a:3:{i:0;s:3:\"383\";i:1;s:3:\"293\";i:2;s:3:\"330\";}', '', 2, '40.68954000', '-73.94300000', 497, '', '2022-08-22 15:00:11'),
