(420, 121, NULL, 'do-i-need-renters-insurance', '', 'Do I need renters insurance?', 'Do I need renters insurance?', '', 'Do I need renters insurance?', '', '', '<p class=\"p1\">Outpost Club requires renters insurance for all tenants. If you already have renters insurance, great! Please send us proof of your policy&nbsp;when you&rsquo;re in the process of security your spot. If you don&rsquo;t have it, Outpost Club partners with Sure Insurance to give you the best deal possible on renters insurance, which&nbsp;covers your items even after you move out of our property. If you leave Outpost, just make sure to let Sure Insurance know you have moved and your items will be covered at your new home.</p>', 6, '', '', '', '', 136, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'Do I need renters insurance?', 0, 0, 'a:0:{}', '', '', '', '', 0, '0.00000000', '0.00000000', 0, '', NULL),
(421, 121, NULL, 'the-renters-insurance-company-you-partner-with-sure-insurance-is-requiring-me-to-sign-up-for-a-full-year-but-im-staying-with-you-for-less-than-a-year-do-i-need-to-sign-up-for-the-year', '', 'The renters insurance company you partner with (Sure Insurance) is requiring me to sign up for a full year, but I’m only staying with you for less than a year. Do I need to sign up for the year?', 'The renters insurance company you partner with (Sure Insurance) is requiring me to sign up for a full year, but I’m staying with you for less than a year. Do I need to sign up for the year?', '', 'The renters insurance company you partner with (Sure Insurance) is requiring me to sign up for a full year, but I’m staying with you for less than a year. Do I need to sign up for the year?', '', '', '<p class=\"p1\">The great thing about SURE Insurance is that they will cover you even if you move, just tell them your new home address, and they will transfer your coverage there!</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">If you still want to cancel however, you cancel the renters insurance policy at any point. You would receive a pro-rated refund for time not used. What that means: if you got set up with the annual billing option and cancelled after 3 months, you would be refunded the 9 months of unearned premium. Additionally, if you went with the monthly payment option and canceled 15 days into the month, you would be refunded the 15 days that the policy was inactive. There are also no cancellation fees!</p>', 6, '', '', '', '', 137, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'The renters insurance company you partner with (Sure Insurance) is requiring me to sign up for a full year, but I’m staying with you for less than a year. Do I need to sign up for the year?', 0, 0, 'a:0:{}', '', '', '', '', 0, '0.00000000', '0.00000000', 0, '', NULL),
(424, 429, NULL, 'cassa-studios', '', 'The Cassa Studios and Residences', 'Cassa Studio Apartments Near Times Square', 'Affordable & 100% furnished studio apartments near Times Square. Submit a free application today and receive an exclusive offer with all inclusive pricing. ', 'The Cassa Studios and Recidences', '<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Manhattan</span></p>', '<h1 class=\"h1 center\">The Cassa Studios and Residences</h1>\r\n<h4>The Cassa Studios offers a variety of common spaces for your use and enjoyment during your stay</h4>', '<div>\r\n<h6 class=\"h5\">The Scoop</h6>\r\n<p>Cassa Studios and Residences powered by Outpost are just a short walk from Times Square in Manhattan, within easy reach of New York&rsquo;s most popular attractions. Step outside and you&rsquo;ll find yourself pulled instantly into the unique energy of the city, surrounded by all the shopping, dining, nightlife and entertainment you could hope for. It is also just minutes from the Javits Center, the busiest convention center in the U.S., making the Cassa Studios the perfect home base whether you&rsquo;re in New York for business or pleasure, or if you plan to stay awhile.</p>\r\n<p>These studios feature sleek, modern design and all the amenities you&rsquo;ll need during your time here, whether you&rsquo;re staying for 2 weeks or a year. Relax on our rooftop garden terrace overlooking Midtown and Hudson Yards, take advantage of the 1,000-square-foot gym or enjoy a drink at our cozy, wood-paneled bar before you head out on the town.</p>\r\n<p>Inside and out, the Cassa Studios is built to fit a modern lifestyle. With a house manager on-site and regular housekeeping, you&rsquo;ll never have to wait in the city that never sleeps. Each room features updated decor and amenities, and large windows to let in plenty of natural light.</p>\r\n</div>', 5, '', 'cassa-rooms-8.jpg', 'cassa-rooms-8.jpg', '', 153, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'The Cassa Studios and Residences', 0, 0, 'a:5:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"title\";s:8:\"Location\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:992:\"<p>The Cassa Studios are in a prime location to easily get around all of New York City, whether you&rsquo;re staying in Manhattan or exploring the many exciting offerings of the outer boroughs. You can walk a few minutes to the Times Square/42nd Street subway station, which offers access to the most lines of any station in New York. From Times Square, you can catch the 1, 2, 3, 7, A, C, E, N, Q, R and W trains, as well as the shuttle train to Grand Central &mdash; meaning that for $2.75, you&rsquo;re just steps away from getting anywhere in Manhattan, Brooklyn, Queens or the Bronx.</p>\r\n<p><strong>All-inclusive travel distance to popular destinations:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Empire State Building: 15 min. walking or via the N/Q/R</li>\r\n<li>Central Park: 17 min. via the N/R</li>\r\n<li>Lincoln Center: 15 min. via the 1</li>\r\n<li>Met Museum: 30 min. via the 7 and 4/5/6</li>\r\n<li>Washington Square Park: 16 min. via the A/C/E</li>\r\n<li>Brooklyn Bridge: 25 min. via the A/C</li>\r\n</ul>\";}i:1;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:10:\"The Space \";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:4:\"body\";s:381:\"<p>We tasked interior designers with making every room feel welcoming and comfortable for all of our guests, without sacrificing style or modernity. These&nbsp;spaces are modern on the inside and out, with sleek surfaces, plush textiles and hardwood floors accented with cozy area rugs.</p>\r\n<p><strong>This space is ready for your stay; all you have to do is show up.</strong></p>\";s:6:\"images\";a:4:{i:0;s:25:\"cassa-common-spaces-5.jpg\";i:1;s:25:\"cassa-common-spaces-6.jpg\";i:2;s:17:\"cassa-space-2.jpg\";i:3;s:17:\"cassa-space-3.jpg\";}}i:2;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:20:\"The Rooms and Suites\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:4:\"body\";s:1944:\"<p>The interiors of rooms and suites at the Cassa Studios are designed to invoke the feel of an elegant Manhattan apartment, rather than a standard hotel room. Each room features contemporary artwork and lighting, with plenty of space to store your belongings and an in-room safe for added peace of mind. Our large windows are perfect for letting in natural light while taking in views of the city.</p>\r\n<p>When you want to relax, you can stream something new with the hotel&rsquo;s free high-speed WiFi. When it&rsquo;s time for work, you&rsquo;ll find a workspace in your room, or can take advantage of one of our many common areas.</p>\r\n<p>The spacious full bathroom includes plenty of counter space for getting ready for a night out, along with premium bath amenities from The White Company.</p>\r\n<p>Bedrooms are available with full, queen, and king-sized beds, depending on if you&rsquo;re looking for a single, double, or suite. A kitchenette is available in your room for your convenience.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Also included: hairdryer, microwave, fridge, iron and ironing board, and other little touches that will make you feel right at home.</strong></p>\r\n<table class=\"table v2\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<th>6+ Months</th>\r\n<th>4-6 Months</th>\r\n<th>1-3 Months</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Extra large</th>\r\n<td>$3800</td>\r\n<td>$3900</td>\r\n<td>$4200</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Standard large</th>\r\n<td>$3200</td>\r\n<td>$3350</td>\r\n<td>$3550</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Standard&nbsp;double</th>\r\n<td>$3100</td>\r\n<td>$3300</td>\r\n<td>$3550</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Standard</th>\r\n<td>$3000</td>\r\n<td>$3200</td>\r\n<td>$3450</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"5\">\r\n<p><em>For all rooms, there&nbsp;is a $100 charge if the key fob is not returned at check-out.&nbsp;</em></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div class=\"center\"><a class=\"button2 red\" href=\"cassa-application\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Check Avalability</a></div>\r\n<p><br /><br /></p>\";s:6:\"images\";a:11:{i:0;s:17:\"cassa-rooms-9.jpg\";i:1;s:18:\"cassa-rooms-11.jpg\";i:2;s:18:\"cassa-rooms-13.jpg\";i:3;s:17:\"cassa-rooms-8.jpg\";i:4;s:18:\"cassa-rooms-15.jpg\";i:5;s:18:\"cassa-rooms-10.jpg\";i:6;s:18:\"cassa-rooms-12.jpg\";i:7;s:17:\"cassa-rooms-7.jpg\";i:8;s:18:\"cassa-rooms-14.jpg\";i:9;s:21:\"cassa-bathrooms-1.jpg\";i:10;s:21:\"cassa-bathrooms-2.jpg\";}}i:3;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:18:\"The Common Spaces \";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:4:\"body\";s:1529:\"<p>The Cassa Studios offer a variety of common spaces for your use and enjoyment during your stay.</p>\r\n<p>Business travelers will find the studios well-suited to your needs. In addition to free high-speed WiFi and your individual workspace.</p>\r\n<p>Our state-of-the-art 1,000-square-foot fitness center makes it easy to stick to your fitness routine and includes a variety of new cardio and weight training equipment, including treadmills, ellipticals, stationary bikes, free weights and machines.</p>\r\n<p>Whether you want to relax with a book, socialize with friends or meet new people, the Cassa Studios&rsquo; rooftop garden terrace is the place to be. With expansive views of bustling Hell&rsquo;s Kitchen, the terrace includes plenty of open space, a children&rsquo;s play area and seating for lounging, taking outdoor meetings or just enjoying one of New Yorkers&rsquo; most cherished summer traditions: hanging out at a rooftop bar as day becomes evening and the lights of the city start to twinkle.</p>\r\n<p>The beautiful full kitchen at the Cassa Suites is now open to all guests for self-service. Please clean up after using the kitchen and any of the appliances, so other guests will be able to enjoy the kitchen, as well.</p>\r\n<p>Reminder: The Cassa Suites is not responsible for any lost or damaged items.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Services:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Self-parking available in onsite indoor garage (fee)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Stays: Stay for as long as you&rsquo;d like, or for as few as 10 days.</strong></p>\";s:6:\"images\";a:7:{i:0;s:19:\"cassa-rooftop-1.jpg\";i:1;s:19:\"cassa-rooftop-2.jpg\";i:2;s:19:\"cassa-rooftop-3.jpg\";i:3;s:25:\"cassa-common-spaces-2.jpg\";i:4;s:25:\"cassa-common-spaces-1.jpg\";i:5;s:25:\"cassa-common-spaces-3.jpg\";i:6;s:25:\"cassa-common-spaces-4.jpg\";}}i:4;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"title\";s:16:\"The Neighborhood\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:1550:\"<p>Walk out of the Cassa Studios and you&rsquo;ll immediately feel the vibrancy and energy that draws tens of millions of people to New York City every year from all around the world. Our exhilarating city is home to more than 8 million people from all different cultures and backgrounds, who all make this vibrant metropolis a place like no other.</p>\r\n<p>Whether you&rsquo;re craving Italian or Uzbeki food, bubble tea or a classic New York slice, you can find it nearby. And if you&rsquo;re looking to enjoy the great outdoors, you don&rsquo;t have to go far! Central Park is just uptown, while Bryant Park, famous for its seasonal gardens and markets, is just three blocks away. You can even walk just 15 minutes through Hell&rsquo;s Kitchen to the brand new Pier 76, overlooking the Hudson River.</p>\r\n<p>Hell&rsquo;s Kitchen is world-renowned for its vibrant LGBTQ+ scene, with plentiful bars and clubs that keep New York&rsquo;s world-class nightlife scene right at your fingertips. The neighborhood is also home to a wide variety of locally owned small businesses, which remain relatively affordable compared to many parts of Manhattan.</p>\r\n<p>If you&rsquo;re in the mood for even more shopping, you can head to the famed district on the Upper East Side, or stay nearby and check out the shops at Hudson Yards, in the shadow of a mesmerizing 150-foot-tall honeycomb-like structure called the Vessel.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Whatever your mood, there will always be something for you in New York &mdash; we look forward to welcoming you!</strong></p>\";}}', '', '', '', '', 1, '40.75635720', '-73.99455640', 0, '', NULL),
(427, 0, 0, 'philadelphia', '', 'Philadelphia', 'Furnished apartments for shared rent in Philadelphia', 'Outpost Club propose furnished rooms in apartments for shared rent in Philadelphia. Submit a free application on today\r\nand receive an exclusive offer with all inclusive pricing.', 'Philadelphia', '<h1 class=\"h1\">Check out our Houses<br /> in Philadelphia</h1>', '', '', 5, '', 'philadelphia.jpg', 'philadelphia.jpg', '', 430, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'Philadelphia', 0, 0, 'a:1:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:0:\"\";}}', '', '', '', '', 0, '0.00000000', '0.00000000', 512, '', '2022-07-11 08:50:45'),
(428, 427, 349, 'the-mason', '', 'The Mason on Chestnut House', 'Coliving Apartments Near University of Pennsylvania (PA 19104) | Outpost Club', 'Rent affordable & 100% furnished rooms in coliving apartments near the University of Pennsylvania. Submit a free application today and receive an exclusive offer with all inclusive pricing. ', 'Mason on Chestnut', '', '<h1 class=\"h1 center\">Mason on Chestnut</h1>\r\n<h4>A SPACIOUS HOME IN A LIVELY NEIGHBORHOOD</h4>', '<div>\r\n<h6 class=\"h5\">The Scoop</h6>\r\n<p>Mason on Chestnut is in the heart of University City, just a couple of blocks from the University of Pennsylvania campus and within easy reach of downtown Philadelphia. This brand new building with luxury amenities is the perfect way to ensure you experience all the positives of college living without having to stay in a cramped dorm room.</p>\r\n<p>The Mason features modern designs and all the amenities you&rsquo;ll need to make your university experience truly great, whether you&rsquo;re here for a semester or all 4 years. With multiple options to exercise, entertain or just relax, the Mason is the perfect home base when you&rsquo;re not in class or exploring the city.</p>\r\n<p>The brand-new building is built for your modern lifestyle, with 24-hour access to many amenities and top-notch security so you can relax or leave home without worry. Each apartment features updated furnishings and amenities, with semi-private balconies and massive windows to let plenty of light in.</p>\r\n</div>', 5, '', 'the-mason-on-chestnut-philadelphia-pa-study-lounge.jpg', 'the-mason-on-chestnut-philadelphia-pa-study-lounge.jpg', '', 431, 1, 1, 0, 0, 'Mason on Chestnut', 0, 0, 'a:6:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"title\";s:8:\"Location\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:704:\"<p>Located just across the Schuylkill River from Center City, University City is reminiscent of a bustling college town within Philadelphia. The Mason is in the perfect location whether you&rsquo;re attending the University of Pennsylvania or Drexel University, and is within a short walk of multiple public transportation options, so you can get around Philadelphia with ease.</p>\r\n<p>If you&rsquo;re walking, the Mason is located just 3 minutes from the Penn campus and less than 10 minutes from Drexel.</p>\r\n<p>Light rail stations on the 10 line are only one block away and can take you all over the city, while the 34th St. MFL station offers another easy option for getting around without a car.</p>\";}i:1;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:997:\"<p>{throughout_phila}</p>\r\n<table class=\"table v2\">\r\n<tbody style=\"width: 80%;\">\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<th>12+ Months</th>\r\n<th>5-11 Months</th>\r\n<th>1-4 Months</th>\r\n<th>Square Ft</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>1-Bedroom Apartment</th>\r\n<td>$2100</td>\r\n<td>Not offered</td>\r\n<td>Not offered</td>\r\n<td>530</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Studio (w/ Balcony and Kitchen)</th>\r\n<td>$1870</td>\r\n<td>Not offered</td>\r\n<td>Not offered</td>\r\n<td>360</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Executive Room&nbsp;w/ En-Suite Bathroom*</th>\r\n<td>$1350</td>\r\n<td>$1450</td>\r\n<td>$1750</td>\r\n<td>275</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Private Room w/ Shared Bathroom (1 Bath per 2 People)*</th>\r\n<td>$750</td>\r\n<td>$850</td>\r\n<td>$1050</td>\r\n<td>93</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"5\">\r\n<p><strong>*Prices above do not include $149/month/person amenities &amp; utilities allowance fee</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div class=\"center\"><a class=\"button2 red\" href=\"../philadelphia-application\" target=\"_blank\">Check Avalability</a></div>\";}i:3;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:26:\"The Studios and Apartments\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:4:\"body\";s:679:\"<p>The studios and one-bedroom apartments at the Mason are designed to provide a quality, comfortable living space where students can work, relax and get to know one another without having to worry about the lack of space and privacy typically found in college housing.</p>\r\n<p>Each fully furnished apartment features stainless steel appliances and hardwood-style floors, with plenty of space to store your belongings and electronic locks on every apartment. Our large windows are perfect for letting in natural light while taking in the view.</p>\r\n<p>Housekeeping services are offered for an additional fee, and an on-site laundry facility is available for your convenience.</p>\";s:6:\"images\";a:8:{i:0;s:24:\"GCM_4629_30_31_32_33.jpg\";i:1;s:62:\"the-mason-on-chestnut-philadelphia-pa-1br-1ba---530sf-11_1.jpg\";i:2;s:59:\"the-mason-on-chestnut-philadelphia-pa-1br-1ba---530sf-7.jpg\";i:3;s:58:\"the-mason-on-chestnut-philadelphia-pa-studio---275sf-5.jpg\";i:4;s:58:\"the-mason-on-chestnut-philadelphia-pa-studio---275sf-7.jpg\";i:5;s:59:\"the-mason-on-chestnut-philadelphia-pa-1br-1ba---530sf-2.jpg\";i:6;s:58:\"the-mason-on-chestnut-philadelphia-pa-studio---275sf-6.jpg\";i:7;s:59:\"the-mason-on-chestnut-philadelphia-pa-1br-1ba---530sf-6.jpg\";}}i:4;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:18:\"The Common Spaces \";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:4:\"body\";s:986:\"<p>The gems of the Mason are its variety of quality common spaces for your use and enjoyment during your stay.</p>\r\n<p>There&rsquo;s no need to join a gym or use campus facilities when you live at the Mason; our yoga room, hardwood indoor basketball court and 24-hour fitness areas have everything you need to stay fit.</p>\r\n<p>With multiple private study rooms, state-of-the-art conference rooms, various lounges and living areas and high-speed internet throughout the entire building, you&rsquo;ll never be without a place to study and get work done.</p>\r\n<p>When it&rsquo;s time to relax, you&rsquo;ll find a 400-seat private movie theater, an outdoor lounge and patio area, a recreational room with pool tables and ping pong, and plenty of room to just hang out and get to know your fellow students.</p>\r\n<p>For your safety, our high-security buildings are controlled by electronic access, with bike storage, storage lockers and a 24-hour electronic package room.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\";s:6:\"images\";a:14:{i:0;s:20:\"GCM_4601_2_3_4_5.jpg\";i:1;s:20:\"GCM_4521_2_3_4_5.jpg\";i:2;s:20:\"GCM_4493_4_5_6_7.jpg\";i:3;s:20:\"GCM_4433_4_5_6_7.jpg\";i:4;s:24:\"GCM_4526_27_28_29_30.jpg\";i:5;s:55:\"the-mason-on-chestnut-philadelphia-pa-primary-photo.jpg\";i:6;s:56:\"the-mason-on-chestnut-philadelphia-pa-study-lounge-2.jpg\";i:7;s:55:\"the-mason-on-chestnut-philadelphia-pa-yoga-studio_1.jpg\";i:8;s:56:\"the-mason-on-chestnut-philadelphia-pa-study-lounge-3.jpg\";i:9;s:56:\"the-mason-on-chestnut-philadelphia-pa-study-lounge_1.jpg\";i:10;s:67:\"the-mason-on-chestnut-philadelphia-pa-pod---90sf-shared-space-2.jpg\";i:11;s:24:\"GCM_4418_19_20_21_22.jpg\";i:12;s:24:\"GCM_4438_39_40_41_42.jpg\";i:13;s:24:\"GCM_4448_49_50_51_52.jpg\";}}i:5;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"title\";s:19:\"PERKS AND BENEFITS:\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:692:\"<div class=\"fx ch3 w perc_advantages\">\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Fast, reliable WiFi</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Regular professional cleaning</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Yoga room + 24-hour fitness area</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Hardwood indoor basketball court</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Keyless entry</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Rec center with ping pong and pool</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Community events</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Dedicated community manager</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Updated appliances</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Dedicated maintenance team</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\";}i:6;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:41:\"Welcome to University City, Philadelphia.\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:4:\"body\";s:159:\"<div>\r\n<p>Located just across the Schuylkill River from Center City, University City is reminiscent of a bustling college town within Philadelphia.</p>\r\n</div>\";s:6:\"images\";a:3:{i:0;s:40:\"actionvance-guy5aS3GvgA-unsplash (1).jpg\";i:1;s:41:\"gibson-hurst-fCk9KS__uGw-unsplash (1).jpg\";i:2;s:40:\"heidi-kaden-6LCen1qDcOw-unsplash (1).jpg\";}}}', '', '', '', '', 0, '39.95554425', '-75.19668008', 510, '', '2022-10-17 09:47:20'),
