(431, 253, 346, 'the-cornelia-house', '', 'The Cornelia House', 'The Cornelia House (NY 11385) | The Outpost Club', 'We worked with interior designers to make The Cornelia House comfortable in every room. ✓ Fully furnished ✓ Security ✓ Gas ✓ Electricity ✓ Water ✓ Wi-Fi ✓ Cleaning and maintenance', 'The Cornelia House | The Outpost Club', '<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Flushing</span>, Queens</p>\r\n<p>Private rooms from $1390</p>', '<h1 class=\"h1 center\">The Cornelia House</h1>\r\n<h4>A SPACIOUS HOME IN A LIVELY NEIGHBORHOOD</h4>', '<div>\r\n<h6 class=\"h5\">The Scoop</h6>\r\n<p>The Cornelia House is located in the heart of Ridgewood, Queens, just a few blocks from the Brooklyn neighborhood of Bushwick. The house is in a bustling part of the neighborhood, surrounded by restaurants and bars and only a few blocks from Myrtle Avenue, a major shop-lined thoroughfare through Brooklyn and Queens.</p>\r\n<p>The house is true to Ridgewood&rsquo;s historic style, built in the Romanesque Revival style with a brick facade and elegant brick arches over each window. The interior of this walk-up has been renovated to support modern lifestyles while maintaining gorgeous elements like exposed brick walls.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h6 class=\"h5\">Location</h6>\r\n<p>The Cornelia House is in the homey neighborhood of Ridgewood, bordering Bushwick, Brooklyn. Ridgewood is known for its relaxed pace, historic streets and as a center of Polish food and culture in New York.</p>\r\n<p>The nearest subway station is the Forest Av stop on the M line, just a 5-minute walk away. You can also walk 10 minutes to the Myrtle-Wyckoff stop, which serves the M and L lines. You can reach the Lower East Side and the East Village of Manhattan in 20 minutes. If you&rsquo;re working in Midtown, Bryant Park is only 35 minutes away, and you can reach the Financial District in 40 minutes. Additionally, the nearest Citi Bike dock is just a 5-minute walk away and the neighborhood has excellent bus access.</p>\r\n</div>', 5, '', 'SDC_CommonFairview_Staged__027.jpg', 'SDC_CommonFairview_Staged__027.jpg', '', 253, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'The Cornelia House', 0, 0, 'a:9:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"title\";s:20:\"Throughout the house\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:585:\"<p>{throughout}</p>\r\n<table class=\"table v2\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<th>12+ Months</th>\r\n<th>5-11 Months</th>\r\n<th>1-4 Months</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Standard&nbsp;</th>\r\n<td>$1390</td>\r\n<td>$1470</td>\r\n<td>$2070</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Standard Large</th>\r\n<td>$1490</td>\r\n<td>$1570</td>\r\n<td>$2170</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"5\">\r\n<p>*Prices above do not include $149/month/person utilities allowance fee</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div class=\"center\"><a class=\"button2 red\" href=\"online-questionnaire\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Apply for free</a></div>\";}i:1;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:12:\"The Bedrooms\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:4:\"body\";s:227:\"<p>All of the bedrooms in the Cornelia House are private and feature full-sized beds. Bedding is available for an additional fee.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Services:</strong> Bedding is available for an additional fee.</li>\r\n</ul>\";s:6:\"images\";a:4:{i:0;s:34:\"SDC_CommonFairview_Staged__027.jpg\";i:1;s:47:\"SDC_CommonFairview_Sales_Ste3L_BackRoom_153.jpg\";i:2;s:53:\"SDC_CommonFairview_Sales_Ste3L_FrontRRoom_133_139.jpg\";i:3;s:45:\"SDC_CommonFairview_Sales_Ste3L_Norman_138.jpg\";}}i:2;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:19:\"The (Co)Living Room\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:4:\"body\";s:344:\"<p>Within each unit, the living room includes a flat-screen TV and comfortable seating. The lower floor has been turned into a spacious, tastefully designed common lounge accessible to the entire house, with a separate restroom and laundry room. The lounge has plenty of seating and a large table for co-working, along with a flatscreen TV.</p>\";s:6:\"images\";a:2:{i:0;s:42:\"SDC_CommonFairview_Staged_Basement_196.jpg\";i:1;s:42:\"SDC_CommonFairview_Staged_Basement_187.jpg\";}}i:3;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:24:\"The kitchens/dining room\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:4:\"body\";s:182:\"<p>The kitchens in these units have been entirely updated, with stainless steel appliances and a breakfast bar, and are fully stocked with dishware, cooking tools and appliances.</p>\";s:6:\"images\";a:5:{i:0;s:34:\"SDC_CommonFairview_Staged__066.jpg\";i:1;s:34:\"SDC_CommonFairview_Staged__076.jpg\";i:2;s:34:\"SDC_CommonFairview_Staged__084.jpg\";i:3;s:34:\"SDC_CommonFairview_Staged__049.jpg\";i:4;s:34:\"SDC_CommonFairview_Staged__092.jpg\";}}i:4;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:13:\"The bathrooms\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:339:\"<p>Every apartment has one to two bathrooms for three to four bedrooms, so you&rsquo;ll never have to wait.</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><strong>The Laundry Room </strong></p>\r\n<p>This building includes a common laundry room &mdash; a luxury in New York City &mdash; so you won&rsquo;t have to haul your laundry to a laundromat or have it sent out.</p>\";s:6:\"images\";a:2:{i:0;s:42:\"SDC_CommonFairview_Staged_Bathroom_178.jpg\";i:1;s:42:\"SDC_CommonFairview_Staged_Bathroom_174.jpg\";}}i:5;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:13:\"The Backyard \";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:304:\"<p>The house&rsquo;s private backyard is accessible through the downstairs common lounge, and has been completely renovated to offer the perfect place to relax or hang out with friends and roommates when the weather is nice. The backyard has a large, open hardwood patio lined with plenty of seating.</p>\";s:6:\"images\";a:1:{i:0;s:32:\"SDC_CommonFairview_Sales_223.jpg\";}}i:6;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"title\";s:20:\"PERKS AND BENEFITS: \";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:647:\"<div class=\"fx ch3 w perc_advantages\">\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Fast, reliable WiFi</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Regular professional cleaning</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Furnished interiors</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Furnished backyard</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Keyless entry</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">In-house laundry</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Community events</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Dedicated community manager</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Updated appliances</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Dedicated maintenance team</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\";}i:7;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"title\";s:6:\"Prices\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:743:\"<table class=\"table v2\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<th>12+ Months</th>\r\n<th>5-11 Months</th>\r\n<th>1-4 Months</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Standard&nbsp;</th>\r\n<td>$1390</td>\r\n<td>$1470</td>\r\n<td>$2070</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Standard Large</th>\r\n<td>$1490</td>\r\n<td>$1570</td>\r\n<td>$2170</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"5\">\r\n<p>*Prices above do not include $149/month/person utilities allowance fee</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div class=\"center\"><a class=\"button2 red\" href=\"online-questionnaire\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Apply for free</a></div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Availability: Year-round / Minimum stay of 1 month / Month-to-month payment options available / Minimum age 18</strong></p>\";}i:8;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:29:\"Welcome to Ridgewood, Queens.\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:4:\"body\";s:1083:\"<div>\r\n<p>Ridgewood, Queens, may share a border with Bushwick, Brooklyn, but has its own unique history and culture. Step outside, pick a direction and walk; in no time at all, you&rsquo;ll find yourself admiring Ridgewood&rsquo;s historic architecture and many historic sites. Ridgewood isn&rsquo;t all history, of course &mdash; you&rsquo;ll find avenues lined with shops, restaurants, bars and anything else you could need, while walking or taking the subway just a stop or two into Bushwick will take you to that neighborhood&rsquo;s famed nightlife.</p>\r\n<p>The nearest subway station is the Forest Av stop on the M line, just a 5-minute walk away. You can also walk 10 minutes to the Myrtle-Wyckoff stop, which serves the M and L lines. You can reach the Lower East Side and the East Village of Manhattan in 20 minutes. If you&rsquo;re working in Midtown, Bryant Park is only 35 minutes away, and you can reach the Financial District in 40 minutes. Additionally, the nearest Citi Bike dock is just a 5-minute walk away and the neighborhood has excellent bus access.</p>\r\n</div>\";s:6:\"images\";a:7:{i:0;s:44:\"2048px-RIDGEWOOD-GLENDALE-FRESH_POND_100.JPG\";i:1;s:35:\"Common-Cornelia-Neighborhood117.jpg\";i:2;s:9:\"image.jpg\";i:3;s:37:\"RIDGEWOOD-GLENDALE-FRESH_POND_021.JPG\";i:4;s:37:\"RIDGEWOOD-GLENDALE-FRESH_POND_116.JPG\";i:5;s:37:\"RIDGEWOOD-GLENDALE-FRESH_POND_170.JPG\";i:6;s:30:\"Ridgewood-what-to-expect-1.jpg\";}}}', '', '', 'a:3:{i:0;s:3:\"383\";i:1;s:3:\"432\";i:2;s:3:\"329\";}', '', 2, '40.70345950', '-73.90196740', 489, '', '2022-08-26 10:57:43'),
(432, 253, 347, 'the-hancock-house', '', 'The Hancock House', 'The Hancock House (NY 11221) | Outpost Club', 'We worked with interior designers to make The Hancock House comfortable in every room. ✓ Fully furnished ✓ Security ✓ Gas ✓ Electricity ✓ Water ✓ Wi-Fi ✓ Cleaning and maintenance', 'The Hancock House | Outpost Club', '<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Bushwick, Brooklyn</span></p>\r\n<p>Private rooms from $1350</p>', '<h1 class=\"h1 center\">The Hancock House</h1>\r\n<h4>The house is in a creative bastion of Brooklyn</h4>', '<div>\r\n<h6 class=\"h5\">The Scoop</h6>\r\n<p>The Hancock House is located in Bushwick, Brooklyn, just a block from Irving Square Park and walking distance to an endless array of shops, dining and entertainment. The neighborhood is known as a creative bastion of Brooklyn, and residents of the Hancock House will find vibrant street art throughout the neighborhood.</p>\r\n<p>The house itself is a classic Brooklyn row house, with a stone facade and large bay windows for natural light. The interior of the Hancock House has been renovated for a new generation of residents, while maintaining the exposed-brick walls and hardwood floors so common to classic Brooklyn homes.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h6 class=\"h5\">Location</h6>\r\n<p>As in much of Brooklyn, Bushwick&rsquo;s coffee shops, bars, art galleries and performance dot the neighborhood&rsquo;s avenues, while the streets maintain a residential feel thanks to the strong community residents have built over the years. Bushwick is the perfect neighborhood to experience a unique part of Brooklyn that is often overlooked. Our favorite eateries include the perfect pizza at Roberta&rsquo;s, Ethiopian cuisine at Bunna Cafe and the popular Taiwanese food at Win Son. If you&rsquo;re looking for a green space to retreat to, just head on over to Irving Square Park, only a block away, or Maria Hernandez Park, a center for community activities in the neighborhood.</p>\r\n<p>The nearest subway station is the Halsey St stop on the L line, less than 10 minutes&rsquo; walking from the house. You can also walk to the Halsey St stop on the J/Z lines in less than 15 minutes and the Knickerbocker stop on the M line in 15 minutes flat. The B20 and B26 bus routes stop around the corner from the house, and the nearest Citibike docking station is less than a block away.</p>\r\n</div>', 5, '', 'hancock-house-bedroom-15.jpg', 'hancock-house-bedroom-15.jpg', '', 255, 1, 1, 0, 0, 'The Hancock House', 0, 0, 'a:9:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"title\";s:20:\"Throughout the house\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:834:\"<table class=\"table v2\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<th>12+ Months</th>\r\n<th>5-11 Months</th>\r\n<th>1-4 Months</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Standard Large</th>\r\n<td>$1450</td>\r\n<td>$1530</td>\r\n<td>$2130</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Standard</th>\r\n<td>$1350</td>\r\n<td>$1430</td>\r\n<td>$2030</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Executive</th>\r\n<td>$1690</td>\r\n<td>$1770</td>\r\n<td>$2370</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Executive Large</th>\r\n<td>$1790</td>\r\n<td>$1870</td>\r\n<td>$2470</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Executive Extra Large</th>\r\n<td>$1850</td>\r\n<td>$1930</td>\r\n<td>$2530</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"5\">\r\n<p>*Prices above do not include $149/month/person utilities allowance fee</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div class=\"center\"><a class=\"button2 red\" href=\"online-questionnaire\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Apply for free</a></div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\";}i:1;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:12:\"The Bedrooms\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:4:\"body\";s:293:\"<p>All of the bedrooms in the Hancock House are private and feature full-sized beds. Bedding is available for an additional fee. Three of the bedrooms have large bay windows at the front of the house, and many of the house&rsquo;s rooms are much larger than your standard New York bedroom.</p>\";s:6:\"images\";a:9:{i:0;s:28:\"hancock-house-bedroom-11.jpg\";i:1;s:28:\"hancock-house-bedroom-12.jpg\";i:2;s:28:\"hancock-house-bedroom-13.jpg\";i:3;s:28:\"hancock-house-bedroom-14.jpg\";i:4;s:28:\"hancock-house-bedroom-15.jpg\";i:5;s:28:\"hancock-house-bedroom-16.jpg\";i:6;s:28:\"hancock-house-bedroom-17.jpg\";i:7;s:28:\"hancock-house-bedroom-18.jpg\";i:8;s:28:\"hancock-house-bedroom-19.jpg\";}}i:2;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:19:\"The (Co)Living Room\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:4:\"body\";s:381:\"<p>Each unit features a spacious open common area, with a flat-screen TV and plenty of comfortable seating in the living room. The dining room table can also be used as a co-working space.</p>\r\n<p>Downstairs, a large, open lounge has been created with ample seating, co-working space and an additional flat-screen TV, so you&rsquo;ll always have room to relax or get work done.</p>\";s:6:\"images\";a:3:{i:0;s:28:\"hancock-house-coliving-2.jpg\";i:1;s:30:\"hancock-house-coliving-3:1.jpg\";i:2;s:28:\"hancock-house-coliving-1.jpg\";}}i:3;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:24:\"The kitchens/dining room\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:4:\"body\";s:188:\"<p>The kitchens in these units have been entirely updated, with stainless steel appliances (including a dishwasher!), and are fully stocked with dishware, cooking tools and appliances.</p>\";s:6:\"images\";a:4:{i:0;s:27:\"hancock-house-kitchen-1.jpg\";i:1;s:27:\"hancock-house-kitchen-2.jpg\";i:2;s:27:\"hancock-house-kitchen-3.jpg\";i:3;s:27:\"hancock-house-kitchen-4.jpg\";}}i:4;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:13:\"The bathrooms\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:477:\"<p>Many bedrooms in the Hancock House have private bathrooms, so you&rsquo;ll never have to wait or try to juggle your post-workout shower with your roommate&rsquo;s social calendar.</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><strong>The Laundry Room </strong></p>\r\n<p>This building includes a common laundry room &mdash; a luxury in New York City &mdash; so you won&rsquo;t have to haul your laundry to a laundromat or have it sent out. Just download the PayRange app and you&rsquo;ll be good to go.</p>\";s:6:\"images\";a:2:{i:0;s:29:\"hancock-house-bathroom-11.jpg\";i:1;s:29:\"hancock-house-bathroom-12.jpg\";}}i:5;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:13:\"The Backyard \";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:231:\"<p>The house&rsquo;s private backyard has been completely renovated to offer the perfect place to relax or hang out with friends and roommates when the weather is nice. The backyard has been redone to include plenty of seating.</p>\";s:6:\"images\";a:1:{i:0;s:26:\"hancock-house-backyard.jpg\";}}i:6;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"title\";s:20:\"PERKS AND BENEFITS: \";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:638:\"<div class=\"fx ch3 w perc_advantages\">\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Fast, reliable WiFi</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Regular professional cleaning</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Furnished interiors</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">In-unit laundry</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Keyless entry</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Dishwasher</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Community events</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Dedicated community manager</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Updated appliances</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Dedicated maintenance team</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\";}i:7;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"title\";s:6:\"Prices\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:998:\"<table class=\"table v2\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<th>12+ Months</th>\r\n<th>5-11 Months</th>\r\n<th>1-4 Months</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Standard Large</th>\r\n<td>$1450</td>\r\n<td>$1530</td>\r\n<td>$2130</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Standard</th>\r\n<td>$1350</td>\r\n<td>$1430</td>\r\n<td>$2030</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Executive</th>\r\n<td>$1690</td>\r\n<td>$1770</td>\r\n<td>$2370</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Executive Large</th>\r\n<td>$1790</td>\r\n<td>$1870</td>\r\n<td>$2470</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Executive Extra Large</th>\r\n<td>$1850</td>\r\n<td>$1930</td>\r\n<td>$2530</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"5\">\r\n<p>*Prices above do not include $149/month/person utilities allowance fee</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div class=\"center\"><a class=\"button2 red\" href=\"online-questionnaire\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Apply for free</a></div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Availability: Year-round / Minimum stay of 1 month / Month-to-month payment options available / Minimum age 18</strong></p>\";}i:8;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:30:\"Welcome to Bushwick, Brooklyn.\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:4:\"body\";s:903:\"<div>\r\n<p>Bushwick is deservedly known for its public art &mdash; the famous street murals &mdash; and its legendary nightlife scene. It&rsquo;s also home to people from all different walks of life, and you won&rsquo;t be surprised to experience what feels like a beautiful celebration of culture just walking down a street like Knickerbocker Avenue, listening to the languages being spoken while deciding which food cart to stop at. The neighborhood features the cherished Maria Hernandez Park, trendy cafes like Variety, a plethora of nightlife options, and an active community that encourages you to get to know your neighbors.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><iframe style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" title=\"YouTube video player\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/UGFty33wPMs\" width=\"100%\" height=\"600\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\";s:6:\"images\";a:7:{i:0;s:79:\"45f35bd23f049a76a8ec91d6dda27135--bushwick-brooklyn-williamsburg-brooklyn_1.jpg\";i:1;s:9:\"90_1.jpeg\";i:2;s:19:\"bikes-771x466_1.png\";i:3;s:51:\"Bushwick-Collective-Mural-Brooklyn-New-York-8_1.jpg\";i:4;s:29:\"GettyImages_817252928.0_1.jpg\";i:5;s:38:\"shutterstoc