(481, 253, 367, 'the-clark-house', '', 'The Clark House ', 'The Clark House (NY 10026) | Outpost Club', 'We worked with interior designers to make The Clark House comfortable in every room. ✓ Fully furnished ✓ Security ✓ Gas ✓ Electricity ✓ Water ✓ Wi-Fi ✓ Cleaning and maintenance', 'The Clark House | Outpost Club', '<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Harlem</span>, Manhattan</p>\r\n<p>Private rooms from $1500</p>', '<h1 class=\"h1 center\">The Clark House</h1>\r\n<h4>A MODERN HOME IN A VIBRANT NEIGHBORHOOD</h4>', '<div>\r\n<h6 class=\"h5\">The scoop&nbsp;</h6>\r\n<p>The Clark House is located in the epicenter of one of the most vibrant neighborhoods in Manhattan. From the food you\'ll find there to the music you\'ll hear floating from open windows in the street, you will be transported. It is a living, breathing representation of its rich history and the rich culture that fills it today.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h6 class=\"h5\">Location</h6>\r\n<p>This space is located in a quaint neighborhood with the beautiful St Nicholas Park nearby and quick access to some of the best parts of manhattan. With the subway at 135th St only 10 mins from Central Park and the 2, 3, and C lines offering express routes into downtown Manhattan you will never want for things to do.</p>\r\n<p>If you would rather stay in the neighborhood for the night, you will have your pick of activities. With the numerous landmarks to visit and a plethora of cuisines to sample, you will feel there is never enough time to do it all.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h6 class=\"h5\">The space</h6>\r\n<p>The Clark House is a newly renovated building with hardwood flooring, exposed brick, stainless kitchens, marble baths, and inviting layouts. The house features a large common space on the lower level to bring the community outside in!</p>\r\n</div>', 5, '', 'clark-house-coliving-7.jpg', 'clark-house-coliving-7.jpg', '', 281, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'The Clark House ', 0, 0, 'a:10:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"title\";s:20:\"Throughout the House\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:593:\"<p>{throughout}</p>\r\n<table class=\"table v2\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<th>12+ Months</th>\r\n<th>5-11 Months</th>\r\n<th>1-4 Months</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Standard</th>\r\n<td>$1500</td>\r\n<td>$1590</td>\r\n<td>$2190</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Standard large with desk</th>\r\n<td>$1620</td>\r\n<td>$1710</td>\r\n<td>$2310</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"5\">\r\n<p>*Prices above do not include $149/month/person utilities allowance fee</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div class=\"center\"><a class=\"button2 red\" href=\"online-questionnaire\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Check Availability</a></div>\";}i:1;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:8:\"Bedrooms\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:4:\"body\";s:304:\"<p>All of The Clark House bedrooms are private and feature full-sized beds.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Amenities</strong>: full-size memory-foam mattresses, pillows, shelving, hooks and closets/organizational tools.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Services</strong>: Bedding is available for an additional fee.</li>\r\n</ul>\";s:6:\"images\";a:4:{i:0;s:25:\"clark-house-bedroom-1.jpg\";i:1;s:25:\"clark-house-bedroom-2.jpg\";i:2;s:25:\"clark-house-bedroom-3.jpg\";i:3;s:25:\"clark-house-bedroom-4.jpg\";}}i:2;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:19:\"The (Co)Living Room\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:4:\"body\";s:434:\"<p>The living room in each apartment in The Clark House is complete with couches, flatscreen TVs, and a table for working or eating. Whether you&rsquo;re cooking with your roommates or watching the latest Netflix series, the shared spaces will always be the perfect spot to relax after a busy day.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Security:</strong> 24/7 security in common areas.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Tech:</strong> Google Chromecast.</li>\r\n</ul>\";s:6:\"images\";a:6:{i:0;s:26:\"clark-house-coliving-7.jpg\";i:1;s:26:\"clark-house-coliving-1.jpg\";i:2;s:26:\"clark-house-coliving-3.jpg\";i:3;s:26:\"clark-house-coliving-6.jpg\";i:4;s:26:\"clark-house-coliving-4.jpg\";i:5;s:26:\"clark-house-coliving-2.jpg\";}}i:3;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:19:\"The community space\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:4:\"body\";s:269:\"<p>The basement is a fully furnished shared common space and work area where you can co-work with your housemates or relax after a long day. A laundry room is also located on this floor, so you\'ll never have to worry about finding an open machine at the laundromat.</p>\";s:6:\"images\";a:5:{i:0;s:26:\"clark-house-basement-3.jpg\";i:1;s:26:\"clark-house-basement-4.jpg\";i:2;s:26:\"clark-house-basement-1.jpg\";i:3;s:26:\"clark-house-basement-7.jpg\";i:4;s:26:\"clark-house-basement-5.jpg\";}}i:4;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:12:\"The kitchens\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:690:\"<p>In these apartments, the kitchen is newly renovated and ready to be put to work. So whether you are making a home-cooked meal or opening the take-out from your favorite spot, you will have everything you need.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Amenities</strong>Amenities include electric stoves, stainless-steel fridges, microwaves, large sinks, coffee makers, blenders, plenty of cabinets, cookware, tableware, cutting boards, and anything else you would need in a kitchen.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Also included:</strong>paper towels, dish soap, hand soap, and garbage/recycling bags, all of which are routinely restocked.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Security:</strong> 24/7 security in common areas.</li>\r\n</ul>\";s:6:\"images\";a:3:{i:0;s:25:\"clark-house-kitchen-3.jpg\";i:1;s:25:\"clark-house-kitchen-2.jpg\";i:2;s:25:\"clark-house-kitchen-1.jpg\";}}i:5;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"title\";s:16:\"The laundry room\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:177:\"<p>The Clark House includes a common laundry room &mdash; a luxury in New York City &mdash; so you won&rsquo;t have to haul your laundry to a laundromat or have it sent out.</p>\";}i:6;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:13:\"The bathrooms\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:326:\"<p>The Clark House features sleek and renovated bathrooms with modern appliances to suit all your needs. With a minimum of 2 bathrooms per unit, you won\'t have to worry about waiting too long.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Also included</strong>: toilet paper, hand soap and small garbage bags, which will never be empty!</li>\r\n</ul>\";s:6:\"images\";a:4:{i:0;s:26:\"clark-house-bathroom-4.jpg\";i:1;s:26:\"clark-house-bathroom-1.jpg\";i:2;s:26:\"clark-house-bathroom-2.jpg\";i:3;s:26:\"clark-house-bathroom-3.jpg\";}}i:7;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"title\";s:19:\"PERKS AND BENEFITS:\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:589:\"<div class=\"fx ch3 w perc_advantages\">\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Fast, reliable WiFi</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Regular professional cleaning</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Furnished interiors</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Updated appliances</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Keyless entry</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Community events</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Dedicated maintenance team</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Dedicated community manager</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">In-house loundry</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\";}i:8;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"title\";s:6:\"Prices\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:757:\"<table class=\"table v2\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<th>12+ Months</th>\r\n<th>5-11 Months</th>\r\n<th>1-4 Months</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Standard&nbsp;</th>\r\n<td>$1500</td>\r\n<td>$1590</td>\r\n<td>$2190</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Standard large with desk</th>\r\n<td>$1620</td>\r\n<td>$1710</td>\r\n<td>$2310</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"5\">\r\n<p>*Prices above do not include $149/month/person utilities allowance fee</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div class=\"center\"><a class=\"button2 red\" href=\"online-questionnaire\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Check Availability</a></div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Availability: Year-round / Minimum stay of 1 month / Month-to-month payment options available / Minimum age 18</strong></p>\";}i:9;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:40:\"WELCOME TO CENTRAL HARLEM / EAST HARLEM \";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:4:\"body\";s:482:\"<p>Central Harlem and East Harlem are two of the most community-driven neighborhoods in New York. A testament to the history and culture that surrounds them today. There is so much to discover, experience, and learn in these communities. It is home to several art festivals and is beaming with numerous restaurants, shops, and historical landmarks. So whether you are interested in music, literature, fashion, or something else, you will always have something new to experience.</p>\";s:6:\"images\";a:4:{i:0;s:48:\"jean-philippe-delberghe-lqdec_txosE-unsplash.jpg\";i:1;s:34:\"jimmy-woo-nb9atvt9URA-unsplash.jpg\";i:2;s:29:\"domo-K9CWHkFlQxo-unsplash.jpg\";i:3;s:36:\"eyeswashere-l_3-UT7oAPk-unsplash.jpg\";}}}', '', '', '', '', 1, '40.81683720', '-73.94084750', 486, '', '2022-10-07 10:28:18'),
