(482, 427, 368, 'the-temple-1-house', '', 'The Temple 1 House', 'The Temple 1 House (PA 19133) | Outpost Club', 'We worked with interior designers to make The Temple 1 House comfortable in every room. ✓ Fully furnished ✓ Security ✓ Gas ✓ Electricity ✓ Water ✓ Wi-Fi ✓ Cleaning and maintenance', 'The Temple 1 House | Outpost Club', '', '<h1 class=\"h1 center\">The Temple 1 House</h1>\r\n<h4>A SPACIOUS HOME IN A LIVELY NEIGHBORHOOD</h4>', '<div>\r\n<h6 class=\"h5\">The scoop&nbsp;</h6>\r\n<p>Temple 1, also known as the Tech Mansion, is a live-in accelerator perfect for entrepreneurs, content creators, and innovators to come together and create something unforgettable. Located in the heart of North Philadelphia East, right next to Temple University and within easy reach of downtown Philadelphia. This brand-new building with luxury amenities is the perfect way to ensure you experience all the best parts of college life and off-campus life.</p>\r\n<p>Temple 1 features modern designs and all the amenities you&rsquo;ll need to make your university experience genuinely great, whether you&rsquo;re here for a semester or all four years. With multiple options to create, entertain or just relax, Temple 1 is the perfect home base for the ​next generation of executives, entrepreneurs, creators, and influencers.</p>\r\n<p>This brand-new building is built for your modern lifestyle, with 24-hour access to many amenities. Each apartment features updated furnishings and amenities, a rooftop terrace to meet other tenants, and common spaces to keep the creativity flowing!</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h6 class=\"h5\">Location</h6>\r\n<p>Located in the North Philadelphia East neighborhood and surrounded by Ludlow, Yorktown, West Kensington, and Glenwood, you will never be looking for something to do. From city landmarks, renowned musical venues, and a plethora of food options, you couldn\'t ask for more.</p>\r\n<p>With the bustling Temple University a 4 min walk away, it is the perfect location to ensure you make it to class on time. Not to mention the multiple public transportation options at your fingertips to get around Philadelphia with ease.</p>\r\n<p>Whether you are trying to stick around the neighborhood or explore the rest of what Philadelphia has to offer, you will find that North Philadelphia East is the perfect place to be.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h6 class=\"h5\">The space</h6>\r\n<p>Temple 1 is a newly renovated building with hardwood flooring, updated appliances, stainless kitchens, beautiful white stone countertops, and inviting layouts. The house features common spaces to bring the community together from a conference room for ideation to a rooftop terrace to enjoy those sunny summer days!</p>\r\n</div>', 5, '', 'temple-house-3.jpg', 'temple-house-3.jpg', '', 432, 1, 1, 0, 0, 'The Temple 1 House', 0, 0, 'a:9:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"title\";s:20:\"Throughout the house\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:572:\"<p>{throughout}</p>\r\n<table class=\"table v2\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<th>12+ Months</th>\r\n<th>6-11 Months</th>\r\n<th>1-4 Months</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Standard</th>\r\n<td>$849</td>\r\n<td>$900</td>\r\n<td>$990</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Standard Large</th>\r\n<td>$899</td>\r\n<td>$950</td>\r\n<td>$1050</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"5\">\r\n<p>*Prices above do not include $149/month/person utilities allowance fee</p>\r\n.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div class=\"center\"><a class=\"button2 red\" href=\"join-us-manhattan\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Apply for free</a></div>\";}i:2;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:8:\"Bedrooms\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:4:\"body\";s:286:\"<p>All of the Temple 1 bedrooms are private and feature full-sized beds.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Amenities</strong>: full-size mattresses, pillows, shelving, hooks, closets/organizational tools.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Services</strong>: Bedding is available for an additional fee.</li>\r\n</ul>\";s:6:\"images\";a:2:{i:0;s:18:\"temple-house-9.jpg\";i:1;s:19:\"temple-house-12.jpg\";}}i:3;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:19:\"The community space\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:4:\"body\";s:403:\"<p>The common spaces are fully furnished with a shared work area where you can co-work with your housemates and innovate on your next big idea! This house features a podcast studio for the content creators out there to facilitate your recording needs. &amp; To top it all off Washers and dryers are also available, so you\'ll never have to worry about finding an open machine at the laundromat again.</p>\";s:6:\"images\";a:5:{i:0;s:18:\"temple-house-3.jpg\";i:1;s:18:\"temple-house-7.jpg\";i:2;s:18:\"temple-house-8.jpg\";i:3;s:19:\"temple-house-11.jpg\";i:4;s:19:\"temple-house-13.jpg\";}}i:4;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:20:\"The (Co)Living Rooms\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:4:\"body\";s:362:\"<p>The living room in each apartment in Temple 1 is complete with couches, flatscreen TVs, and a table for working or eating. Whether cooking with your roommates or watching the latest Netflix series, the shared spaces will always be the perfect spot to relax after a busy day.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Security:</strong> 24/7 security in common areas.</li>\r\n</ul>\";s:6:\"images\";a:1:{i:0;s:18:\"temple-house-2.jpg\";}}i:5;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:12:\"The kitchens\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:4:\"body\";s:686:\"<p>In these apartments, the kitchen is newly renovated and ready to be put to work. So whether you are making a home-cooked meal or opening the take-out from your favorite spot, you will have everything you need.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Amenities</strong> include electric stoves, stainless-steel fridges, microwaves, large sinks, coffee makers, blenders, plenty of cabinets, cookware, tableware, cutting boards, and anything else you would need in a kitchen.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Also included:</strong> are paper towels, dish soap, hand soap, and garbage/recycling bags, all of which are routinely restocked.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Security:</strong> 24/7 security in common areas.</li>\r\n</ul>\";s:6:\"images\";a:3:{i:0;s:18:\"temple-house-4.jpg\";i:1;s:18:\"temple-house-5.jpg\";i:2;s:19:\"temple-house-14.jpg\";}}i:6;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"title\";s:16:\"The laundry room\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:175:\"<p>Temple 1 includes a washer/dryer set in each unit &mdash; a luxury in any city &mdash; so you won&rsquo;t have to haul your laundry to a laundromat or have it sent out.</p>\";}i:7;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:13:\"The bathrooms\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:4:\"body\";s:323:\"<p>The Temple 1 House features sleek and renovated bathrooms with modern appliances to suit all your needs. With two full bathrooms per unit, you won\'t have to worry about waiting too long.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Also included</strong>: toilet paper, hand soap and small garbage bags, which will never be empty!</li>\r\n</ul>\";s:6:\"images\";a:3:{i:0;s:18:\"temple-house-1.jpg\";i:1;s:18:\"temple-house-6.jpg\";i:2;s:19:\"temple-house-10.jpg\";}}i:8;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"title\";s:19:\"PERKS AND BENEFITS:\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:697:\"<div class=\"fx ch3 w perc_advantages\">\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Fast, reliable WiFi</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Regular professional cleaning</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Furnished interiors</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Updated appliances</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Keyless entry</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Community events</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Dedicated maintenance team</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Dedicated community manager</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">In-unit laundry</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Podcast studio</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Think tank area</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\";}i:9;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"title\";s:6:\"Prices\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:551:\"<table class=\"table v2\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<th>12+ Months</th>\r\n<th>6-11 Months</th>\r\n<th>1-4 Months</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Standard</th>\r\n<td>$849</td>\r\n<td>$900</td>\r\n<td>$990</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Standard Large</th>\r\n<td>$899</td>\r\n<td>$950</td>\r\n<td>$1050</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"5\">\r\n<p>*Prices above do not include $149/month/person utilities allowance fee</p>\r\n.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div class=\"center\"><a class=\"button2 red\" href=\"join-us-manhattan\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Apply for free</a></div>\";}}', '', '', '', '', 0, '39.98568605', '-75.15073270', 483, '', '2022-11-07 12:02:33'),
