(522, 182, 0, 'how-do-i-cancel-my-sure-insurance-renters-insurance-after-i-move-out', '', 'How do I cancel my renters insurance after I move out?', 'How do I cancel my Sure Insurance (renters insurance) after I move out?', '', 'How do I cancel my Sure Insurance (renters insurance) after I move out?', '', '', '<p>The quickest way to cancel your Sure Insurance is to call their underwriter Assurant at (800)-432-8612 with your policy number, and select option 7, then 6 (to speak with a representative). A representative will be able to help you cancel. Please let us know if you need any help along the way.</p>', 6, '', '', '', '', 522, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'How do I cancel my Sure Insurance (renters insurance) after I move out?', 0, 0, 'a:0:{}', '', '', '', '', 0, '0.00000000', '0.00000000', 0, '', '2022-10-17 12:43:37'),
(525, 253, 56, 'the-maison-linden-house', '', 'The Maison on Linden', 'The Maison on Linden', 'We worked with interior designers to make The Maison Jefferson comfortable in every room. ✓ Fully furnished ✓ Security ✓ Gas ✓ Electricity ✓ Water ✓ Wi-Fi ✓ Cleaning and maintenance', 'The Maison on Linden', '<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ridgewood,</span> Queens</p>\r\n<p>Private rooms from $1500</p>', '<h1 class=\"h1 center\">The Maison on Linden</h1>\r\n<h4>A Bustling Block In A Dynamic Ridgewood Community</h4>', '<h6 class=\"h5\">Maison Means Home</h6>\r\n<p>Maison is made for everyone and anyone seeking to embrace New York City. Radical in its approach yet familiar in its design, Maison aims to provide an inclusive, welcoming home for modern city dwellers in a context where moving to a new city is not a difficult and lonely process.</p>\r\n<p>Maison means Home, whether you\'re looking for a move-in-ready private bedroom for just a month or long-term. Furnished, beautifully designed, with private bathrooms and large shared amenities: Everything is ready for you to move in, meet your community and enjoy everything the city has to offer.</p>\r\n<p>The Maison properties are always located within a short walk of public transportation. The Maison on Linden is less than a 5-minute walk from M Line and less than a 10-minute walk from the L line. With 2 CIty Bike states only 3 mins away as well. That can get you all the way to Chelsea in a short 30 min train ride!</p>', 5, '', 'MSNLNDN_Maisonette Large_02.jpg', 'MSNLNDN_Maisonette Large_02.jpg', '', 157, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'The Maison on Linden', 0, 0, 'a:9:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"title\";s:8:\"Location\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:464:\"<p>The Maison on Linden is located in the neighborhood of Ridgewood, which is ideally situated so you can easily explore both Queens and Brooklyn! This neighborhood is home to many local bars and restaurants, so you won&rsquo;t need to go far to find your next bite or favorite cocktail. This house is also a short walk away from trendy Brooklyn neighborhoods like East Williamsburg and Bushwick, so you can explore two Burroughs without hopping on the subway.</p>\";}i:1;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:20:\"Throughout the House\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:347:\"<p>We worked with interior designers to make the house comfortable for all of our members in any room of the house. For the furniture we used only the best suppliers and materials, from real wooden surfaces to sleek countertops.</p>\r\n<p><strong>We&rsquo;ve thought of all the little things you need to feel right at home upon arrival.</strong></p>\";s:6:\"images\";a:1:{i:0;s:11:\"MSNLNDN.jpg\";}}i:2;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:20:\"The rooms and suites\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:4:\"body\";s:906:\"<p><strong>The&nbsp;Maison Suite</strong></p>\r\n<p>The Maisonette Suite bedroom comes with an en-suite bathroom along with a wet-bar and its own fridge. It is fully furnished, with a wardrobe, a lounge area, and a spacious desk.</p>\r\n<table class=\"table v2\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<th>12+ Months</th>\r\n<th>5-11 Months</th>\r\n<th>1-4 Months</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Maisonette Large</th>\r\n<td>$1690</td>\r\n<td>$1770</td>\r\n<td>$2370</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Maisonette</th>\r\n<td>$1590</td>\r\n<td>$1670</td>\r\n<td>$2270</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Maisonette Small</th>\r\n<td>$1500</td>\r\n<td>$1580</td>\r\n<td>$2180</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"5\">\r\n<p>*Prices above do not include $149/month/person utilities allowance fee</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div class=\"center\"><a class=\"button2 red\" href=\"linden-application\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Check Availability</a></div>\r\n<p><br /><br /></p>\";s:6:\"images\";a:6:{i:0;s:25:\"MSNLNDN_Maisonette_02.jpg\";i:1;s:25:\"MSNLNDN_Maisonette_01.jpg\";i:2;s:31:\"MSNLNDN_Maisonette Small_01.jpg\";i:3;s:31:\"MSNLNDN_Maisonette Small_02.jpg\";i:4;s:31:\"MSNLNDN_Maisonette Large_02.jpg\";i:5;s:31:\"MSNLNDN_Maisonette Large_01.jpg\";}}i:3;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:16:\"The Open Kitchen\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:4:\"body\";s:312:\"<p>Each of the four apartments of the building is outfitted with a fully fitted kitchen, all clad in stainless steel, to reflect the beautiful Brooklyn light. The kitchens are open onto a dining lounge, a versatile space to share a meal, work from home, or have a drink with your housemates after a busy day.</p>\";s:6:\"images\";a:2:{i:0;s:31:\"MSNLNDN_Maisonette Large_07.jpg\";i:1;s:31:\"MSNLNDN_Maisonette Large_06.jpg\";}}i:4;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:10:\"The Lounge\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:4:\"body\";s:283:\"<p>Opening into the backyard is a large, fully furnished common lounge and work area where you can co-work with your housemates or relax after a long day. A laundry room is also located on this floor, so you\'ll never have to worry about finding an open machine at the laundromat.</p>\";s:6:\"images\";a:2:{i:0;s:31:\"MSNLNDN_Maisonette Small_05.jpg\";i:1;s:31:\"MSNLNDN_Maisonette Small_06.jpg\";}}i:5;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:29:\"The Backyard Community Garden\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:225:\"<p>A large backyard is surrounded by planters customizable to tenants to grow anything you\'d like. The deck is furnished with lounge chairs and dining furniture, so you can enjoy one another\'s company during nice weather.</p>\";s:6:\"images\";a:1:{i:0;s:35:\"maison-jefferson-backyard-min-2.jpg\";}}i:6;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"title\";s:18:\"Perks and Benefits\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:1248:\"<div class=\"fx ch3 w perc_advantages\">\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Community</h4>\r\n<p>Meeting new people and building connections in a new city can be challenging. At Maison, you can meet your neighbors through the shared kitchens and large amenities provided in the building.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Common Areas</h4>\r\n<p>Each Maison unit is built around the idea of coming together in community, with a spacious common kitchen and living room in-unit and an additional large lounge/work area&nbsp;that opens onto the furnished backyard. Tenants love our common areas for game nights, cooking together or relaxing with a glass of wine to catch up on the events of the day.&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Fully Furnished</h4>\r\n<p>All our properties are fully furnished with comfortable, high-quality&nbsp;and functional furniture to make you feel at home.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">On-Site Laundry</h4>\r\n<p>This&nbsp;property has a dedicated laundry room with washers and dryers accessible at any time.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Convenience</h4>\r\n<p>With a minimum lease of 1 month, full furnishings and no need to set up utilities and internet accounts, moving in is easy.&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\";}i:8;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"title\";s:3:\"FAQ\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:1542:\"<div class=\"w100 faq\">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><input id=\"faq_1\" class=\"hide\" type=\"checkbox\" /><label class=\"h6\" for=\"faq_1\">Fixed Monthly Expenses</label>\r\n<div class=\"text\">While living with us, your&nbsp;fixed rent and utilities price &mdash; including high-speed WiFi &mdash; means you won\'t have to be worried about surprise charges from a landlord you\'ve never even spoken to. Hello, New York; goodbye, rental headaches.</div>\r\n</li>\r\n<li><input id=\"faq_2\" class=\"hide\" type=\"checkbox\" /> <label class=\"h6\" for=\"faq_2\">Full-Month Security Deposit Option</label>\r\n<div class=\"text\">Before you move-in, we charge one full-month security deposit, which you will get back in full after your stay with us ends. If you would like to waive the security deposit, however, you may do so through&nbsp;our partners at Qira! They&rsquo;ll pay your security deposit for a small monthly fee ranging from $10-$20.</div>\r\n</li>\r\n<li><input id=\"faq_3\" class=\"hide\" type=\"checkbox\" /> <label class=\"h6\" for=\"faq_3\">House Leaders</label>\r\n<div class=\"text\">All of our locations have a House Leader. If you have any questions during your stay with us, they&rsquo;ll be there for you.</div>\r\n</li>\r\n<li><input id=\"faq_4\" class=\"hide\" type=\"checkbox\" /><label class=\"h6\" for=\"faq_4\">Varying Contract Lengths</label>\r\n<div class=\"text\">Our lease lengths allow you to choose what works best for your plans. You can&nbsp;reach out to us to extend your stay if your plans change, or sign a longer lease up front to take advantage of lower prices.</div>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\";}i:9;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"title\";s:17:\"THE NEIGHBOURHOOD\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:589:\"<p>Ridgewood is a homey neighborhood bordering Brooklyn, known for its relaxed pace and historic streets. It is home to many local bars and restaurants, such as While in Katmandu, so you will never need to travel far to get some sustenance. It is a 2-minute walk from the Seneca Ave. subway station, a 20-minute ride into central Williamsburg, or a 30-minute ride into the Lower East Side.</p>\r\n<p><strong>So whether you are looking for a quiet night in or a night on the town, this house will be the perfect location to do it all &mdash; and we look forward to welcoming you!</strong></p>\";}}', '', '', '', '', 2, '40.70338083', '-73.90938630', 526, '', '2022-11-09 09:07:51'),
