(529, 253, 0, 'the-maison-suydam-house', '', 'The Maison on Suydam ', 'The Maison on Suydam', 'We worked with interior designers to make The Maison Jefferson comfortable in every room. ✓ Fully furnished ✓ Security ✓ Gas ✓ Electricity ✓ Water ✓ Wi-Fi ✓ Cleaning and maintenance', 'The Maison on Suydam', '<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Bushwick,</span> Brooklyn</p>\r\n<p>Private rooms from $1600</p>', '<h1 class=\"h1 center\">The Maison on Suydam</h1>', '<h6 class=\"h5\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Maison Means Home</h6>\r\n<p>Maison is made for everyone and anyone seeking to embrace New York City. Radical in its approach yet familiar in its design, Maison aims to provide an inclusive, welcoming home for modern city dwellers in a context where moving to a new city is not a difficult and lonely process.</p>\r\n<p>Maison means Home, whether you\'re looking for a move-in-ready private bedroom for just a month or long-term. Furnished, beautifully designed, with private bathrooms and large shared amenities: Everything is ready for you to move in, meet your community and enjoy everything the city has to offer.</p>\r\n<p>The Maison properties are always located within a short walk of public transportation. The Maison on Suydam is a 3-minute walk from L Line that can take you straight to manhattan in a short 20 min train ride!</p>', 5, '', 'MSNSDM_Apt 2R_02.jpg', 'MSNSDM_Apt 2R_02.jpg', '', 159, 1, 1, 0, 0, 'The Maison on Suydam', 0, 0, 'a:8:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"title\";s:8:\"Location\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:310:\"<p>The Maison on Suydam is located at the heart of Bushwick, The house has plenty of cafes, restaurants, and bars within walking distance and is located near some of Bushwick&rsquo;s most beloved murals. Every room in this house is complete with it&rsquo;s own private bathroom and wetbar so you will never</p>\";}i:1;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:20:\"Throughout the House\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:347:\"<p>We worked with interior designers to make the house comfortable for all of our members in any room of the house. For the furniture we used only the best suppliers and materials, from real wooden surfaces to sleek countertops.</p>\r\n<p><strong>We&rsquo;ve thought of all the little things you need to feel right at home upon arrival.</strong></p>\";s:6:\"images\";a:1:{i:0;s:29:\"maison-jefferson-spaces-5.jpg\";}}i:2;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:20:\"The rooms and suites\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:4:\"body\";s:964:\"<p><strong>The&nbsp;Maison Suite</strong></p>\r\n<p>The Maisonette Suite bedroom comes with an en-suite bathroom along with a wet-bar and its own fridge. It is fully furnished, with a wardrobe, a lounge area, and a spacious desk.</p>\r\n<table class=\"table v2\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<th>12+ Months</th>\r\n<th>5-11 Months</th>\r\n<th>1-4 Months</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Maisonette Large</th>\r\n<td>$1790</td>\r\n<td>$1870</td>\r\n<td>$2470</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Maisonette</th>\r\n<td>$1690</td>\r\n<td>$1770</td>\r\n<td>$2370</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Maisonette Small</th>\r\n<td>$1600</td>\r\n<td>$1680</td>\r\n<td>$2280</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"5\">\r\n<p>*Prices above do not include $149/month/person utilities allowance fee</p>\r\n<p><strong>Available from October&nbsp;15th</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div class=\"center\"><a class=\"button2 red\" href=\"linden-application\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Check Availability</a></div>\r\n<p><br /><br /></p>\";s:6:\"images\";a:5:{i:0;s:28:\"Bedroom-MSNSDM_Apt 2R_02.jpg\";i:1;s:28:\"Bedroom-MSNSDM_Apt 2R_08.jpg\";i:2;s:28:\"Bedroom-MSNSDM_apt 2L_02.jpg\";i:3;s:28:\"Bedroom-MSNSDM_apt 2L_07.jpg\";i:4;s:28:\"Bedroom-MSNSDM_apt 2L_06.jpg\";}}i:3;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:16:\"The Open Kitchen\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:4:\"body\";s:312:\"<p>Each of the four apartments of the building is outfitted with a fully fitted kitchen, all clad in stainless steel, to reflect the beautiful Brooklyn light. The kitchens are open onto a dining lounge; a versatile space to share a meal, work from home, or have a drink with your housemates after a busy day.</p>\";s:6:\"images\";a:3:{i:0;s:28:\"Kitchen-MSNSDM_Apt 2R_13.jpg\";i:1;s:28:\"Kitchen-MSNSDM_Apt 2R_15.jpg\";i:2;s:28:\"Kitchen-MSNSDM_apt 2L_17.jpg\";}}i:4;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:17:\"The Cellar Lounge\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:4:\"body\";s:283:\"<p>Opening into the backyard is a large, fully furnished common lounge and work area where you can co-work with your housemates or relax after a long day. A laundry room is also located on this floor, so you\'ll never have to worry about finding an open machine at the laundromat.</p>\";s:6:\"images\";a:2:{i:0;s:53:\"maison-jefferson-basment-21.1200x1200.1200x1200_1.jpg\";i:1;s:53:\"maison-jefferson-basment-22.1200x1200.1200x1200_1.jpg\";}}i:5;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:29:\"The Backyard Community Garden\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:219:\"<p>A backyard is surrounded by planters customizable to tenants to grow anything you\'d like. The deck is furnished with lounge chairs and dining furniture, so you can enjoy one another\'s company during nice weather.</p>\";s:6:\"images\";a:1:{i:0;s:37:\"maison-jefferson-backyard-min-2_1.jpg\";}}i:6;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"title\";s:18:\"Perks and Benefits\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:1397:\"<div class=\"fx ch3 w perc_advantages\">\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Community</h4>\r\n<p>Meeting new people and building connections in a new city can be challenging. At Maison, you can meet your neighbors through the shared kitchens and large amenities provided in the building.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Common Areas</h4>\r\n<p>Each Maison unit is built around the idea of coming together as a community, with a spacious common kitchen and living room in-unit and an additional large lounge/work area that opens onto the furnished backyard. Tenants love our common areas for game nights, cooking together, or relaxing with a glass of wine to catch up on the events of the day.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Fully Furnished</h4>\r\n<p>All our properties are fully furnished with comfortable, high-quality, and functional furniture to make you feel at home.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">On-Site Laundry</h4>\r\n<p>This property has a dedicated laundry room with washers and dryers accessible at any time.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Convenience</h4>\r\n<p>With a minimum lease of 1 month, full furnishings, and no need to set up utilities and internet accounts, moving in is easy.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Common Place Cleanings</h4>\r\n<p>All of the common spaces in this property are cleaned bi-monthly by a team of professional cleaners.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\";}i:7;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"title\";s:17:\"THE NEIGHBOURHOOD\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:601:\"<p>Bushwick is deservedly known for its public art &mdash; the famous street murals &mdash; and its legendary nightlife scene. It&rsquo;s also home to people from all different walks of life, and you won&rsquo;t be surprised to experience what feels like a beautiful celebration of culture just walking down a street, listening to the languages being spoken while deciding which food cart to stop at. The neighborhood features the cherished Maria Hernandez Park, trendy cafes like Variety, a plethora of nightlife options, and an active community that encourages you to get to know your neighbors.</p>\";}}', '', '', 'a:2:{i:0;s:3:\"525\";i:1;s:3:\"439\";}', '', 2, '40.70558251', '-73.91974872', 528, '', '2022-10-26 05:14:56'),
