(532, 253, 443, 'the-woodbine-house', '', 'The Woodbine House ', 'The Woodbine House', '', 'The Woodbine House', '<p>Ridgewood, Queens</p>\r\n<p>Private rooms from $1340</p>', '<h1 class=\"h1 center\">The Woodbine House</h1>\r\n<h4>A CORNER HOME IN A QUIET NEIGHBORHOOD</h4>', '<div>\r\n<h6 class=\"h5\">The scoop&nbsp;</h6>\r\n<p>The Woodbine House is situated in Ridgewood, Queens, between Bushwick and Fresh Pond. This neighborhood is home to many local bars and restaurants and a short walk to other trendy areas in Brooklyn. You won&rsquo;t need to go far to find your next regular restaurant or bar. This house is perfectly set between 2 Burroughs, so you will have plenty to expolore without hopping on the subway. This home is an eight-unit property with a mix of furnished and unfurnished units, a full gym, and wonderful common spaces that will make you feel right at home.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h6 class=\"h5\">Location</h6>\r\n<p>The Woodbine House is located on a quaint street in Ridgewood that is sure to be a breath of fresh air compared to most bustling neighborhoods in New York. This area is known for its relaxed pace, historic streets, and incredible food, with the bonus of being just a 5 min walk from the Fresh Pond subway station and a 20-minute ride into central Williamsburg or a 30-minute ride into the Lower East Side of Manhattan.</p>\r\n</div>', 5, '', 'GCM_6111_2_3_4_5.1200x1200.jpg', 'GCM_6111_2_3_4_5.1200x1200.jpg', '', 238, 1, 1, 0, 0, 'The Woodbine House', 0, 0, 'a:9:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"title\";s:20:\"Throughout the house\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:680:\"<p>{throughout}</p>\r\n<table class=\"table v2\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<th>12+ Months</th>\r\n<th>5-11 Months</th>\r\n<th>1-4 Months</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Economy Twin</th>\r\n<td>$1260</td>\r\n<td>$1340</td>\r\n<td>$1940</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Private (Standard)</th>\r\n<td>$1340</td>\r\n<td>$1420</td>\r\n<td>$2020</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Private (Standard Large)</th>\r\n<td>$1440</td>\r\n<td>$1520</td>\r\n<td>$2120</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"5\">\r\n<p>*Prices above do not include $149/month/person utilities allowance fee</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div class=\"center\"><a class=\"button2 red\" href=\"join-us-manhattan\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Apply for free</a></div>\";}i:1;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:8:\"Bedrooms\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:4:\"body\";s:304:\"<p>All of The Woodbine House bedrooms are private and feature full-sized beds.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Amenities</strong>: full-size memory-foam mattresses, pillows, shelving, hooks, closets/organizational tools.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Services</strong>: Bedding is available for an additional fee.</li>\r\n</ul>\";s:6:\"images\";a:7:{i:0;s:24:\"GCM_6046_47_48_49_50.jpg\";i:1;s:20:\"GCM_6051_2_3_4_5.jpg\";i:2;s:24:\"GCM_6056_57_58_59_60.jpg\";i:3;s:20:\"GCM_6081_2_3_4_5.jpg\";i:4;s:20:\"GCM_6091_2_3_4_5.jpg\";i:5;s:20:\"GCM_6111_2_3_4_5.jpg\";i:6;s:24:\"GCM_6116_17_18_19_20.jpg\";}}i:2;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:19:\"The community space\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:4:\"body\";s:527:\"<p>The basement is a fully furnished shared common space and work area where you can co-work with your housemates or relax after a long day. A gym is also located on the main floor, so you\'ll never have to worry about finding a gym in the area again.</p>\r\n<p>The living room in each apartment in The Woodbine House is complete with couches and a table for working or eating. Whether you&rsquo;re cooking with your roommates or simply catching up, the shared spaces will always be the perfect spot to relax after a busy day.</p>\";s:6:\"images\";a:3:{i:0;s:24:\"GCM_6126_27_28_29_30.jpg\";i:1;s:22:\"GCM_6131_2_3_4_5_6.jpg\";i:2;s:24:\"GCM_6146_47_48_49_50.jpg\";}}i:4;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:12:\"The kitchens\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:614:\"<p>In these apartments, the kitchen is newly renovated and ready to be put to work. So whether you are making a home-cooked meal or opening the take-out from your favorite spot, you will have everything you need.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Amenities</strong> include electric stoves, stainless-steel fridges, microwaves, large sinks, coffee makers, blenders, plenty of cabinets, cookware, tableware, cutting boards, and anything else you would need in a kitchen.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Also included</strong>: paper towels, dish soap, hand soap, and garbage/recycling bags, all of which are routinely restocked.</li>\r\n</ul>\";s:6:\"images\";a:3:{i:0;s:24:\"GCM_6016_17_18_19_20.jpg\";i:1;s:20:\"GCM_6031_2_3_4_5.jpg\";i:2;s:24:\"GCM_6036_37_38_39_40.jpg\";}}i:5;O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:5:\"title\";s:7:\"the gym\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"2\";s:4:\"body\";s:148:\"<p>The Woodbine House includes a full gym &mdash; a luxury in New York City &mdash; so you won&rsquo;t have to worry about finding one near you!</p>\";s:6:\"images\";a:3:{i:0;s:24:\"GCM_6156_57_58_59_60.jpg\";i:1;s:20:\"GCM_6161_2_3_4_5.jpg\";i:2;s:24:\"GCM_6166_67_68_69_70.jpg\";}}i:6;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"title\";s:13:\"The bathrooms\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:244:\"<p>The Woodbine House features updated and renovated bathrooms with modern appliances to suit all your needs.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Also included:</strong> toilet paper, hand soap, and small garbage bags, which will never be empty!</li>\r\n</ul>\";}i:7;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"title\";s:19:\"PERKS AND BENEFITS:\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:644:\"<div class=\"fx ch3 w perc_advantages\">\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Fast, reliable WiFi</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Regular professional cleaning</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">On-site gym</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">Furnished interiors</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">UPDATED APPLIANCES</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">KEYLESS ENTRY</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">COMMUNITY EVENTS</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">DEDICATED MAINTENANCE TEAM</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">DEDICATED COMMUNITY MANAGER</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 class=\"title\">BI-MONTHLY CLEANINGS</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\";}i:8;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"title\";s:6:\"Prices\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:838:\"<table class=\"table v2\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<th>12+ Months</th>\r\n<th>5-11 Months</th>\r\n<th>1-4 Months</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Economy Twin</th>\r\n<td>$1260</td>\r\n<td>$1340</td>\r\n<td>$1940</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Private (Standard)</th>\r\n<td>$1340</td>\r\n<td>$1420</td>\r\n<td>$2020</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Private (Standard Large)</th>\r\n<td>$1440</td>\r\n<td>$1520</td>\r\n<td>$2120</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"5\">\r\n<p>*Prices above do not include $149/month/person utilities allowance fee</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div class=\"center\"><a class=\"button2 red\" href=\"join-us-manhattan\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Apply for free</a></div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Availability: Year-round / Minimum stay of 1 month / Month-to-month payment options available / Minimum age 18</strong></p>\";}i:9;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"title\";s:17:\"Welcome to Queens\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";s:544:\"<p>Ridgewood, Queens, may share a border with Bushwick, Brooklyn, but it has a unique history and culture. Step outside, pick a direction and walk; in no time, you&rsquo;ll find yourself admiring Ridgewood&rsquo;s historic architecture and many historical sites. Ridgewood isn&rsquo;t all history, of course &mdash; you&rsquo;ll find avenues lined with shops, restaurants, bars, and anything else you could need while walking or taking the subway; just a stop or two into Bushwick will take you to that neighborhood&rsquo;s famed nightlife.</p>\";}}', '', '', '', '', 