(85, 'please-sir-can-we-have-smores', 0, 'Please, sir. Can we have s’mores?', '<p>When: May 4th @ 7pm</p>\r\n<p>Where: South Williamsburg House, 21 Fayette Street</p>', '<p>What happens when you put chocolate, marshmallow and a little bit of fire in the same room together? S&rsquo;mores! Chocolatey, gooey, warm squares of goodness!<br /><br />Roasting fresh marshmallows around a campfire and smashing them together with blocks of chocolate and graham crackers has been an outdoor tradition throughout the US and Canada for several decades. Now we&rsquo;re sharing it with you - the members of Outpost Club!<br /><br />Come join us in the backyard of the new South Williamsburg house, where we&rsquo;ll be gathered around the firepit with roastable sweet treats in hand. <br /><br />Make sure to RSVP. Once you try them, you&rsquo;ll definitely want s&rsquo;more!<br /><br />Where: South Williamsburg House, 21 Fayette Street</p>', 0, 85, 'Please, sir. Can we have s’mores?', 'Please, sir. Can we have s’mores?, Events', 'Roasting fresh marshmallows around a campfire and smashing them together with blocks of chocolate and graham crackers has been an outdoor tradition throughout the US and Canada for several decades. Now we’re sharing it with you - the members of Outpost Club!', '2019-05-08 18:01:48', NULL, ''),
(83, 'quiche-my-brunch2', 0, 'Quiche My Brunch', '<p>When: April 21st @ 11:30A.M.</p>\r\n<p>Where: Bushwick House, 1277 Jefferson Ave</p>\r\n<p>Ridegewood House, 1925 Putnam Ave</p>', '<p>Quiche My Brunch is back! This week it will be held at the Bushwick and Ridgewood Houses where spinach and lorraine quiches will be served along with a variety of fruits, croissants, coffee and juices. Make sure to RSVP so we know how much quiche to buy!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Where: Bushwick House, 1277 Jefferson Ave</p>\r\n<p>Ridgewood House, 1925 Putnam Ave</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 0, 83, 'Quiche My Brunch', 'Quiche My Brunch, Events, Brunch', 'Quiche My Brunch is back! This week it will be held at the Bushwick and Ridgewood Houses where spinach and lorraine quiches will be served along with a variety of fruits, croissants, coffee and juices.', '2019-04-17 17:59:23', NULL, ''),
(84, 'parfait-brunch2', 0, 'Parfait Brunch', '<p>When: April 28th @ 11:30am</p>\r\n<p>Where: Central Park Manhattan&nbsp;House,&nbsp;350 Manhattan Ave</p>\r\n<p>South&nbsp;Williamsburg House,&nbsp;21 Fayette Street</p>', '<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Get your Sunday started off right with your very own yogurt parfait at this week&rsquo;s brunch. We&rsquo;ll be providing a variety of yogurt, granola, fruits, and croissants for you to mix and match to your heart&rsquo;s content. There will ofcourse be coffee and juice to wash it all down. So, please tap the RSVP button if you&rsquo;d like to be included!</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Where: Central Park Manhattan&nbsp;House,&nbsp;350 Manhattan Ave</p>\r\n<p>South&nbsp;Williamsburg House,&nbsp;21 Fayette Street</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 0, 84, 'Parfait Brunch', 'Parfait Brunch, Events', 'Get your Sunday started off right with your very own yogurt parfait at this week’s brunch. We’ll be providing a variety of yogurt, granola, fruits, and croissants for you to mix and match to your heart’s content.', '2019-04-24 15:20:43', NULL, ''),
(86, 'happy-hour-at-duckduck-bar', 0, 'Happy Hour at DuckDuck Bar', '', '<p>Is it happy hour yet? Friday, May 10th we&rsquo;ll be making a trip to DuckDuck in Williamsburg for happy hour specials from 4-8pm. Specials include buy-one-get-one well cocktails, half-off Rolling Rock Draft &amp; Narragansett Lager, and $1 off almost everything else! TGIF, right?!<br /><br />Even if you can&rsquo;t be there for the entire thing, stop by when you get off work!<br /><br />You must be 21+ to attend this event.<br /><br />Where: DuckDuck Bar - 161 Montrose Ave, Brooklyn<br /><br />Visit: <a href=\"https://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fduckduckbar.com%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1viAmCM-K31819j6VfyfPua0p2c4R3hRaU-9pOw1zxnHQBtIadJL0Eqo0&amp;h=AT3wWb2Mnml2PIrJbFZ5e8KfR4Lc4WL_7v96tx94ch7zTjoP2b-xYFw2TLJU5sI0Vy599mHGgbkssh9L7vWhMpjD2GqT6kmmR6a6zWoDOxm_SFqD637Uv73J7ysccxLwj4eJyQh3\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" data-lynx-mode=\"origin\">duckduckbar.com</a> for more info</p>', 0, 86, 'Happy Hour at DuckDuck Bar', 'Happy Hour at DuckDuck Bar, Events', 'Is it happy hour yet? Friday, May 10th we’ll be making a trip to DuckDuck in Williamsburg for happy hour specials from 4-8pm. Specials include buy-one-get-one well cocktails, half-off Rolling Rock Draft & Narragansett Lager, and $1 off almost everything else! TGIF, right?!', '2019-05-08 18:15:47', NULL, ''),
(87, 'meditation-workshop', 0, 'Meditation Workshop', '<p>When: May 16th @ 7:30pm</p>', '<p>Ever wonder how some people make tons of commitments in their daily lives, yet still have the mental strength to deal with angry New Yorkers and MTA delays at the end of the day? They probably meditate.<br /><br />If you&rsquo;ve ever been curious about the art of meditating, this month&rsquo;s workshop will be facilitated by Cody Blakely, a member of the Outpost East Bushwick house and future Ayurvedic Wellness Counselor. May 16th at the Bed-Stuy House we&rsquo;ll clear the floor for him to share a few techniques with us to use in our daily lives.<br /><br />Please RSVP if interested in attending.<br /><br />Where: Bed-Stuy House, 253 Hart Street<br /><br />We will be starting the meditation at 8pm sharp! Please arrive early!</p>', 0, 87, 'Meditation Workshop', 'Meditation Workshop, Events', 'If you’ve ever been curious about the art of meditating, this month’s workshop will be facilitated by Cody Blakely, a member of the Outpost East Bushwick house and future Ayurvedic Wellness Counselor. May 16th at the Bed-Stuy House we’ll clear the floor for him to share a few techniques with us to use in our daily lives.', '2019-05-08 18:26:20', NULL, ''),
(88, 'why-not-write2', 0, 'Why Not Write?', '<p>When: May 21st @ 7:30pm</p>', '<p>Calling all writers and artists! Have you done anything creative lately? Why Not Write?<br /><br />This event is now a regular part of the Outpost Club event series and will bring creative members of the community together to work on their projects in a supportive and non-judgmental environment. Whether it be a novel, short story, haiku or even a journal entry -- all are welcome to attend and work on their chosen craft. You&rsquo;re welcome to ask for constructive feedback from other attendees, or you can keep your project to yourself. Even if your project is not writing, you may still choose to bring it and work on that instead. Why Not Write might just be the motivation you need to get your project going!<br /><br />This event will be held at the East Bushwick House at 250 Schaefer Street. Refreshments will be served and you are welcome to bring your own drinkables.</p>', 0, 88, 'Why Not Write?', 'Why Not Write?, Events', '', '2019-05-08 18:30:40', NULL, ''),
(89, 'memorial-day-bbq', 0, 'Memorial Day BBQ', '<p>When: May 26th, 2019</p>\r\n<p>Where: East Williamsburg House, 118 Kingsland Ave</p>', '<p>It&rsquo;s finally warm enough to light up the BBQ grill! And we&rsquo;ll be doing just that for our members and friends on May 26 in celebration of Memorial Day. Join us in the East Williamsburg backyard for charcoal-grilled veggie burgers, regular burgers, hot dogs, potato chips, soda and more! <br /><br />Make sure to RSVP so we can save you a burger or two. Please feel free to bring your own food and snacks as well. BYOB!<br /><br />Where: East Williamsburg House, 118 Kingsland Ave, Brooklyn</p>', 0, 89, 'Memorial Day BBQ', 'Memorial Day BBQ, Events', 'It’s finally warm enough to light up the BBQ grill! And we’ll be doing just that for our members and friends on May 26 in celebration of Memorial Day. Join us in the East Williamsburg backyard for charcoal-grilled veggie burgers, regular burgers, hot dogs, potato chips, soda and more! ', '2019-05-08 18:38:10', NULL, ''),
(90, 'cereal-brunch', 0, 'Cereal Brunch', '<p>When: May 19th @ 12pm</p>\r\n<p>Where: Bushwick House, 1277 Jefferson Ave</p>\r\n<p>Ridgewood House, 1925 Putnam Ave</p>', '<p>For many of us, childhood was a golden age where we enjoyed crunchy cereals and all things sugar with no regrets. Enjoy being a kid again at this weekend&rsquo;s brunch, which will feature some of the cereals many of us knew and loved as children:<br /><br />Fruity Pebbles<br />Frosted Flakes<br />Cinnamon Toast Crunch<br />Oatmeal<br />and more!<br /><br />A variety of fruits, juices, waffles and (of course) coffee will be served.<br /><br />Where: Bushwick House, 1277 Jefferson Ave, Brooklyn<br /><span class=\"text_exposed_show\"><br />Ridgewood House, 1925 Putnam Ave, Brooklyn</span></p>', 0, 90, 'Cereal Brunch', 'Cereal Brunch, Events', 'Enjoy being a kid again at this weekend’s brunch, which will feature some of the cereals many of us knew and loved as children.', '2019-05-15 15:59:59', NULL, ''),
(91, 'avocado-toast-brunch', 0, 'Avocado Toast Brunch', '<p>When: May 26th @ 12pm</p>\r\n<p>Where: Central Park Manhattan House, 350 Manhattan Ave</p>\r\n<p>South Williamsburg House, 21 Fayette Street</p>', '<p>This week we&rsquo;re getting fancy with an Avocado Toast Brunch at the Central Park Manhattan and South Williamsburg Houses. Outpost will provide a variety of breads for toasting, tomatoes for topping and avocados for spreading at a brunch that will be both healthy and satisfying. Also on the menu is:<br /><br />Feta cheese<br />Cucumber<br />A variety of fruits<br />Fruit juice<br />&amp; Coffee<br /><br />If interested, please RSVP so we know how many avocados to bring!<br /><br />Where: Central Park Manhattan House, 350 Manhattan Avenue - NY, NY<br /><span class=\"text_exposed_show\"><br />South Williamsburg House, 21 Fayette Street - Brooklyn</span></p>', 0, 91, 'Avocado Toast Brunch', 'Avocado Toast Brunch, Events', '', '2019-05-15 16:04:51', NULL, ''),
(92, 'prospect-park-picnic', 0, 'Prospect Park Picnic', '<p>When: June 1, 2 p.m.</p>\r\n<p>Where: Bandshell Picnic Tables, Prospect Park</p>', '<p>Sunny days are finally here (we hope), so we\'re going to get out and enjoy them every chance we get.<br /><br />Join us June 1 in Prospect Park (closest to the Flatbush house), where we\'ll gather to play frisbee and bocce, have some lunch and lounge in the grass. We&rsquo;ll meet at the Bandshell Picnic Tables to start and you can join in whenever! Be aware that the later you are, the less likely there is to be food left (: <br /><br />This will be a great opportunity to reconnect with old friends and make new ones as members of all houses are welcome to attend. <br /><br />Where: At the Bandshell Picnic Tables just inside Prospect Park, near 9th St and Prospect Park West. The closest stops are the 7th Ave F/G, 9th St D/N/R/W and Grand Army Plaza 2/3/4. (Put \"Bandshell Picnic Tables\" into Google Maps)<br /><br />**Keep an eye on your house group chat for up-to-date location information in case we have to move within the park**</p>', 0, 92, 'Prospect Park Picnic', 'Prospect Park Picnic, Events', '', '2019-05-30 19:16:07', NULL, ''),
(93, 'smoothie-bowl-brunch', 0, 'Smoothie Bowl Brunch', '<p>When: June 2, 12 p.m.</p>\r\n<p>Where: East Bushwick, Flatbush and East Williamsburg houses</p>', '<p>***Please RSVP if you plan to attend so we can make sure to order enough food.***<br /><br />This week&rsquo;s brunch will feature everything you need to create the perfect smoothie bowl:<br /><br />Greek yogurt<br />Chia seeds<br />Sliced almonds<br />Coconut shreds<br />Almond milk<br />A variety of fruits<br />Fruit juices<br />...and more!<span class=\"text_exposed_show\"><br /><br />A blender will be onsite to thoroughly blend your creations. Coffee and croissants will be available, as well.<br /><br />All are welcome to join, regardless of which house you currently live at! <br /><br />East Bushwick House: 250 Schaefer St.<br />Flatbush House: 1682 Nostrand Ave.<br />East Williamsburg: 118 Kingsland</span></p>', 0, 93, 'Smoothie Bowl Brunch', 'Smoothie Bowl Brunch, Events', '', '2019-05-30 19:21:20', NULL, ''),
(94, 'downtown-brooklyn-rooftop-party', 0, 'Downtown Brooklyn Rooftop Party', '<p>When: June 8, 8 p.m.</p>\r\n<p>Where: Downtown Brooklyn House, 126 Douglass St.</p>', '<p>Join us at the Downtown Brooklyn House on June 8 for our first rooftop party of the season! Bring bottles, bring friends -- and tap that Going button if you\'re in so we can plan ahead, please! <br /><br />**If you don\'t know the door code, message your group chat when you arrive**</p>', 0, 94, 'Downtown Brooklyn Rooftop Party', 'Downtown Brooklyn Rooftop Party, Events', '', '2019-05-30 19:23:27', NULL, ''),
(95, 'kyle-southleigh-ep-release---free-show--party', 0, 'Kyle Southleigh EP Release - FREE Show + Party!', '<p>When: June 15, 6 p.m.</p>\r\n<p>Where: East Bushwick House, 250 Schaefer St.&nbsp;</p>', '<p>This\'ll be guaranteed to be a good time: Join us at East Bushwick on June 15 for a free concert! Kyle Southleigh, a member at the East Bushwick House, is releasing his EP and playing a show for Outpost members to celebrate. <br /><br />Kyle moved to New York in March to pursue his dream of releasing music and making a career out of it, but has been working on his first album for months longer. Come support a fellow Outpost member, enjoy the show, have a drink and head out afterward to continue the party! <br /><br />Doors: 6 p.m.<br />Intro: 7:30 p.m. <br />Show: 8 p.m.&ndash;9 p.m.<br /><br />Find Kyle on Instagram: @kylesouthleigh <br />Find him on Twitter: @Kyle_southleigh</p>', 0, 95, 'Kyle Southleigh EP Release - FREE Show + Party!', 'Kyle Southleigh EP Release - FREE Show + Party!, Events', '', '2019-05-30 19:43:24', NULL, ''),
(96, 'roaring-20s-speakeasy-party', 0, 'Roaring \'20s Speakeasy Party', '<p>When: June 21, 8 p.m.</p>\r\n<p>Where: NEW Knickerbocker House, 270 Jefferson St.&nbsp;</p>', '<p>To celebrate Outpost\'s 15th (!) house, we\'re turning the new Knickerbocker House\'s bar (you read that right!) into a Prohibition-era speakeasy, complete with \'20s-themed beverages, hors d\'oeuvres, card games, music and more. \'20s-era costumes/inspired-dress are strongly encouraged, but not required -- BUT, you might win something special if you dress up (:<br /><br />PASSWORD required for entry: \"Gatsby\"<br /><br />Here\'s an inspiration board for outfits: <a href=\"https://pin.it/z5ji224cmsz3by?fbclid=IwAR3wM91sLw7QvNmrJQkoftgKKxuBr8LnbsWM0yev25grVsTn4eKhQ705M4E\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" data-lynx-mode=\"origin\" data-lynx-uri=\"https://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpin.it%2Fz5ji224cmsz3by%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3wM91sLw7QvNmrJQkoftgKKxuBr8LnbsWM0yev25grVsTn4eKhQ705M4E&amp;h=AT31oIsvlzOb7Sn7pbjE_ea2fWrjiBT9kgnCdfEsNB5Zl2dMo9tHqf7Q9ywzbZEHnP5T9q5PerSCcLB2fb4R4eI_Bp-Fe38zsaeOaH_LvrXLvak2anZsy_6ifEGMCUR0UbSjZcBiRZ4\">https://pin.it/<wbr />z5ji224cmsz3by</a></p>', 0, 96, 'Roaring \'20s Speakeasy Party', 'Roaring \'20s Speakeasy Party, Events', '', '2019-05-30 19:47:08', NULL, ''),
(104, 'neon-glow-party', 0, 'Neon Glow Party', '<p>Rave who? We&rsquo;re bringing the glow to you with the greatest blacklight party of all Outpost Club history!</p>', '<p>Rave who? We&rsquo;re bringing the glow to you with the greatest blacklight party of all Outpost Club history. We&rsquo;ve got music, a blacklight dance floor, and a glowing face paint station!</p>\r\n<p>We&rsquo;re going to light up the night with this luminous shindig and we&rsquo;d love to see you there! RSVP by tapping &ldquo;Going&rdquo; on this event. Make sure to wear white or neon to make the most of the blacklight action! See you there!</p>', 0, 103, 'Neon Glow Party', 'Neon Glow Party, Events', 'Rave who? We’re bringing the glow to you with the greatest blacklight party of all Outpost Club history. We’ve got music, a blacklight dance floor, and a glowing face paint station! \r\n\r\nWe’re going to light up the night with this luminous shindig and we’d love to see you there! RSVP by tapping “Going” on this event. Make sure to wear white or neon to make the most of the blacklight action! See you there!\r\n', NULL, NULL, ''),
(97, 'backyard-tiki-party', 0, 'Backyard Tiki Party', '<p>When: June 28, 8 p.m.</p>\r\n<p>Where: South Williamsburg House, 21 Fayette St.&nbsp;</p>', '<p>It\'s officially the first weekend of summer -- so do you know what that means? It\'s backyard tiki party time at the South Williamsburg House!</p>\r\n<p>Mingle with old friends and make new ones while you swing and lounge on the hammocks. Dance to the beat in the spacious backyard, snack on finger foods and drink some special tiki punch to really feel the vibe. BYOB, and see you there!</p>\r\n<p>**Friends are welcome, but please RSVP**</p>', 0, 97, 'Backyard Tiki Party', 'Backyard Tiki Party, Events', '', '2019-05-30 20:41:37', NULL, ''),
(98, 'pride-mimosa-brunch', 0, 'PRIDE Mimosa Brunch', '<p>When: June 30, 10:30 a.m.&ndash;12:30 p.m.</p>\r\n<p>Where: Montrose Williamsburg House, 131 Boerum St.&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Whether you\'re LGBTQIA+ or an ally, you\'re welcome at our pre-Pride March mimosa brunch at the Montrose Williamsburg House. <br /><br />We\'re starting brunch early so we can head to the parade route in the city with plenty of time to celebrate -- so make sure to bring whatever you need!<br /><br />Please remember to tap \"Going\" if you\'re planning to join so we can get enough (lol) champagne.<br /><br />**As with all Outpost events, this is a queer-friendly safe space. You\'re welcome to attend even if you don\'t identify as LGBTQIA+, but please be respectful.**</p>', 0, 98, 'PRIDE Mimosa Brunch', 'PRIDE Mimosa Brunch, Events', '', '2019-05-30 20:48:02', NULL, ''),
(99, 'san-francisco-pizza--movie', 0, 'San Francisco: Pizza + Movie', '<p>When: June 27, 7 p.m.</p>\r\n<p>Where: Japantown House</p>', '<p>Join us in the common area for pizza and a movie!</p>', 0, 99, 'San Francisco: Pizza + Movie', 'San Francisco: Pizza + Movie, Events', 'Join us in the common area for pizza and a movie!', '2019-06-13 17:16:41', NULL, ''),
(100, '4th-of-july-bbq--fireworks', 0, '4th of July BBQ + Fireworks', '<p>Happy 4th of July! We&rsquo;ll be celebrating this most American of holidays in true Outpost style: With a giant community party -- and we&rsquo;ll be pulling out all the stops for this one. Join us at the South Williamsburg House for a daytime BBQ, with an array of games and rays rolling on the rooftop and the backyard.</p>', '<p>Happy 4th of July! We&rsquo;ll be celebrating this most American of holidays in true Outpost style: With a giant community party -- and we&rsquo;ll be pulling out all the stops for this one. Join us at the South Williamsburg House for a daytime BBQ, with an array of games and rays rolling on the rooftop and the backyard. <br /><br />There will be a range of food throughout the day, as well as cornhole, bocce ball, great conversation and of course we&rsquo;ll be watching the fireworks at around 9:25pm -- with a great view of the East River from the rooftop! <br /><br />Bring bottles, bring friends, bring red white and blue anything. Tap \'Going\' on this event or the website so we know how much food to buy! See you there!</p>', 0, 100, '4th of July BBQ + Fireworks', '4th of July BBQ + Fireworks, Events', 'Happy 4th of July! We’ll be celebrating this most American of holidays in true Outpost style: With a giant community party -- and we’ll be pulling out all the stops for this one. ', '2019-06-25 19:21:56', NULL, ''),
(101, 'coney-island-day-trip', 0, 'Coney Island Day Trip', '<p>It wouldn\'t be summer without a trip to Coney Island! If you don\'t already know, Coney Island is New York City\'s favorite beach destination.</p>', '<p>It wouldn\'t be summer without a trip to Coney Island! If you don\'t already know, Coney Island is New York City\'s favorite beach destination. It\'s in Brooklyn and accessible by subway (yay!)... There\'s sand, sea, a funfair and plenty of hot-dogs and ice cream.<br /><br />We\'ll be meeting at the beach at 1 p.m and we\'ll spend the Saturday soaking up the sun and playing beach games. Just bring a towel and (if you\'re brave) a swimsuit. See you there!</p>', 0, 101, 'Coney Island Day Trip', 'Coney Island Day Trip, Events', 'It wouldn\'t be summer without a trip to Coney Island! If you don\'t already know, Coney Island is New York City\'s favorite beach destination.', '2019-06-27 23:38:21', NULL, ''),
(102, 'movies-with-a-view-trip-girlfight', 0, 'Movies with a View Trip: Girlfight', '<p>Movie nights are better outside. They\'re even better with friends and a panoramic view of the Brooklyn Bridge and the river!</p>', '<p>Movie nights are better outside. They\'re even better with friends and a panoramic view of the Brooklyn Bridge and the river!&nbsp;We\'ll be making a trip to Brooklyn Bridge Park for the annual \'Movies with a View\' to see Girlfight (movie info below). There will be music, street food and a beautiful sunset followed by the movie.<br /><br />We\'ll meet at 6 p.m to get a good spot, but feel free to show up later. The music kicks off at 6 and the movie starts at sundown (around 8:20 p.m). Bring a blanket to sit on if you don\'t want to get grassy -- full info on the website here: <a href=\"https://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.brooklynbridgepark.org%2Fevents%2Fgirlfight%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0U4wDnMYVGQHb1FYAxSHmRtiYTLgu6GUeqO76yKAhPwz9NoU14wSJ8rC4&amp;h=AT1IcyFIC9vCPKmIKXOdBJMj2bU44NNZaCCzvOu-abdKLBVLbdIr9jRtM_NbSrY-mR6K0mVl-2SmElpGL3g93lc4-xUkY9nb4FvjePhm_4ZPAJiiOi8kGsCjaYEzaE-CkUh7ppYS\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" data-lynx-mode=\"origin\">https://<wbr />www.brooklynbridgepark.org/<wbr />events/girlfight</a> <br /><br />More about Girlfight:&nbsp;\"High-school senior Diana (Michelle Rodriguez), without her father knowing, trains as a boxer and achieves impressive success, blazing new trails for female boxers. Girlfight (2000) is written and directed by Karyn Kusama.\"</p>', 0, 102, 'Movies with a View Trip: Girlfight', 'Movies with a View Trip: Girlfight, Events', 'Movie nights are better outside. They\'re even better with friends and a panoramic view of the Brooklyn Bridge and the river!', '2019-06-27 23:43:59', NULL, ''),
(103, 'karaoke-at-cobra-club', 0, 'Karaoke at Cobra Club', '<p>Waiting to be discovered as a singing sensation? Looking for an invitation to Broadway? This is your moment. Or just come and laugh at others. No pressure.</p>', '<p>Waiting to be discovered as a singing sensation? Looking for an invitation to Broadway? This is your moment. Or just come and laugh at others. No pressure.<br /><br />We\'ll be heading to Cobra Club for their Friday night karaoke session, a fun bar with cheap drinks and a relaxed vibe in the heart of Bushwick. <br /><br />We\'ll meet at the East Bushwick House for pre-game to dampen any nerves, but you can meet us directly at Cobra if you like. Just as long as you bring your sense of adventure (and a crowd-pleasing song choice idea...).</p>', 0, 107, 'Karaoke at Cobra Club', 'Karaoke at Cobra Club, Events', 'Waiting to be discovered as a singing sensation? Looking for an invitation to Broadway? This is your moment.', '2019-06-27 23:47:47', NULL, ''),
(107, 'ice-cream-social', 0, 'Ice Cream Social', '<p>What brings people together more than our shared love of ice cream?</p>', '<p>What brings people together more than our shared love of ice cream? We have all the toppings and all the good times.</p>\r\n<p>This summer has been ridiculously hot, so why not cool down and chill out in the sweetest of ways?</p>\r\n<p>Looking forward to seeing you there!</p>', 0, 104, 'Ice Cream Social', 'Ice Cream Social, Events', 'What brings people together more than our shared love of ice cream? We have all the toppings and all the good times. \r\n\r\nThis summer has been ridiculously hot, so why not cool down and chill out in the sweetest of ways? \r\n\r\nLooking forward to seeing you there!', NULL, NULL, ''),
(106, 'trivia-night', 0, 'Trivia Night at Caveat NYC', '<p>This isn&rsquo;t your average pub trivia &ndash; this is interactive storytelling you can WIN.&nbsp;</p>', '<p>This isn&rsquo;t your average pub trivia &ndash; this is interactive storytelling you can WIN.</p>\r\n<p>You and your team will compete in an adventure of trivia and storytelling, revealing clues to a bigger, mind-blowing true story along the way, with chances to upset the score via physical challenges and treasure hunts!</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">As an Outpost Club member, entrance is free to the event! Register here: </span><a href=\"https://www.caveat.nyc/event/big-questions-little-answers-8-16-2019\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">https://www.caveat.nyc/event/big-questions-little-answers-8-16-2019</span></a></p>', 0, 105, 'Trivia Night at Caveat NYC', 'Trivia Night at Caveat NYC, Events', 'This isn’t your average pub trivia – this is interactive storytelling you can WIN. \r\n\r\nYou and your team will compete in an adventure of trivia and storytelling, revealing clues to a bigger, mind-blowing true story along the way, with chances to upset the score via physical challenges and treasure hunts!', NULL, NULL, ''),
(105, '', 0, 'Summer Bash', '<p>We are going all out for our celebration of the summer! Food and activities galore!</p>', '<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We&rsquo;re going all out for our celebration of the summer! We&rsquo;re coming together to have a fantastic time, toss and score with cornhole and sing your favorite summer jams with karaoke. Risk it for the biscuit with Giant Jenga and compete for the win in bocce ball.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">See how low you can go with limbo and throw around a frisbee or beach balls with friends. Endless possibilities await for a great time. Last but not least, there will be pizza and s&rsquo;mores to round out the night with deliciousness.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Tap &ldquo;Going&rdquo; on this event or on the website to let us know you&rsquo;ll be there and how much food to buy. Looking forward to seeing you there!</span></p>', 0, 106, 'Summer Bash', 'Summer Bash, Events', 'We’re going all out for our celebration of the summer! We’re coming together to have a fantastic time, toss and score with cornhole and sing your favorite summer jams with karaoke. Risk it for the biscuit with Giant Jenga and compete for the win in bocce ball. \r\n\r\nSee how low you can go with limbo and throw around a frisbee or beach balls with friends. Endless possibilities await for a great time. Last but not least, there will be pizza and s’mores to round out the night with deliciousness. \r\n\r\n', NULL, NULL, ''),
(108, 'mexican-independence-day-party', 0, 'Mexican Independence Day Party', '<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Join us for our Mexican Independence Day fiesta on Saturday, September 14th at 5pm at the East Bushwick House. We will enjoy Mexican food and drink while celebrating Mexican Independence. &iexcl;Viva Mexico!&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Join us for our Mexican Independence Day fiesta on Saturday, September 14th at 5pm at the East Bushwick House. We will enjoy Mexican food and drink while celebrating Mexican Independence. &iexcl;Viva Mexico!&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Let us know you&rsquo;ll be there by tapping &ldquo;Going&rdquo; on the Facebook event or RSVP&nbsp;here!</span></p>', 0, 108, 'Mexican Independence Day Party', 'Mexican Independence Day Party, Events', 'Join us for our Mexican Independence Day fiesta on Saturday, September 14th at 5pm at the East Bushwick House. We will enjoy Mexican food and drink while celebrating Mexican Independence. ¡Viva Mexico! ', NULL, NULL, ''),
(109, 'bbq-meet--greet', 0, 'BBQ Meet & Greet', '<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We&rsquo;re excited to welcome you to Outpost with our BBQ get-together on Sunday, Sept. 22 at 2pm at the Journal Square House. Get to know the other Outpost New Jersey members and enjoy the beginning of the fall season together!</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We&rsquo;re excited to welcome you to Outpost with our BBQ get-together on Sunday, Sept. 22 at 2pm at the Journal Square House. Get to know the other Outpost New Jersey members and enjoy the beginning of the fall season together!</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Let us know you&rsquo;ll be there by tapping &ldquo;Going&rdquo; on the Facebook event or RSVP&nbsp;here!</span></p>', 0, 109, 'BBQ Meet & Greet', 'BBQ Meet & Greet, Events', 'We’re excited to welcome you to Outpost with our BBQ get-together on Sunday, Sept. 22 at 2pm at the Journal Square House. Get to know the other Outpost New Jersey members and enjoy the beginning of the fall season together!', NULL, NULL, ''),
(110, 'smores--cider-night', 0, 'S\'mores & Cider Night', '<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Fall is officially here, and we&rsquo;re celebrating by gathering around the fire and cooking up some s&rsquo;mores on Saturday, Sept. 21 at 8pm at the South Williamsburg House! We&rsquo;ll spend the first night of fall sitting around the fire, making s&rsquo;mores and drinking cider and hot cocoa in anticipation of the turning of the leaves and crisp weather!</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Fall is officially here, and we&rsquo;re celebrating by gathering around the fire and cooking up some s&rsquo;mores on Saturday, Sept. 21 at 8pm at the South Williamsburg House! We&rsquo;ll spend the first night of fall sitting around the fire, making s&rsquo;mores and drinking cider and hot cocoa in anticipation of the turning of the leaves and crisp weather!</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Let us know you&rsquo;ll be there by tapping &ldquo;Going&rdquo; on the Facebook event or RSVP&nbsp;here!</span></p>', 0, 110, 'S\'mores & Cider Night', 'S\'mores & Cider Night, Events', 'Fall is officially here, and we’re celebrating by gathering around the fire and cooking up some s’mores on Saturday, Sept. 21 at 8pm at the South Williamsburg House! We’ll spend the first night of fall sitting around the fire, making s’mores and drinking cider and hot cocoa in anticipation of the turning of the leaves and crisp weather!', NULL, NULL, ''),
(111, 'pizza--game-night', 0, 'Pizza & Game Night', '<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Join us for pizza and games galore. You&rsquo;ll be sure to find a great New York slice and favorite games like UNO, Cards Against Humanity, Catchphrase, Pictionary, Werewolf, Ping Pong and more on Saturday, Sept. 29 at 6pm at the Bed-Stuy House! </span></p>', '<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Join us for pizza and games galore. You&rsquo;ll be sure to find a great New York slice and favorite games like UNO, Cards Against Humanity, Catchphrase, Pictionary, Werewolf, Ping Pong and more on Saturday, Sept. 29 at 6pm at the Bed-Stuy House! </span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Let us know you&rsquo;ll be there by tapping &ldquo;Going&rdquo; on the Facebook event or RSVP&nbsp;here!</span></p>', 0, 111, 'Pizza & Game Night', 'Pizza & Game Night, Events', 'Join us for pizza and games galore. You’ll be sure to find a great New York slice and favorite games like UNO, Cards Against Humanity, Catchphrase, Pictionary, Werewolf, Ping Pong and more on Sunday, Sept. 29 at 6pm at the Bed-Stuy House! ', NULL, NULL, ''),
(112, 'greek-food-festival', 0, 'Greek Food Festival', '<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Join us for the 68th-annual Greek Food Festival! If you love your spanakopita, moussaka and gyros, or even if you don&rsquo;t know what they are, this is sure to be an event to remember. There will be homemade Greek pastries, Greek music and dancing, as well as wine tasting! We&rsquo;ll meet on Saturday, Sept. 21 at 3pm at the SoMa House and leave for the festival together.</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Join us for the 68th-annual Greek Food Festival! If you love your spanakopita, moussaka and gyros, or even if you don&rsquo;t know what they are, this is sure to be an event to remember. There will be homemade Greek pastries, Greek music and dancing, as well as wine tasting! We&rsquo;ll meet on Saturday, Sept. 21 at 3pm at the SoMa House and leave for the festival together.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Let us know you&rsquo;ll be there by tapping &ldquo;Going&rdquo; on the Facebook event or RSVP&nbsp;here!</span></p>', 0, 112, 'Greek Food Festival', 'Greek Food Festival, Events', 'Join us for the 68th-annual Greek Food Festival! If you love your spanakopita, moussaka and gyros, or even if you don’t know what they are, this is sure to be an event to remember. There will be homemade Greek pastries, Greek music and dancing, as well as wine tasting! We’ll meet on Saturday, Sept. 21 at 3pm at the SoMa House and leave for the festival together.', NULL, NULL, '');
